{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r746568155", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing food", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "21 February 2020", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much Eutalika for your amazing 5 star review, we are thrilled that you enjoyed the experience so much, my Bokan team are thrilled. We are really looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "eutalika", "reviewer_origin": ["Canterbury, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r746568155-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Highly recommend the food! The most amazing location and the best chefs!great view, amazing food, exciting flavours that I've never tried before! I went with my friends and with my family! Great place for romantic dinner \u2764"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r739899453", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "MAGNIFIQUE ", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "18 January 2020", "answer_text": ["Wow Jean Yves, your review is amazing. We just loved reading and sharing it with our talent. Thank you so much and we look forward to welcoming you back for another Magnifique experience soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JeanyvesTov", "reviewer_origin": ["Golfe-Juan Vallauris, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r739899453-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Whaou ", "It\u2019s really really good, ", "We\u2019re passionned about good gastromy in France, and this restaurant it\u00b4s absolutely perfect!", "The view is fantastic ", "The food is fabulous ", "The service is so nice ", "Always it\u2019s really perfect ", "Again thanks you for this moment fantastic ", "\u00abthe better restaurant in London\u00a0\u00bb "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r741474592", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Much better out there......", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "27 January 2020", "answer_text": ["Thank you Kevin T for sharing your experience from last night. I am so sorry that we disappointed you. I have spoken with Ornella who looked after you and we really wish you had let us know that you were disappointed with us so we could have rectified this before you left. If you would contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com I would appreciate it. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "satanbug", "reviewer_origin": ["Auckland, New Zealand"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "528"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "170"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r741474592-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were on site so decided to visit. We shared a few starters and a main with a couple of cold beers. We arrived as the restaurant opened and were told there were only two lobsters left if that was what we fancied. Hopeless...The starters were good, we enjoyed those but when the mains finally arrived over an hour later all were dry and tasteless. For close to \u00a3 300 pounds you would expect much, much better and I won\u2019t bother again. Enjoy...."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r738963228", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A wonder", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "13 January 2020", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much Maylis N for this fabulous review and I am so happy you and your brother enjoyed your time with us. Guillaume is so creative and his flavours are amazing. Of course Florian compliments the food beautifully with the service. We are really looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "maylisn2020", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r738963228-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My brother and I went to Bokan for dinner last week and I'll surely return.", "First, the view, breath-taking! Maybe one of the best in London. ", "Then the service, brilliant. Professional, precise, very knowledgeable and lovely staff.", "And the food! Outstanding! The young Head chef, French and talented, is so creative. The association of flavors and textures, gorgeous. ", "It's been a long time I've had such a surprising and delightful dinner. ", "Modernity weds UK sourced products with perfection. The menu is intelligent, using local and seasonal products, artistic, plates are wonderful, and nearly magical, making octopus dance gracefully with clementine and chocolate is definitely magic.", "Go there with no hesitation, you won't be desappointed!", "Congratulations to this young and efficient team lead by the charming Florian."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r739999991", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful as Well as good ", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "19 January 2020", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much Justine R for this beautiful 5 star review about your recent experience in Bokan. We are thrilled that you and your partner enjoyed this special time with us and I hope we can welcome you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "justine-royer85", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r739999991-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to dinner with my partner in this restaurant, and we came out absolutely smitten. The setting and the view are sublime, the atmosphere is warm, the team is very professional, and the dishes will amaze you with their flavours. ", "I highly recommend to spend a pleasant moment under all plans."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r741502709", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Disappointed ", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "27 January 2020", "answer_text": ["Thank you Elena T for your review. I have spoken with length with Florian who I know you spoke with on Saturday also. I would rally appreciate it if you could contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com to discuss these issues. I am so sorry and look forward to hearing from you. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "elenatX4465YE", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r741502709-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I dined here with friends on a Saturday night, restaurant was not crazy busy and we had a wonderful table by the window with an amazing view. This was the only positive point I can say about my dinner experience. It was not the first time for me here, I visited the bar and the restaurant few times and this was very disappointing: we went with the tasting menu and between the first 3 courses we waited a crazy amount of time (30/40 minutes) and we then asked if it was possible to speed up a little bit. After our request was taken very seriously and we did not even have the time to finish the following course that we have our plate cleared and the new course on the table.", "The service was bland, not attentive at all. Clearing the table a waitress dropped a fork on my friend\u2019s dress and did not even apologise! She looked at my friend like it was her fault. ", "What is more I mentioned in the booking notes, I called and I sent an email as it was a special birthday celebration and I was reassured that they would have presented a celebration cake at the table. We had dessert, we had coffe, asked for the bill.... celebration plate never arrived.", "This is not what you expect when you pay almost \u00a3500 for a dinner not even in a Michelin star or anything like that.", "I won\u2019t be back in the restaurant for sure."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r741703006", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food, service and amazing views", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "28 January 2020", "answer_text": ["We absolutely love your 5 star review Hallie14, thank you so much for sharing this. To be one of your best restaurant experiences you have had in London makes us really proud. We are really looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Hallie14", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "294"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "155"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r741703006-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Took my friend for her birthday it was one of the best restaurants experiences I have had in London. The staff was so so helpful and could not do enough to help you and spoke us over everything we ate and drank. ", "We went for the 6 course tasting menu which was amazing choice and served so nicely and on request not when they wanted us to have it. It is a great relaxing restaurant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r743086109", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "THE WORST CUSTOMER LOYALTY IN LONDON! MCDONALDS STYLE MANAGEMENT & ATTITUDE WITH BETTER FOOD.", "diner_date": " January 2020", "rating_date": "4 February 2020", "answer_text": ["Thank you Richard A for your review and I am so sad to read your feedback. Please be assured that you are not just a number to us, we really do value you. I would really appreciate it Richard if you could contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com so I can personally look after you and your future bookings with us. I really hope that we can have another chance as we have looked after you so well for 2 years I would really appreciate the opportunity to fix this issue and personally make sure you have a great evening with the table you wish for. I look forward to hearing from you. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - Bokan General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Richard A", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r743086109-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["For about 2 years I've dinned at Bokan approximately 4 times a month and maybe even more. I even chose Bokan for Christmas lunch. I think I could be considered a good, if not a very loyal client. I have never pulled rank, never asked for special treatment and never got stressed out over the placement of the table. I have now planned a dinner for 6 at Bokan next month. For this one time I asked if I could reserve a table of my choice for this very special group of people to experience the restaurant. I was told very plainly and clearly ..... NO, IT IS NOT OUR POLICY! I was even told by one staff member that if I came 2 hours in advance of the dinner at 6pm I could then take the table of my choice because the place would be empty !!!! Now, I have been dining in the best restaurants in the world for about 60 years in fact long before any of the Bokan staff could even spell the word restaurant. The fact that for one time I'm not able to book a table of my choice proves several facts. 1. There is no restaurant / customer loyalty. 2. The management of the restaurant really has no idea what world class dining is about! 3. The customers of Bokan are merely a number and the place clearly caters to the transient diner with whom they need not establish a rapport or a relationship with. Considering this attitude of Bokan I will take my custom as well as my friends elsewhere. We will dine on the special evening mentioned at C. London (Cipriani) where I can book the table I feel comfortable at, where the table linens are as exquisite as the food and the white uniformed staff is smiling, courteous, and care about me ...... the customer. Goodbye Bokan. Your mediocre service will not take you far. By the way, The Ivy In The Park is also a wonderful restaurant that cares about their clients."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r746567050", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing cuisine ", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "21 February 2020", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much Eutalia L for sharing your amazing experience at Bokan, thank you so much! My team are thrilled with your feedback and we can't wait to welcome you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "eutalial2019", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r746567050-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The best food cooked by amazing chefs# served by very friendly staff! Amazing view as well! Highly recommend the restaurant # "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r745907605", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Bottomless brunch with a view ", "diner_date": " February 2020", "rating_date": "18 February 2020", "answer_text": ["Oh Shelley4096 thank you so much for this fabulous 5 star review about your bottomless brunch, we are thrilled that you never had an empty glass and of course that you loved the amazing food. We are really looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Shelley4096", "reviewer_origin": ["Leatherhead, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "102"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r745907605-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What a great place we chose for our bottomless brunch, never once had an empty glass for two hours! Never rushed us off the table. Stayed all afternoon. The food was AMAZING. Staff were great and can\u2019t wait to return. Oh and the views are incredible even in Storm Dennis!! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r731119585", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Lovely food let down by front of house", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "7 December 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you Ted181 for your feedback. I absolutely agree that the service absolutely has to match the food. I am so sorry about your experience at Bokan. I would really appreciate it if you could contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com to discuss your issues further. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ted181", "reviewer_origin": ["Northamptonshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r731119585-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Bokan 37 is an expensive restaurant. So I expected the service to be top class too. However, it was very disjointed. On arrival, as a party of 4, we were not offered a drink but given the wine menu. So we selected a bottle of champagne. The waitress took our order for the champagne and the starters and main courses. She sent over the sommelier who recommended and left on the table a claret for the main course. We then waited for a while until the starters arrived whereby we had to chase up the champagne. When it finally arrived the waiter tried to take away the claret glasses until we retrieved them as we also had our claret, long before the champagne. Fortunately we had chosen cold starters. Then during the main course one of the waitresses leant right across the table to pour the jus rather than going around. The service continued rather haphazardly all evening. Overall, the view is lovely, the food is tasty and beautifully presented but the kitchen is let down by a disorganised (but friendly) waiting staff."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r738131882", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful experience !", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "9 January 2020", "answer_text": ["On behalf of myself, Guillaume and Florian, THANK YOU for this wonderful review about your experience in Bokan and we have to agree that the octopus is absolutely one of our favourite dishes. We are so pleased that we made your night so special ad I am sure now you know about us we will be welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "182acp", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r738131882-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Never heard of this restaurant before but I heard it was good so I decided to give it a shot for a special evening with my girlfriend and I\u2019m glad I did!", "The restaurant is very cosy with a great view of the city. The staff is very welcoming and the floor manager, Florian has been very helpful.", "I took the octopus as a starter and followed with the turbot. The dishes where delicious, with inventive and original combinations of ingredients. The chef, Guillaume, did an excellent job and I will surely be back! ", "I will definitely be back and I\u2019d like to thank the whole team for making our night so special !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r730860531", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "25th Birthday Dinner", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "5 December 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your beautiful 5 star review. I am thrilled that you enjoyed your experience with us and of course the amazing views. I hope we can welcome you back next time you are over from Italy. Our menu changes frequently so lot's more dishes to try. Many thanks again. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Graziamp", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r730860531-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We came from Italy just for two days for our son's birthday and we spent one evening at the Bokan 37. Everything was amazing except the table that wasn't the one we asked for when we booked, but it didn't really matter because the view was great anyway. Food and service were very good, we enjoyed the evening!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r725877871", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing dinner", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "12 November 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow, we love your amazing review Chagte about your romantic evening in Bokan. I am so pleased that you enjoyed the tasting menu and of course the welcome from our lovely Coco starts the night off perfectly. We look forward to welcoming you back. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Chagte", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r725877871-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["First,this place has a stunning view from the 37 floor,moreover there is a bar on the 38th floor and a terrace on the 39th f.", "We had a very warm welcome from coco the French host and our waiter (Portuguese guy with mustache) very knowledgeable of all the dishes and wines.", "We booked for the Chef menu tasting of 6 courses, very tasty food and dessert!Love it!", "We had a very romantic night.Thank you bokan!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r734075707", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Bokan 38 Bar; Well looked after, great views...", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "22 December 2019", "answer_text": ["We love our 5 star rating and review GaryJ1956, thank you so much for sharing your Bokan experience. I am so pleased that you really enjoyed your time with us and were well looked after. I hope we can welcome you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GaryJ1956", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r734075707-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great setting on 38th floor with extensive views over London skyline... Spacious table for party of six, (advise booking in advance at popular times), well looked after by the bar staff, stayed for about 2 hrs and had a great time. Recommended"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r727611346", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Staff needs improvement", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "19 November 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you DeniseDalton for taking the time to share your experience and I am sorry we have let you down on this occasion. I have shared your feedback with my Restaurant Manager and Welcome team and please be assured that I am addressing it. If you do decide to return please contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com so I can ensure you have a 5 star experience with us next time. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Lauren T", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r727611346-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice view but the service needs a lot of work ", "Initially the host did not ask if we would like to check our coats. I mentioned that every guest had their coats in the restaurant, which looked untidy with coats everywhere.", ".The table we sat was good , since we didn't have any reservation.", "We chose a bottle of an excellent wine, which we didn't enjoy enough because the waitress didn't have a clue how to open a wine bottle, and cork residues felt in. So we asked for another bottle straight away, as long as we knew how bad is for poisoning the cork. ", "The food we ordered was nothing special and overpriced. Our fried potatoes, of course, took 40 minutes to arrive.", "Great for its view and the easy access, but the service needs improvement (not worthy of the service charge you are required to pay)."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r726420148", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday Dinner", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "14 November 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much LuciemQ1439DG for your beautiful review about your recent Bokan Experience. I am so pleased that you and your boyfriend had such amazing time with us and we looked after you so well. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon and we are looking forward to it. Kind regards. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "luciemQ1439DG", "reviewer_origin": ["Northampton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r726420148-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went with my boyfriend for his birthday dinner and it was absolutely amazing. Service was high level, food was great and the view was stunning. Personnel helped us with our dietary requirements and gave us the table we asked for when we booked. Definitely recommended!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r734982490", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Christmas Disasters", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "27 December 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your feedback Yvonne G. I am slightly confused as to why you would ever be told we were serving Turkey and Pudding and custard as this has never been on the menu and I confirmed with my talent that the only menu we sent to people was the one we were serving. I am sorry that you did not like the dishes we presented to you and indeed the salmon is served raw as it was described tartare. I would appreciate it if you could contact me directly to discuss in more detail the issues you had on h9057-gm@accor.com. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Yvonne G", "reviewer_origin": ["Croydon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "72"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "72"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r734982490-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I booked Bokan Christmas dinner because we were staying in the hotel on 25/12/19 and at the time of booking, I spoke to a staff who told me that on Christmas Day the restaurant would serve turkey and Christmas pudding with custard. On Christmas Day I was shocked and upset at the restaurant when I spoke to a waiter and I was told that there was no turkey or Christmas pudding with custard.", "The waitress gave us a table in the corner facing the window and no one could see our faces only our backs. We received bad customer care, a waiter took our orders he frequently went to other tables and check if other customers were ok and if their food is ok and we were ignored. I had to get out of my seat to go over to speak to a waiter to say that I was not happy with the starter. ", "I received the crab starter but it was making me sick so I was given the salmon but it was raw and I was unable to eat this. ", "We ordered the main dish cow\u2019s cheek and chips but when this arrived we ate a small piece but it was slimy and was making us sick. We called the waiter and asked him if we could have another main dish and he said, \u201cNo because the chef cooked it for us and cannot give us another main dish.\u201d My daughter and I only ate the chips for the main dish. ", "The waitress recommended The Red Seal cocktail, this was served in a long stem champagne glass and not a cocktail glass and it was very sour. We told the waiter that we did not like it because it was very sour. He said he would ask the bar upstairs to make us a sweet cocktail. We were given another cocktail in a black African head glass. I asked the waiter if he could let me know what the ingredients are and if grapefruit juice was in the cocktail. He later returned and said grapefruit juice is not in the cocktail but he does not know the rest of the ingredients because they made it upstairs in the bar. ", "The dessert Christmas log with ice cream was ok. ", "The bill was presented in an old reading book \u201cThe Facemaker\u201d. I asked the waiter I have never seen the bill presented in this way. He said it is new.", " I rang the reception and spoke to Jerome about the problems we had in the restaurant and that our main meal Cow\u2019s cheek was taken away but we were not offered another main meal and we were starving. My daughter is allergic to all nuts so when Jermore offered fish fingers and chips he later rang back to say that the fish fingers contain nuts. We told Jerome that we would have the Duck legs with chips. We received the Duck legs but it was cold and when we cut inside it was pink. We got the chips later. I was unable to sleep during the night because the duck was not digesting. On the morning of 26/12/19, we had severe vomiting and diarrhoea. ", "Due to the problems we suffered our Christmas 2019 was ruined. ", "I am never returning to this restaurant again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r709002464", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Ok food, terrible service ", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "12 September 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you Claire, I am so sorry about this and please be assured that I am addressing it. If you could please contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com I would really appreciate it. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ClaireCur", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r709002464-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband and I were staying at the Novotel for a couple of days and on our first night, decided to have dinner at Bokan. We were shown to a table and were sat for probably about 15 minutes before our order (drink and food) was taken. Around 40 minutes later, we still hadn\u2019t received our drinks, never mind the food. This was despite a couple who came in after us getting both food and drinks long before us. The waiters kept walking past and looking at the table and could clearly see we didn\u2019t have any drinks yet, but did nothing about it. It wasn\u2019t until I got the attention of a female member of staff, who looked to be in charge possibly and mentioned it to her that something started to be done. It was however, an hour, before we even got our drinks and then eventually our food came out. We were charged a \u00a37.25 service charge, which seemed excessive seeing as it took so long to get anything to eat or drink. When the food arrived, it was ok but nothing special and certainly not worth the wait. I wouldn\u2019t recommend this place, we certainly weren\u2019t made to feel very welcome and nothing was offered as an apology for the poor service. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r736569319", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Beautiful restaurant and staff apart of the event manager", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "3 January 2020", "answer_text": ["Thanks Gabriele N for sharing your feedback about your business lunch. I am so sorry to read about the issues with the Events Manager and please be assured that this is not the normal feedback we receive and of course I will address it. However I am delighted that you really enjoyed your lunch in Bokan and the staff were amazing. I do hope we can welcome you back soon. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Gabriel\u0117 N", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r736569319-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Came for business lunch. All the staff were amazing, but very poor communication between the events manager and waitress. The events manager told us that we are not able to change the pre-order, but at the end of the day, the waiter changed without any problems. Also, it took a lot of time to organize because the events manager was super slow and not really friendly."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r735357099", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfection as usual", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "29 December 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow, that a beautiful review marie072758 and of course we are thrilled that it was magnificent as expected. Guillaume really is delivering some amazing dishes and of course I am thrilled that Florian gave you a great welcome as our new Restaurant Manager. We are really looking forward to welcoming you back in 2020. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Marie072758", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r735357099-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This was my third time at Bokan and as expected it was magnificent! To the person who welcomes you yo the last spoon of desert everything is exceptional! Every time I go I discover new mix of flavours that I would never imagine could go so well together! It\u2019s always a delight to the palate and the eyes! Again my compliment to Chef Guillaume and this time a very big thank you to the new Manager of the restaurant Florian who gave us a proper welcome! Can\u2019t wait to go again definitely one of my favourite place in London!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r725727587", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delicious food, free flowing Prosecco and super friendly service", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "11 November 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much DoraexploraUK for this fabulous 5 star review about your wonderful brunch on Saturday, I am thrilled that you enjoyed it so much. I am pleased to read how much you enjoyed the atmosphere in the bar afterwards too. Looking forward to seeing you again soon. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "DoraexploraUK", "reviewer_origin": ["Woking, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "93"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "40"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r725727587-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a wonderful brunch on Saturday. Amazing views across London and lovely atmosphere. Super friendly team who served us and made us feel very welcome. ", "The food was delicious, the Prosecco was free flowing and a high quality. Fun atmosphere in the bar afterwards too. ", "Will definitely be going back! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r709189889", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Superb food and service", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "12 September 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow Kirbs1, thank you so much for your 5 star review and your fantastic experience in Bokan. We are thrilled to read it and share it with the talent, especially of course my Executive Chef. I love the John Dory and when I had it, it was cooked to perfection. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "kirbs1", "reviewer_origin": ["norwich"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r709189889-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Fantastic view over London. Service was excellent from start to finish and the food was exceptional. So much so I sought out the head chef to thank him. The John Dory was the best I've ever had. Faultless throughout."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r708642279", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Good view, bad service", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "10 September 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review. I am so sad and disappointed with your feedback, I am so sorry. I would really appreciate it if you could contact me directly at your convenience to discuss this further. My e-mail is h9057-gm@accor.com. Many thanks and I look forward to hearing from you. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "danielcO2200BQ", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r708642279-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had really bad service, change of courses took a really long time. Some of waiters speak English inseparably, so we struggled to understand them sometimes. One Polish waiter was like from distant village asking us \u201cAre you okay now?\u201d, \u201cyou didn\u2019t like the food?\u201d when I didn\u2019t finish it. This kind of level would be acceptable in road cafe in Belarus but not on rooftop restaurant in London. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r711891680", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect brunch", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "22 September 2019", "answer_text": ["We absolutely love your \"Perfect Brunch\" review about your recent experience with us at the weekend. I am so pleased that you enjoyed your time with us so much and we certainly never like to see a glass empty during bottomless brunch. So glad you saw us on Masterchef and we did not disappoint you. I really hope we can welcome you back in the future. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Londoner016", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "293"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "265"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r711891680-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Thank you so much to the lovely staff at Bokan for hosting us for our brunch yesterday. You might have seen this restaurant featured on Celebrity Masterchef recently and it lived up to the exceptionally high standard of providing quality food and service. We had the bottomless prosecco brunch and not once did we need to ask to be topped up. We were given a table with a five star view of the city of London, really beautiful. For starters I had salmon with steamed hen eggs and it was absolutely delicious. My wife had a tuna starter which she loved. The next course was sirloin cooked to tender perfection on the Josper grill. Fabulous. The plum dessert didn't disappoint either. The service was excellent and we would highly recommend this restaurant for brunch on a sunny day. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r714338330", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delicious food, beautiful views and perfect service", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "30 September 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow, thank you for sharing your amazing experience in Bokan 37. We are thrilled to read how much you enjoyed your time and how well Katherine looked after you. We are really looking forward to welcoming you back soon MichelleD1331. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MichelleD1331", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r714338330-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to Bokan for dinner on a Monday evening as a bit of a last minute celebration. We ordered the lamb and the duck. The mains were both delicious and full of flavour. We had assistance choosing the best red wines to go with our meals which was fantastic. We were served by Katherine who was wonderful and friendly and described what all the foods were. We will definitely return. The decor is fab and the views are great. Can\u2019t fault it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r718762502", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A piece of heaven in london!", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "16 October 2019", "answer_text": ["Oh Lorenzo we just love your title of the review and Bokan is a piece of heaven in London. We are all thrilled that you loved your time with us so much and of course the amazing views. We can't wait to welcome you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lorenzoottaviani92", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r718762502-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["When i saw for the first time this pub/restaurant i have been shocked because there is an amazing view all around it. You can we london and it is really amazing the view.", "Speaking about the inside is very well and nice furnished, really nice style.", "If i want to make a nice impression with someone bokan is always the perfect choice.", "Lorenzo"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r713635787", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing celebration of wedding anniversary", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "28 September 2019", "answer_text": ["We absolutely love your 5 star review P5381BS thank you so much. I am delighted that you chose us to celebrate your wedding anniversary and of course the surprise cake at the end to top your perfect evening off. Constantin is thrilled with his personal mention and I am delighted he looked after you so well. I hope we can welcome you back soon. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "_P5831BS", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r713635787-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I chose this restaurant to celebrate our 3 years wedding anniversary with my husband.", "I have never been there before, but I knew that it was a good choice once I saw the amazing view of London.", "The food was well cooked and delicious. We were served amuse bouche and warm bread with butter, which was a nice touch to start our meal.", "The portions were a bit small, but this is to be expected in this kind of restaurants.", "Now, our waiter, Konstantin was always friendly and made sure that we had a pleasant and unique experience. At the end, there was a surprise, a chocolate cake with the message \"Happy Anniversary\", which was the perfect way to finish this meal and experience.", "I totally reccomend this restaurant, especially for special occasions. Upstairs there is a bar with the same views, but we did not visit it this time."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r723759798", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Service awful, food OK, views fantastic", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "4 November 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you GabrielePan for your review. I have responded on your google and other trip advisor review asking you to contact me directly with regards to the issues you had so I can try to address them. I do hope that you will do this on h9057-gm@accor.com. I look forward to hearing from you. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GabrielePan", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r723759798-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were kept waiting for an hour for a table although we had a reservation and stayed in the hotel. Coco, who appeared to be in charge of table organisation was unapologetic and patronising. There wasn\u2019t enough staff to be attentive and alert. The food was good although the price had raised our expectations, which were not entirely met. I would give Bokan restaurant a miss, the bar and terrace are great."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r725636521", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful views, food and service", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "11 November 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow, what a beautiful review about your Brunch experience at Bokan, thank you NellyBolo for sharing this. We try very hard to make sure that your glass is never empty :). We look forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "NellyBolo", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r725636521-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The views at Bokan 37 were fantastic and we were lucky to have clear, sunny weather with lovely views over the London and the Thames. The set menu with unlimited prosecco was good value, with the warm waiting staff refusing to let your glass get anywhere near empty. ", "To round off a birthday celebration I was presented with a gorgeous mini cake with chocolates for the four of us, which was a lovely surprise organised by my friends.", "I would definitely revisit; well recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r706150210", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Constantin was a lovely waiter!", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "3 September 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much helloitsniv for sharing your recent experience with us at Bokan. We love your feedback about Constantin who is very precious to us and he is thrilled with his personal mention. I hope we can welcome you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "HonestreviewerN", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r706150210-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Had the pleasure of Constantin as our waiter. It was friend\u2019s birthday so we celebrated in great company. Price of the food is a bit high but service and view is good"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r698156302", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Amazing views of London", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "12 August 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your lovely review about your experience in Bokan and I am so glad to read how much you enjoyed it. I hope we can welcome you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "noxinpres", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "83"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r698156302-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This is gem in the Docklands area of London. With great food, and amazing views of London. My only negative is the food portions are very small, however the quality and atmosphere makes up for this."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r700383701", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful View, Beautiful Food", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "18 August 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow, that a stunning review for your recent experience in Bokan. We are just delighted to read how much you enjoyed celebrating your partners birthday with us. We are really looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LynsFrostee", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "374"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "175"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r700383701-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Took my partner here for his birthday as he loves a meal with a gorgeous view and Bokan did not disappoint. Im not sure why this restaurant is not more widely known as it is far superior in terms of the stunning view to many of the central restaurants in the city such as those based at the Shard.", "The food was delicious and the staff were very accommodating without being too much. It's not a cheap venue but if you're looking for somewhere for a special night out Bokan is 100% the place to go to."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r701546248", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent meal, great wine", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "21 August 2019", "answer_text": ["wow, THANK you so much Jimbhai for taking the time to share your fabulous experience you had at Bokan. The wild boar has just come on the menu and we are really getting rave reviews about it. Nelson is absolutely thrilled with his personal mention and he is so passionate about his wines and can be daring at times which enhances the whole tasting menu experience. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon and we are looking forward to it. Thank you so much again. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jimbhai", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "26"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r701546248-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We treated ourselves to a big Saturday night dinner at Bokan and it didn\u2019t disappoint. We had the tasting menu which was a foodies delight with lots if high notes including a wild boar and fig main which stole the show. A word about the wine though. Nelson the sommelier is an absolute star. I honestly can\u2019t recall a better matched wine list for a tasting menu. And by Saturday night London standards it was fairly priced. What else? There\u2019s great live music, a lively bar and terrace for drinks beforehand and of course the amazing view. Go on, treat yourself!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r702922271", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Really Bad Customer Service!", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "25 August 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review and I am sorry about the issues you had. We do not have a strict dress policy however we do advise on all of our booking sites about flip flops. There are a number of reasons that we have this policy in place and I would really appreciate the opportunity to discuss them with you further. Please e-mail me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "marcotU4798IW", "reviewer_origin": ["Laax, Switzerland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r702922271-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Absolutely terrible and unfriendly Service at the Bokan. Reserved weeks in advance for my birthday dinner and as it was in the middle of summer and 34 degrees our entire party was not let in because I was wearing sandals in the 34 degree summer heat! I have spent a lot of money at this place before and there was many other people wearing sandals in the 34 degree heat. They were very unfriendly about it and just told me I have to go; will never go there again!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r703306799", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "View to die for", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "26 August 2019", "answer_text": ["We love your 5 star review Paul S, thank you so much for sharing your Bokan experience. I love the Butchers and Cheese selection, what a great choice. The views of course are stunning especially at sunset. We are looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Paul S", "reviewer_origin": ["Warrington, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "511"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "181"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r703306799-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Called in without booking as residents of the Novotel expecting to be declined but to our surprise a delightful maitre d showed us to a table with a terrific view of the Thames.", "We ordered the butchers and cheese selection and the Chenin Blanc to accompany. All exceptional quality, if a little on the expensive side, but the view and the live music more than made up for this."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r696071342", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Bokan - Incredible dinner overlooking London", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "6 August 2019", "answer_text": ["We just love that we exceeded your expectations during your recent visit to Bokan. From the warm welcome you got from our welcomer's to the amazing views and of course the fabulous food. The foie gras is a favourite of mine and I am so glad you enjoyed this. We are all really looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Gyrithe K", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "705"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r696071342-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Dinner at Bokan did exceed my expectations! On our arrival the staff greet us with such a warm welcome. We were lucky to be seated by the window, overlooking London and the city lights! Incredible menu options, but I decided trying the foie grass as starter, then the stone bass for main! Impeccable service, and super friendly staff!", "Definitely recommended!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r704749436", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Brilliant food, 1 let down ", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "30 August 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much Lewdini for taking the time to share your experience at Bokan. I am pleased with your feedback about the quality of the food but I am obviously frustrated with the service issues. Whilst this is not an excuse I investigated who it was that looked after you and funnily enough it was her last shift with us and I feel really disappointed in her that she would choose to behave like this. I do hope you will come back and see us again soon and please let me know if you are returning on h9057-gm@accor.com so I can really look after you personally. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lewdini", "reviewer_origin": ["Liverpool, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r704749436-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Food was Delicious, pigeon best I\u2019ve had and ribeye cooked perfectly. We were sat 15 minutes after time allotted but was no issue as we had a drink in bar. The only downside that stopped me from giving 5 star was the wait at bar (although I understood it was busy and mainly time consuming cocktails) and the poor service in the restaurant, while it seemed most of the servers were attentive and lovely our waitress openly complained about her number of tables (just 4) and treated the evening with a distain for her job that reflected in her lack of attentiveness and poor attitude to that table (her general demeanour was of one who didn\u2019t care of those she served, 35 minutes to order food, no drinks offered throughout the evening and when we did eventually order drinks we had to ask another waitress to search for them, which she was prompt in doing) apart from feeling like this one waitress didn\u2019t really want to be there our evening was great. We left the restaurant and enjoyed more drinks in the bar "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r704258967", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Romantic night out", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "29 August 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much Michael A for this fabulous 5 star review and I am so thrilled you enjoyed your time with us so much you are coming back for your anniversary., Emmanuel is so happy with his personal mention and he will be rewarded and recognised for this! We are looking forward to welcoming you back. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Micheal A", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r704258967-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I was at bokan restaurant (Novotel, canary wharf), earlier this month to celebrate my wife's birthday. The food and drinks are nice and not expensive.", "The icing on the cake of our trip was pictures taken at bokan 39(an open bar on the 39th floor with an amazing view of London.", "I and my wife would have missed the opportunity of taking pictures and having the amazing view of London which bokan 39 offers, if not for the friendly and professional security manager(Emmanuel). He was the one that drew our attention to the existence of bokan 39 and what it offers.", "I and my wife hopes to visit bokan next month during our wedding anniversary."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r705902676", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Endroit incontournable ", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "3 September 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow, we love your 5 star review ophvn and your beautiful words about keeping this moment in Bokan for a long time has warmed my heart. Corentin is of course thrilled with his personal mention, he is very special to us in Bokan. I hope we can welcome you back to Bokan for another memorable experience soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ophvn", "reviewer_origin": ["Paris, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r705902676-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Amazing restaurant with an incredible view on all the London city. It was a magical moment with the sunset.", "The food was really nice and delicat, but there are not many vegetarian choices...", "We will keep this moment at Bokan for a long time, for sure!", "Thanks to Corentin for his welcome and his amazing kindness!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r686956996", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Incredible experience!", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "5 July 2019", "answer_text": ["Thanks so much Delphine P for this amazing review about your incredible experience at Bokan. Guillaume is thrilled that you enjoyed the food so much especially the duck which is really unusual yet goes so well and of course the lemon tart is stunning. We can't wait to welcome you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Delphine P", "reviewer_origin": ["Saint-Medard-en-Jalles, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r686956996-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Incredible experience! I came a few weeks ago with my husband for our anniversary. Very impressed by the quality of the dishes, the prawn starter and the duck for main was stunning, very tasty and unusual..! The lemon tart was also delicious. Many thanks to Guillaume for the outstanding service, he was very knowledgeable and brought us an anniversary plate. One of the best dinner we\u2019ve never had. Definitely worth it. I will come back soon, thank you again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r686532623", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Loved It!", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "3 July 2019", "answer_text": ["We are thrilled with our 5 star review LaBionda1234 and also to hear that this is not your first time with us at Bokan and I am sure it will not be your last. Jerome of course is delighted with his personal mention, thanks for this, he sets an example to his team. Looking forward to seeing you on your next visit. Jacqui, Jerome and The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LaBionda1234", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r686532623-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I always come here with my colleagues and a part from the view which is magnificent, we always experience a great service. A personal note to Jerome who is always very friendly and helpful :)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r686502443", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing food and very good service", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "3 July 2019", "answer_text": ["we are so thrilled Bernardothe that you took up your friends recommendation to come and visit us in Bokan after a long week at work and we were the perfect end to your week. I hope we can welcome you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ornella Y", "reviewer_origin": ["Amsterdam, The Netherlands"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r686502443-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I came to have a dinner after a long week of work in London. Some friends recommanded Bokan to me. Excellent customer service. I had starter, main course and dessert with wine to pair with each courses. Very impressed by the service, very attentive and friendly. The food was tasty and well presented. I\u2019ll definitely come back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r696046036", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Brilliant food with the best views of London", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "6 August 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow Darrenhumphries100 we absolutely love your 5 star review, thank you so much for sharing your brilliant experience in Bokan. I am so glad you chose the tasting menu and I would love to know what your facourite dish was as mine is the slow cooked beef short ribs. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon and we are looking forward to it. Thanks again. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "darrenhumphries100", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r696046036-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The chefs tasting menu was absolutely fantastic. The staff where friendly and extremely approachable. If you\u2019re looking for a roof top bar/restaurant with superb views choose Bokan! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r686961789", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Incredible food with a view - the full package!", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "5 July 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow, what a fabulous 5 star review about your brunch with us in Bokan. We are thrilled that you enjoyed it so much and Guillaume is thrilled with your feedback. We can't wait to have you back. Thanks again. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "christabellpidduck", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r686961789-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I tried out the brunch on a sunny Sunday and was bowled over by the level of food and service. Seriously underrated restaurant and tucked out of the way in Canary Wharf, but totally worth a visit. Chef Guillaume is doing something really special up on the 37th floor at B\u014dkan - all three courses were a delight, especially the Josper grilled pork with padron pepper & potato. Can't wait to go back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r688762461", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing dinner, view & service", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "11 July 2019", "answer_text": ["We just love your review CallOnMe. We are thrilled that you enjoyed your experience with us in Bokan and the well balanced flavours of the dishes. I agree our pastry team deliver the most amazing desserts, they are so talented. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CallOnMe", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r688762461-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Very friendly and complete service from start to finish. All the menu is great, very well-balanced flavours and presentation. Desserts were particularly good! Highly enjoyable and relaxed environment."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r688533828", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great views, Great food and great staff", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "10 July 2019", "answer_text": ["We just love your review, thank you so much for sharing this amazing review about your Bokan experience. We loved reading how much you loved the food and of course the great service. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mckie64", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r688533828-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The meal we had was amazing. Although in a rush to see the show the staff were speedy, professional but also relaxed. they made the effort to come and speak to me while my wife used the ladies room. The food is to die for. Similar prices to similar venues I have been to like the shard or Fenchurch in walkie talkie building but the food is ten times better. Could not choose off the menu as it all looked great, when we got our food we just wanted to at each others."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r691855101", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great menu choice, lovely presentation cooked nearly to perfection", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "22 July 2019", "answer_text": ["We really enjoyed reading your review about your experience in Bokan 37. I am sorry that the taste combination didn't work for you on this occasion. However of course we are thrilled that everything was cooked to perfection. Great that you would recommend us and I hope we can welcome you back in the future. Kind regards. Jacqui & The Bokan family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "RobinKClarke", "reviewer_origin": ["Maidenhead, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "62"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r691855101-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I chose king crab / pickles based starter (as did my wife), really enjoyed that. \u00a314 each, not cheep. Mains, my wife had the organic lamb \u00a332, me the Stone bass \u00a329. Both cooked to perfection. However, I fed back to the waiting staff, the odd combination of white coco bean, as a fish-o-holic, always eager to try new combos, I simply didn;'t see the point, didn't work for me. No worries, fish was beautifully cooked so happy to leave the beans (apart from the 3 I tried).", "Our deserts were lovely too. It is expensive, great waiting staff and you can view the kitchen. As a treat, yep, I'd recommend it. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r688789999", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Couldn't get to the roof terrace...", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "11 July 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you Keith W for taking the time to share your experience with regards to Bokan. I am sorry that you were not able to access the roof terrace which had been reserved for a private event. I absolutely take on board your feedback that you should have been advised at reservation stage, please be assured that I will address this. I am so pleased to read your comments about Cristian and you enjoyed your meal. I agree the desserts are stunning :). I do hope we can welcome you back in the future. Kind regards. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Keith W", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "100"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r688789999-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["A week or so ago I booked a table at the restaurant on 37 and was hoping to have a drink on the roof terrace on 39 on this wonderful warm evening. Unfortunately for us the whole terrace had been booked for the evening so we had drinks on floor 38 instead. I had only found this out this morning when the receptionist called to confirm our reservation. This was mentioned on the website but I hadn\u2019t thoroughly checked it. The guy on reception on 38 was very welcoming and perfect for front of house. The bar staff were very friendly and the guy that served our drinks at the table on 38 enjoyed conversation and a joke or two. As we were leaving to go to the restaurant I had half-jokingly asked him whether the tip we gave him included a quick sneak view of the party upstairs he became quite serious and said it was not possible. Maybe I read it wrongly but he seemed a little distant from that moment. At 7pm the restaurant had only 2-3 other tables booked and we were served quickly. Our waiter, Cristian, was a delight. Both the receptionist that called this morning and Cristian checked to see whether there were any allergies and also asked whether it was a special occasion. After choosing our mains and changing one meal there was a slight mix-up. This minor error with our meal choices would have been quickly corrected but we were happy to proceed as presented and the beef and duck choices were delicious as were the desserts. It was a slightly higher price than expected with a main, a side and a dessert each, with just one glass of wine at the table around \u00a360 per head. To me the docklands area has a slightly distant \u2018unreal\u2019 feel to it and there was less interaction with other customers in this establishment than we usually find in The City and West End. This could well change depending on the night and could also be my own personal take on the vibe. I personally love the established feel about more historic areas in London."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r695240732", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Brunch With A View", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "3 August 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much RandomJLondon for sharing your perfect Brunch experience in Bokan 37. We are so pleased that you enjoyed your time with us so much. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon and we are looking forward to it. Many thanks again. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "RandomJLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "141"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "67"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r695240732-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Based in the Canary Wharf Novotel this restaurant is the perfect place to have a relaxed brunch with delicious food and an awesome view. We had the brunch menu but did not opt for the additional bottomless Prosecco for \u00a315. I would recommend this place for a birthday, romantic meal or just a general catch up with friends and family."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r677859623", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A Treat", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "31 May 2019", "answer_text": ["We really enjoyed reading your 5 star review about Bokan. I am so pleased you took the tasting menu which is fabulous. We are so thrilled that you enjoyed your time with us and I hope we can welcome you back in the future. Kind regards. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mark20VT", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r677859623-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Met some friends for dinner and we all tried the tasting menu. It was excellent and complemented the amazing views across London. Could not fault the service and would recommend to anyone wanting something a bit special."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r686501627", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The best", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "3 July 2019", "answer_text": ["WOW, thank you so much for this great 5 star review about your recent experience in Bokan. Myself and the team are thrilled to read how much you enjoyed your time with us and we thank you for sharing. I am sure we will see you again soon and we are looking forward to it. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Smnlove", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r686501627-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["A stunning night with an amazing London view and the best service for dinner - high end wait staff, and top quality food. All beautifully presented and tasty. Thank you chef for your attention and passion."]}
