{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r680366237", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Very Good Dinnnng with a great View", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "10 June 2019", "answer_text": ["We absolutely love your 5 star review Nettantor thank you so much for sharing your Bokan experience. Guillaume and his brigade will be thrilled to read this. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon and we are looking forward to it. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Nettantor", "reviewer_origin": ["Scheiblingkirchen, Austria"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r680366237-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["After a nice afternoon in Greenwich, we had a wonderful dinner in this very nice and beautiful restaurant. We were greeted very nicely and the staff is very helpful and dedicated.", "The food was wonderful and the view from the 37th floor was a dream.", "Any time again. "]}
