{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r685483253", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great View, Food good, 5 star prices with 1 star service ", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "30 June 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you for taking the time to review your experience and I am so sorry that despite us delivering beautiful food with an amazing view we have let you down so badly with the service, we are so sorry. Please be assured that I am dealing with this. I would really appreciate it if you do get the time to contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "M5442ZZmichaeld", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r685483253-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["As loads of people mention, view is excellent. Food was good, chose the tasting menu, 70pp, and the wine pairing 40 pp. One round totally forgot to serve wine, despite waving arms could get no attention, ended up basically having to walk into kitchen to ask for wine to be shouted at \u201cits coming\u201d no apology, table behind kicked off for same reason shoddy service and they called Security, crazy. Took service off bill that was all. "]}
