{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r680295037", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a fantastic view", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "9 June 2019", "answer_text": ["We are thrilled Susieprice2614 that you enjoyed drinks in Bokan and of course the amazing views. We can't wait to see you again soon. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "susieprice2614", "reviewer_origin": ["Epsom, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r680295037-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Actually only had drinks in the bar - but what a fantastic roof top - 39 floors up in the open. Wonderful views of the Thames and landmarks."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r686280431", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Nice view!", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "3 July 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for taking the time to review your experience in Bokan, we are disappointed that we let you down with only a 2 star review. I would appreciate it if you would contact me directly to discuss your issues so we can address why the score was so low. My e-mail is h9057-gm@accor.com. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Nellytrips", "reviewer_origin": ["Hasselt, Belgium"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "102"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r686280431-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had dinner in this restaurant.", "The view is amazing, we were lucky to have our table at the window.", "We arrived a little early and we asked for a apero in the rooftop bar! We had to go to our table and got our cocktail and also imediately our food. We didn\u2019t had the time to enjoy our apero first, and we had enough time, the food was ok. It looked beautiful, but the Taste was a little less spicy.", "The waiter asked every time if we wanted more water/wine/dessert/coffee... ", "friendly but also like he wanted to sell more and more.... ", "I didn\u2019t like the dessert, the chocomouse was very bitter. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r677837959", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "AMAZING DINNER", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "31 May 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow, thank you so much Cremo89 for your fabulous 5 star review with regards to your recent visit to Bokan. We are thrilled that from the moment you walked in everything was perfect. We can't wait to welcome you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Cremo89", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r677837959-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked here for a special occasion and since the moment we walked in, everything has been perfect: staff is professional, polite and friendly. Delicious cocktails and amazing food. Superlative views.", "We will definitely come back."]}
