{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r673267390", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous time at Bokan", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "11 May 2019", "answer_text": ["We are delighted Kazach7 that you enjoyed your wonderful experience with us at Bokan. One of our values is for all of our guests to feel welcome so I am particularly pleased with that feedback but of course all of it is wonderful. I am sure we will be seeing you again soon and we are looking forward to this. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Kazach7", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r673267390-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a wonderful time at Bokan. Not only were the views over London spectacular but the staff were incredibly helpful and friendly. We were made to feel welcome and valued, and nothing was too much trouble. We\u2019ll definitely be back."]}
