{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r661713277", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Tasting menu not so great", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "27 March 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you 2christiant for taking the time to share your feedback with us about your recent experience in Bokan. I am glad that you enjoyed the location and the roof top bar however I am so sorry that you found our tasting menu not so great. This is not the normal feedback we get and I am really sad about this. If you are planning to return please contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com to arrange your visit so I can personally take care of you. I hope we have the opportunity to welcome you back. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "2christiant", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r661713277-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife and I went for our anniversary as a recommendation from a work. Colleague.", "I have to say the place was perfect for the occasion very friendly staff and good live music with a roof garden at the 39th floor, everything till there was great. Now comes the menu a la carte or the \u00a370 pp tasting menu on paper looked appealing and decided to go for the tasting menu option. Big mistake there was no a single item that we can say it was enjoyable where dishes we so over power by the 50% French liquor that killed everything to very blunt slow cooked beef..", "Very desappointing "]}
