{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r658490002", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Brilliant Brunch with fizz", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "14 March 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much KernowBoys for sharing your feedback about your Sunday Brunch at Bokan 37 Restaurant. We are so pleased that you read that it was an absolutely amazing experience and service, and of course our beautiful interior design and stunning views of London. Your feedback about the team really makes us very proud and Deborah is thrilled with her personal mention, and of course will be rewarded for this. We are looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Louisa & The Bokan Family. "], "reviewer_pseudo": "kernowtraveller50", "reviewer_origin": ["Redruth, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "263"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "135"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r658490002-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["First time here for us all for Sunday Brunch with the optional bottomless Prosecco. Absolutely amazing experience and service. Beautiful decor and views of London. Would have enjoyed the roof top terrace had it not been for the very high winds.", "Our waitress, Deborah? Was outstanding and made us feel special. She was a delight. The food was absolutely wonderful and we totally worth the price, as was the bottomless Prosecco. ", "Highly recommend "]}
