{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r651275793", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect birthday dinner", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "10 February 2019", "answer_text": ["We are so happy that you chose Bokan to celebrate such a special birthday and of course we are thrilled that you enjoyed our vegan tasting menu so much. The views are stunning and so glad you got a lovely table by the window so you could enjoy them. I will certainly look into the issues with the cocktails. I hope you will come back and see us soon. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "hayleydb32", "reviewer_origin": ["Surrey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "71"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r651275793-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My boyfriend took me here for my 21st dinner and we both had the vegan tasting menu. The food was incredible and we were sat at a window table which gave us a stunning view of the city. ", "The staff were all friendly. ", "The cocktails at the bar were great but the ones at dinner were the same price and a lot smaller so felt a bit ripped off there. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r651069439", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The best rooftop bar in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "9 February 2019", "answer_text": ["We love your review Keti D, thank you so much for taking the time to share your amazing experience with us. Veni is thrilled with her personal mention and of course will be rewarded for this. We are all looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Keti D", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r651069439-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great atmosphere and stunning view! Best place for drinks and quick food in Canary Wharf. Really pleased by the way a member of staff - Veni took care of us last night when I had my birthday celebration. She was constantly checking on us and making sure that we had everything that we need. I'll definitely continue visiting this place."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r651986261", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful views, beautiful food", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "13 February 2019", "answer_text": ["We are thrilled Debra with your fabulous feedback about your stay with us and your experience in Bokan. I am so glad to hear how much you enjoyed your time with us. I hope we can welcome you back in the future, next time you are in London. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Debra P", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r651986261-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were staying in the hotel and requested a table in the restaurant with a view and although couldnt be guaranteed, we were not disappointed when we arrived, just wow! Food was amazing and the restaurant had a real buzz about it and although a bit chilly in November the rooftop bar is a nice touch."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r652215729", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful food and stunning views", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "13 February 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow Kirstie, the best meal you have ever had is just amazing to hear, thank you so much for this. The views are stunning and when you match this with great food, great singing and great service, what more could you ask for. Looking forward to seeing you again soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Kirstie A", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r652215729-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Food was delicious and very good quality. Probably the best meal I have ever had! The views were amazing, overlooking central London. Great atmosphere with live singing. Overall, a wonderful experience!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r651975618", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fancy Bar wirh great view London Downtown", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "13 February 2019", "answer_text": ["We are so pleased to hear that you end your colleagues enjoyed your time with us in Bokan, thanks for sharing the experience. Of course your feedback about my team really makes me so proud and we still delivered great service even when we get so busy. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon. Kind regards. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "666gerarde", "reviewer_origin": ["Muhltal, Germany"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r651975618-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["In the 38th and 39th floor of the Novotel hotel we had a really good evening with our colleagues. You can book a separate area for ca. 20 people. On the 38th floor there is the open roof top bar with a fantastic view of the coty of London. On the 38th floor you have the main bar area. We had wine and fingerfood. Both were really good. The team was nice. Ibhad the feeling in the peak time of the evening they had to cover quite a lot of guests, but were never stressed and alway friendly. Unfortunately they did not have one type of beer onntap, but I can recommend the IPA. Summary: fancy bar with a full panoramic view. Reservation needed."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r658334485", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Really poor service", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "13 March 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you Noubliepas for taking the time to share with us your experience and of course I am so sad we let you down with regards to the cooking of your steak and handling of your feedback on the night. Please be assured that I will be addressing this with the team. As you have mentioned all your other experiences have been amazing at Bokan, so if you would give us another chance and would return to Bokan 37 Restaurant, please contact me directly so I can personally look after your booking with us. We hope that we can welcome you back very soon. ", "Kind regards. Louisa Daxer Robbins - Operations Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Noubliepas", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r658334485-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Appalling service here tonight. A medium steak came well done, sides came almost at the end of the meal, no apology, and the extremely rude manager decided to have a go at the kitchen staff in front of us. A real pity as all my other experiences here have been amazing."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r653328577", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a view!", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "18 February 2019", "answer_text": ["We love your 5 star review KandM881, thanks so much for sharing. Our Bokan team are thrilled with your feedback and we are really looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Kind regards. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "KandM881", "reviewer_origin": ["Luton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r653328577-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This is a great restaurant with a fantastic view over the city. Stunning. The food and service were exceptional. Highly recommended. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r654068754", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic views ", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "22 February 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you Matthewwalker2291 for this fabulous 5 star review, we love it. We are thrilled that you found our staff fantastic, and of course the views and our new cocktail menu. Looking forward to seeing you again soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Matthewwalker2291", "reviewer_origin": ["New Quay, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "65"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "56"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r654068754-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Came here for a couple of drinks whilst visiting friends in London. ", "Phoned to book a table for 10pm. Arrived to a table reserved in the window with fantastic views over London. ", "The staff were brilliant. Views incredible. Vast choice of drinks. ", "Will return. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r656959329", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Breakfast meeting ", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "7 March 2019", "answer_text": ["Thanks so much Spiroy for sharing your feedback about your breakfast meeting in Bokan. We are so pleased that you enjoyed it and of course are stunning views of London. I hope we can welcome you back in the future. Kind regards. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "spiroy", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "38"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r656959329-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Good service. Quality and diversified buffet breakfast. Orders come quickly. The real treat are the stunning views of London. Quite breathtaking. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r655347191", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A hidden gem", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "28 February 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much cdw85 for your 5 star review and I am delighted that this was your 2nd time with us and we did not disappoint :). Saturdays are getting busy so thrilled that you reserved in advance to make sure you got a great table with our great views and lucky you had some nice weather for the rooftop. I am sure we will be welcoming you back again soon in Bokan. Kind regards. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "cdw85", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r655347191-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["It was the second time I\u2019ve been here, we booked a table 2 weeks in advance As Saturdays can get busy. We arrived with no problems - shown to our seats and given a drinks menu, we took our drinks up on the rooftop where we got a table with an amazing view and enjoyed a lovely afternoon in the sun sipping cocktails. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r642843267", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "New Year's Eve Dinner", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "1 January 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow Ismael, thank you so much for this amazing feedback and of course our 5 star rating. I am so delighted to read how much you enjoyed spending your New Year's Eve with us at Bokan. Rita and Veni are just thrilled with their personal mention, I am so proud of them and all of the team who worked so hard to make sure everyone enjoyed themselves. I was here too on New Year's Eve and I agree that the menu Aurelie and her team put together was awesome. We are looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Many thanks again for sharing your experience. Kind regards. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ismael G", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r642843267-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Since the first moment you take the lift to go up until 37th floor with an exclusive lift separated from hotel lobby, until you sit in your table with full views of Central London, there are a lot of pleased and comfortable moments.", "Rita & Veni, at the reception, are two lovely ladies members of the Team who make your welcome at the restaurant one of the most kind moments.", "What else? Dinner in New Year's Eve was awesome ( some pictures attached ), where chefs make an amazing mix of flavors, textures & elegant presentations on plates as you only see in best world restaurants.", "This has been the second time we have booked in B\u00f5kan but will not be the last. Totally recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r642086620", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Great cocktails - terrible service", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "28 December 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you Michelle F for taking the time to share with us your experience and of course I am so sad we let you down with regards to the service. Please be assured that I will be addressing this with the team. If you would give us another chance and would return to Bokan 38, please contact me directly so I can personally look after your booking with us. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Michelle F", "reviewer_origin": ["Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "11"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r642086620-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This bar has an amazing view, great cocktails and good bar snacks but the service was awful! We ordered snacks and a bottle of champagne to celebrate a special occasion. After about 40 minutes we asked about our order and several people can around making excuses about a problem with their \u201csystem\u201d. We asked for the manager - he never came and finally our order arrived with the waitress telling us they could comp our cheese plate ..... still no one ever came back to check on us or ask if we had everything! Just terrible service and poor management."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r644839712", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Vaida", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "9 January 2019", "answer_text": ["We all absolutely love your review and of course the 5 star rating about your night in Bokan. Antonella and Angelita are thrilled with their personal mention and will be rewarded and recognised for this. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "tdirse", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r644839712-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great service, amazing vibe, thanks to Antoneiia! And Angelita! - for making it a NIGHT ", "Hope Tomas had the blasting birthday night \u2665\ufe0f"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r642674483", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Not so Happy New Year!", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "31 December 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you Reni for letting us know about these issues you experienced. I am so sorry that we let you down and of course I really would like to investigate this further for you. If you could please contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com I would very much appreciate this. I look forward to hearing from you. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Reni R", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r642674483-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["If I could give this place less than 1 star, I would. They completely ruined my New Year's celebration by miss-advertising their venue. ", "We emailed them on Friday 28th December to simply enquire if they had more tickets available (No expectations as we know how busy this night is, and it was lastminute.com). Failing to respond within 24 hours (which is quite a reasonable expectation for such business) we decided to call instead. Upon speaking to one of their unqualified staff, they advised us that walk-ins will be available all night upon payment of \u00a350 per person at the door. This does not secure any tables which was fine for us as we only wanted to enjoy a drink and watch the fireworks from up high. We were pretty happy with this result! ", "To our surprise, today we receive a response to our email (4 days later - excellent customer service I must say) informing us that they are fully booked for the night, but hope to see us another time. How nice of them! ", "As we live in the area we took it upon ourselves to go there personally today and hoped that this will be somehow resolved as they have provided such bad service. Yet again, we were even more disappointed to see that 1st, the manager who responded to our email was so busy she could not take 5 minutes of her time to talk to us about this. 2nd, 'in their defence' (their words, not mine) the manager works office hours and was not there when we called on the weekend, so I guess misinforming clients should be totally acceptable, especially when it comes to one of the busiest nights of the year when all everyone wants is to celebrate somewhere special. ", "I was shocked to see such bad level of management and customer service from such a nice establishment. I have been to Bokan many times before this, and have personally recommended it to many of my friends as probably the best rooftop bar in London, but I am sorry to say that I will not longer be doing that. To see a manager who would leave their staff to deal with a problem without facing it professionally, and allow others to take blame for their own poor service. Astonishing. Happy New Year Bokan!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r643260130", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a gem!", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "3 January 2019", "answer_text": ["From everyone in Bokan and especially Antonella, thank you so much for sharing this amazing 5 star review, we are thrilled. I am so glad that you ended your holiday with us in Bokan and you enjoyed it so much. I hope next time in London you come back and visit us. Many thanks again. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lkwayy", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r643260130-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Last night in London and this was the place we chose to do dinner and drinks. Antonella, our waitress was absolutely amazing :) wonderful customer service, great food and spectacular views! An amazing way to end a great holiday."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r650917623", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Great ambience, good food, terrible waiters, super long waiting time", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "8 February 2019", "answer_text": ["Thank you Twettiseek for your feedback, I am so sorry we have let you down. I would like the opportunity to investigate this further and would need some details from you with regards to when you visited us. If you could contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com I would really appreciate it. Many thanks and I look forward to hearing from you. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - Bokan General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Twettiseek", "reviewer_origin": ["London, England"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "78"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r650917623-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We celebrated a 50th birthday with 6 people at Bokan. While the food was generally very good and well presented on the plate, the service was absolutely terrible. The staff was not trained and inattentive. When we asked for the cocktail list, it took forever to arrive, and the waiter could not explain the cocktails and had to get another member of the bar staff. The same happened with the wine menu. Likewise, the waiters were unable to explain certain items on the dinner menu, i.e. what they were or how they were prepared. Everything took an absolutely extraordinary amount of time to arrive. We had endless wait times between courses and long periods with empty drinks. It was very hard to track down the waiters for anything, and we had to physically get up twice to grab one to place an order. It was exhausting and distracting, bringing the mood down. ", "We were also not served at the same time, i.e. some of us were sitting in front of their rapidly cooling main course while others hadn't received theirs yet. The mashed potatoes that were meant to come with my steak arrived only after I was finished. The same happened to some of our party as well, where side dishes were forgotten or arrived too late. ", "The food was good, but not outstanding. The \"petit fours\" that came after dessert, were not what we expected: they included cheap tasting jellied sugar candy and by no means \"petit fours,\" as in \u201cdelicate pastry\u201d. I would not recommend the \u201cbirthday cake\u201d that we had pre-ordered. It was not a cake in any sense of the word, but a moussey fluffy mass on a hard crust. It was impossible to cut and portion and unpleasant to eat. We left it there despite having paid around \u00a350 in advance. ", "I\u2019ve heard the same review from friends who, like us, also live in Canary Wharf around the corner from the restaurant. We could be regulars, but I\u2019m worried to go back and have the same experience. This area is in dire need of some outstanding restaurants, and it would be good if Bokan cleaned up their act and invested in better service staff. The ambience and d\u00e9cor are great, very New York. We just need some New York style waiters. There, you\u2019d get served a 3-course meal and are in and out in 1 hour..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r644099624", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great view and great food", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "6 January 2019", "answer_text": ["Wow Ricardo, we are so thrilled to read your review about your recent experience with us, thank you for sharing. The Bokan team are so proud to read how much you enjoyed not only the amazing views but of course the service and the food from Aurelie and her Team. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon and we are looking forward to it. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ricardo_Marques", "reviewer_origin": ["Odivelas, Portugal"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "243"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "89"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r644099624-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Restaurant located on the top floors of Novotel Canary Wharf. The decoration is modern and the views of London are amazing. The service was very nice and the food excellent."]}
