{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r638725337", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday Celebration", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "11 December 2018", "answer_text": ["We are just thrilled to read this fabulous 5 star review, thanks so much Marina for taking the time to share this. Our views are amazing and even in the winter the heated terrace is perfect to see the sights of London. Of course we love that you enjoyed our warm and welcoming atmosphere. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon. Many thanks again. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "marina_cappuccino", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r638725337-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What an amazing restaurant! Bokan has a very warm and welcoming atmosphere and the entire staff is very courteous. Not to mention that the views are superb! Since the restaurant is in Canary Wharf, you have an astonishing outlook of the entire London area. They even have an outdoor terrace, that is well-heated, where you can enjoy a few drinks. Being there for my birthday, I felt very spoiled. The food was prepared very tasty and there was attention paid to the aesthetic of the dishes."]}
