{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r638745018", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Awful experience!", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "11 December 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you Anna for your review, I am of course so sorry about this. I would really appreciate it if you could contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com so I can discuss this further with you. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Anna H", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r638745018-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We spent a girls weekend in London and booked this restaurant as it looked amazing from the photos but we were very disappointed!", "It was like a marathon, the minute we sat down everything was rushed and we didn't have time to relax or enjoy our food or drinks. We ordered cocktails to start our evening but those didn't arrive until after our starter so we had no drinks with our started. We then finally received the cocktails with our main but since we prefered to drink wine with the main we had to chuck down our cocktails and quickly order the wine before we finished our main. We felt all so sick after our food because everything was rushed and we had no time to diggest or even enjoy our food.", "The staff was rude to us as well. We asked two people if they could take a photo of us but they both turned us down very rudely because they didn't have time. At least they could have said sorry in a friendly tone that they don't have time but they amlost shouted at us for asking the. ", "When we confronted our waiter Florian and told him that everything is too fast and that we're having a bad time he just ignored us and told us yes the service needs to be fast and then he left as he didn't like the confrontation.", "If your table tells you that they're having a bas time then as a good waitor you should at least try and change things, but he didn't.", "So we just decided not to take desert and just leave as it was just so horrible.", "Such a shame because it's such a beautiful place but I guess they didn't want us there ...", "Carole"]}
