{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r639846205", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Mixed bag", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "16 December 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you for choosing to visit Bokan W6327VDandrewh. Whilst it is fantastic to hear that overall you loved our great music, cocktails and staff, we're sorry to hear that you didn't enjoy our tasting menu and we appreciate your feedback regarding this.", "Please let us know, next time you visit Bokan so we can recommend some dishes for you.", "Warm regards,", "Sarah & the Bokan team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "W6327VDandrewh", "reviewer_origin": ["Hornchurch, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "32"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r639846205-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great music, great cocktails and great venue....shame it was let down by the food. We went for the tasting menu, which really didn't hit the spot. Very well presented but lacked depth in flavour and some odd combinations which just didn't work for me. The beautifully smoked salmon was the stand out dish though. Subtle and uniquely beautiful. ", "I have to add that all the waiting staff were so attentive, friendly and unpretentious which was really nice. Will definitely come back but not for the tasting menu."]}
