{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r633413802", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delicious food", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "14 November 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much Valerie for taking the time to share your Bokan experience with us. We are thrilled to read how much you enjoyed it and of course the live music with Kieron is fantastic and really does add to the ambience of the evening. I have not tried that dessert as yet but you have made my mouth water this morning and I will certainly be asking for it next time too. We are looking forward to welcoming you back soon. any thanks again. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "valerie0410", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "33"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r633413802-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We dined at Bokan and we had an amazing time.", "Food is great, there was live music which added a nice ambiance.", "I had the best dessert ever : meringue, banana, avocado, coconut and tequila sorbet. Wow !!", "The place is cool, the view over London is beautiful and the waiters are lovely.", "I would definitely go back to this restaurant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r635055730", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Amazing venue and great view.. service inconsistent", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "22 November 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you Edwina for sharing your thoughts and feedback about your recent experience with us. I am sorry that you had some issues with our service and please be assured that this is not the standard we normally deliver. I would like to investigate this further so I would appreciate it if you have the time to contact me directly on h9057-gm@accor.com so I can gain some more information from you. I hope to hear from you soon. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Edwina K", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r635055730-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["It is an amazing venue, beautifully presented with gorgeous views of the city.", "The food was of an excellent standard. What let it down was the awkward and inconsistent service.", "The host was really lovely and helpful upon our arrival and even gave us a window seat which was great.", "However the service at the table felt rushed... we had literally just sat down and were approached for our drink orders immediately . We hadn't had a chance to look at the menus yet.", "The waiter was pleasant enough, but came across as robotic and scripted in his interactions and throughout the meal kept asking how it was going. once is enough.", "Then they seemed in a rush to take our dishes away after each course when we hadn't quite finished.", "What was annoying at the end of the meal was the miscommunication from the waiter ,who told us they'd stopped serving drinks in the restaurant, however we could go down to the bar.", "SO we headed down waited to order at the bar and after waiting for about 5-10 minutes were asked if we were hotel guests (which we weren't) , we were then told that only hotel guests could be served at this time of the evening! Couldn't they have told us this at the start whilst we were waiting?", "I think after spending \u00a3250 for 2 people in the restaurant they could make an exception?", "The restaurant could be outstanding if they sorted out their service."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r635103685", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The best food I ate in London", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "22 November 2018", "answer_text": ["Wow Jeanne1972, we just love your review about your amazing experience at Bokan. Guillaume and Aurelie are jus thrilled to read this feedback and to know that we \"Heart warmed\" you is just fantastic and we are Heart Warmed too! I am sure we will welcome you back when you next visit London and we are already looking forward to it. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jeanne1972", "reviewer_origin": ["Dubai, United Arab Emirates"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "45"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r635103685-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Being a frequent Visitor of London, I was curious to discover this restaurant on the 37th Floor of Novotel Canary Warf. And I was so impressed. The staff are very knowledgeable. The card offers vegitarian, fish and meat... and the quality of the food was awesome. Beautiful starter, Great entree and the cheese for dessert is to die for. And then a big shout out to our waiter Guillaume. Adviced us a Great wine that both matched the bouillabaisse and the red meat. And he Made lots of little Jokes to make us feel special. And WHERE DID THEY FIND CHEF AURELIE?! Working it in her open kitchen was a joy to watch. Make a reservation! Enjoy the view of London and be heart warmed. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r635943586", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Diner at Bokan", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "27 November 2018", "answer_text": ["I am so proud when I am reading this fabulous 5 star review, thank you so much for sharing your experience with us. being welcomed by Veni really does start your evening off in the right way before she hands you over to Aurelie and Jerome who will look after you with great food and a few laughs. I hope we can welcome you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan 37 Team!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "fredvaillant", "reviewer_origin": ["Paris, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r635943586-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["It was a marvellous moment, first of all the welcome by Vini was a plaisure, Aurelie the cooker is excellent and Jerome who take care of us was very professional with so british sense of humor. Everything was delicious and we had such a great time. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r636598426", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great views", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "29 November 2018", "answer_text": ["Oh Ninagould50, we are delighted that we surprised you with our cocktail and I agree our amazing views of London, thanks so much for sharing this fabulous Bokan experience and we are looking forward to seeing you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Nina G", "reviewer_origin": ["Swindon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r636598426-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What a surprise! Went to floor 38 and 39 of the Novotel in Canary Wharf and enjoyed cocktails with amazing views of London. Will definitely return"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r635869864", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Thank you mr B", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "26 November 2018", "answer_text": ["We are delighted with the 5 star review, thank you so much Alsu. I agree we do a great dirty martini and Mr B is happy that you enjoyed it. Our Gin Menu is extensive and we are currently doing a fabulous Sipsmith Hot Gin selection for the winter months. I hope we see you back in Bokan soon. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Alsu H", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r635869864-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Excellent place, with a great dirty Martiny. Thank you! ", "Also I don\u2019t drink gin, but my friend does and he enjoyed his treat too!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r636803021", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Terrible staff", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "1 December 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you for letting me know about these issues you experienced, I am so sorry. I would like to discuss this further with you and would really appreciate you contacting me on h9057-gm@accor.com. Many thanks and I look forward to hearing from you. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "McWebb", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "75"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r636803021-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We popped in for a drink - great view but despite sitting at the bar, it took for ever to get served. When we asked how we could get a drink, a surly and grumpy member of staff (Darina or Davina I think) begrudgingly served us. When we got the bill, there was a \u2018discretionary\u2019 service charge added!", "Oh yes, and to top it off, when leaving, we were virtually bathed out of the way by. Waitress - no \u2018excuse me\u2019 or apology - genuinely shocking and made us ashamed to be British!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r636758349", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Amazing view, cocktails meh", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "30 November 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you brettjmcc, I am so sad to read your review. Please be assured that I have addressed this my team and I can only apologise for this. I hope we get the chance to welcome you back again. Please contact me directly if you are returning on h9057-gm@accor.com. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "brettjmcc", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r636758349-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["So the title might be misleading slightly but it is my overall feeling. Let me explain that personally I judge a bar by its Long Island Ice Tea, especially one that charges a service charge even with drinks ordered at the bar...", "First round OK, but my wife who asked for a double gin and tonic ended up having to get another bottle of tonic. Sure you will say that you get a lot of gin, but it ruined the experience initially. Long Island was OK,but not stellar. ", "Then onto the the 2nd. Well, if I had wanted to order Tequila I would have,but I didn't. To say the bar person took it badly is a bit of an understatement. Sure he may have thought he was OK about it, but sadly some of us can read body language, the rolls of the eyes and lip reading the commentary to his friends sat at the bar. There wasn't really much of an improvement on the second try but I was too tired to argue.", "Overall poor rating based on the experience but the view is great"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r637323656", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Very good food and ambience", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "3 December 2018", "answer_text": ["We love our 5 star review and we are thrilled that you enjoyed your Bokan experience. The views are amazing and then the food that Aurelie and her team produce really is outstanding. We are looking forward to welcoming you back. Thanks so much for sharing your feedback. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "SP-M1981London", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r637323656-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I would highly recommend Bokan for an outstanding food and London views experience ! Really good service and reasonable prices !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r633338272", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Mother in Law's 70th Birthday celebration- excellent experience", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "14 November 2018", "answer_text": ["Wow, we absolutely love your review and are thrilled that you all enjoyed this birthday celebration with us at Bokan. The team were delighted to read their personal feedback about how well they looked after you all, even the small and fidgety children :), everyone is welcome at Bokan. I am sure we will be welcoming you al back soon and thank you for sharing your experience. See you soon. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "HusnaS1", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r633338272-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We recently celebrated my mother in law's 70th birthday at the Bokan restaurant. We were a diverse group, including toddler, young children and two generations of adults, many of us with different dietary preferences. The restaurant staff were extremely friendly, accommodating and hospitable. They attended to all our needs and queries and ensured all of us had the mostly amazing experience. The food was freshly prepared and very delicious. The price is on the higher range but worth the quality of food, beautiful view from the table as well as from the roof top. Starting from the reservation process to the dining and billing, it was a very smooth experience and I would highly recommend this restaurant for celebrations of all kinds; including those involving small and fidgety children:-)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r629212793", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "anniversary surprise", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "28 October 2018", "answer_text": ["We are delighted that you chose Bokan for your anniversary surprise. My Chef is thrilled with the feedback about her menu :). Next time maybe start with a glass of Prosecco and then try one of our fabulous wines with lunch or dinner. I am sure we will be welcoming you back again soon. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "PeterbloLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r629212793-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The staff were friendly and very attentive, the view amazing and the food in the chefs selection tremendous - Oh how I wish we hadn't had the prosecco which did nothing to compliment the great food. When we go again I will order a decent bottle of wine"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r629332333", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "50/50", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "29 October 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you Katherine for taking the time to write a review about your Bokan experience. I am pleased to read that you did enjoy atmosphere and the view and of course the service. I am so sorry to hear about the issues with your cod and please be assured that I am addressing this but I can confirm that none of our fish is frozen, it does come in fresh every day. I am thrilled that your other half loved his lamb and you had a great dessert. I really hope we can welcome you both back in the future. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "katherinebZ8801JZ", "reviewer_origin": ["Oxford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r629332333-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked into Bokan as we were staying in the hotel, and weren't due to arrive until late and didn't want the hassle of going back out again to eat. The atmosphere and view is great and the waiting staff are attentive, but the food was very much a 50/50 thing. The other half said his lamb was one of the best meals he'd ever had, my cod however had to be sent back as it was stone cold and raw in the middle (I suspect from the texture it was previously frozen). When the replacement (very quickly) came it was so very salty it was almost inedible, coupled with the over salted fries it made for a unpleasant meal which was marginally rescued by a fabulous desert ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r627117577", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Outstanding", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "22 October 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much Philip, we are so thrilled with your review about your experience at Bokan. Matteo mixes the best cocktails and I don't think I have ever met such a passionate mixologist in all my time in this industry. Of course Florian always makes sure the Prosecco is free flowing :), so glad you enjoyed him looking after you. We cannot wait to welcome you back soon. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Philip P", "reviewer_origin": ["Lichfield, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "37"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r627117577-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We wanted somewhere in London to Celebrate 3 60th birthdays this year with work colleagues.", "I picked Bokan from the previous reviews and I'm delighted I did, what a find!", "From the pre lunch drinks ably mixed by Matteo to the amazing lunch with (very) free flowing Prosecco and the stunning views, even from the toilet! Our waiter Florian and the team looked after us very, very well. I could not find a fault with any of the excellent courses served and all six of us who dined agreed on an outstanding experience.", "Thank you Bokan, we will be back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r627828011", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "beautiful restaurant!", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "24 October 2018", "answer_text": ["Thanks so much Ibby H we are delighted to read how much you enjoyed your dinner at Bokan with work colleagues. The views are absolutely stunning but of course your feedback about how friendly my team are makes me super happy! We are looking forward to seeing you again soon. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ibby H", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r627828011-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great good, friendly staff and fantastic views over central London. Met some work colleagues here for dinner and had a very pleasant dinner, good choice of food, including catering for a vegetarian in our group. Total price was reasonable based on what we ate and wine consumed. Would recommend as social or work dinner venue."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r632364067", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful Bottomless Brunch", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "10 November 2018", "answer_text": ["Great review Belinda and we are thrilled to read that Bokan is now a must every time you come to London. Constantin is of course thrilled with his personal mention. We look forward to welcoming you back again very soon. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "814belindag", "reviewer_origin": ["Perth, Australia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r632364067-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We have made Bokan a must every time I visit London to see my favourite gal. We have had amazing service on both occasions with Constantin, and would recommend this wonderful experience to anyone! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r632497906", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Average sky bar", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "11 November 2018", "answer_text": ["Thanks for your feedback, and I am so sorry that we have let you down. This is so unusual to hear this feedback and please be assured that I am addressing it. If you do have the time to give me some further feedback to work with I would appreciate it. My e-mail is h9057-gm@accor.com. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sunnyflowers01", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r632497906-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This sky bar offers lovely views and a nice sheltered seating area outside.", "However the bar has a a very small selection of cocktails. I visited on a Saturday night, and ordered one cocktail to be told they can\u2019t make it. So I chose another cocktail and got told again, he can\u2019t make it. I asked if he was serving cocktails, he said yes but not those two, they don\u2019t have the alcohol for it!", "How can a sky bar not have the alcohol to make cocktails, I do not understand. This is a busy Saturday night after all. I was not offered an alternative cocktail either. I would say poor bar service could be improved a lot! I wouldn\u2019t recommend this sky bar if you wish to have cocktails as they only have a small menu and they probably won\u2019t be able to make them either!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r629382513", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "I only did drinks - fantastic", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "29 October 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for taking the time to write a review and so thrilled to hear that it was already your second time and you have already planned your 3rd visit with us. Looking forward to seeing you again in December if not before. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "VWA", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "99"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "57"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r629382513-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What a great find. This place has both a rooftop bar and restaurant with stunning views across London.", "I was so impressed with my first visit that I went back the following weekend. I have also now booked the restaurant for December.", "The drink prices are average for London but the views are exceptional. There are a number of places to sit and take in the views, however the outside terrace is quite small and can get a bit smoky. Having said that it does depend on who is sitting outside when you visit.", "Lovely selection of drinks and bar snacks if you want to while away a couple of hours."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r632533630", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Astonishing view", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "11 November 2018", "answer_text": ["We love your review, thank you so much for sharing this. The views are amazing and we are looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lapolie", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "41"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r632533630-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Fantastic atmosphere... for drinks and we ordered starters to share...tasty..", "If the weather is good... the best photos of London"]}
