{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r623311022", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good views and good dishes", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "8 October 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for sharing your experience of Bokan with others. We are so pleased you enjoyed your time with us and I agree the crab salad is one of my favourite dishes, I am so glad you enjoyed the freshness of it. We are really looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Thank you! Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "7RAC", "reviewer_origin": ["York, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "493"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "427"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r623311022-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["It\u2019s a little bit of a walk and not in the most auspicious of settings but it was worth it.", "Wines were decent value: Viognier and red from the Douro were keenly priced and tasty. Guests were surprised when I told them the price. ", "I went for the crab salad then the lobster and scallop ravioli - both were excellent. The crab salad was exceptionally fresh with a lovely, spikey and zesty dressing. ", "The bread was served really nicely in a tear and share fashion. ", "Will definitely return. "]}
