{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r623918059", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "11 October 2018", "answer_text": ["Wow, thank you Cyril for this fantastic review about your experience with us in Bokan! We loved reading it and sharing it with our Bokan Family. We are all looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Thanks so much! Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "cbulvestre", "reviewer_origin": ["Liverpool, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r623918059-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["From the beginning until the end this venue is perfect!", "The staff is so friendly and professional, and what a meal! ", "The tasting menu pairing with wine was absolutely Fabulous!, the chef is exceptional and you can discover many different way to enjoy the flavour of the world.", "The view of London is wonderful as well!", "I will definitely coming back ", "Cyril"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r624531037", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "13 October 2018", "answer_text": ["Happy birthday first of all and thank you for choosing Bokan to celebrate this occasion. Antonella is fantastic and of course she will be rewarded for her personal mention. Thank you so much for recommending us and of course we cannot wait to see you again. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "krassykarate", "reviewer_origin": ["Sofia, Bulgaria"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r624531037-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I had a great time, Antoinella gave us amazing customer service experience and even brought us chocoloatea at the end for my birthday. The managers were also very helpful and understanding. I\u2019m definitely recommending this place for any occassion!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r625748316", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Exceptional!", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "17 October 2018", "answer_text": ["What a fantastic review Elo70, thank you so much for sharing your experience. We are thrilled that you enjoyed the special Parmesan tasting menu that my Amazing Chef Aurelie created to celebrate this ingredient and I agree I have never in my life tried Parmesan ice cream and it was fabulous. When you match amazing food with our amazing views it makes for an amazing evening :). Looking forward to welcoming you back. Thanks again. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Elo70", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r625748316-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This place is a fantastic restaurant! This is the second time that I am going for dinner to Bokan and I absolutely loved it! Friendly and professional staff! The cuisine is exquisite! The Chef is brilliant! From starters to deserts you will be surprised and your palate will want some more... I would have never imagined to try parmesan ice cream one day but believe me you have to try it, with an apple tart and lemon cream it's wonderful! And that's one of the many delights the Chef wants to make you discover! ", "And don't forget the view ,it's stunning! ", "I just can't wait to go back! ", "Thanks again!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r614028686", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Stunning London view", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "5 September 2018", "answer_text": ["Thanks so much Anne Marie for sharing your experience at our gem that we call Bokan! We are thrilled that you enjoyed your time with us and that you really liked the way we have designed our hotel which took a long time to do with the heart of this area always in our minds. We are looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Anne Marie H", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "46"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r614028686-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for the view and found a gem off the beaten track. Elegant interior design with rustic finishes that gives the space a cosy feel. Windows throughout, comfy sofas. Prices ok for a rooftop/high bar. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r615629667", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Nice", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "11 September 2018", "answer_text": ["On behalf of myself and the whole team at Bokan, thank you so much for sharing your recent experience at Bokan 37 Restaurant. ", "We are just thrilled with your feedback! We are really proud of Chef Aurelie, together with our Restaurant Manager Jerome and their team who create very delicious food and memorable experiences. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon and we are looking forward to it. Louisa & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Linda J", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r615629667-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The wiev, the food, the service all exellente! Good value for money and highly attentive staff. Would go again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r620722722", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect Lunch ", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "30 September 2018", "answer_text": ["Firstly Happy Birthday and we are delighted you shared this with us at Bokan. I am so pleased to read how much you ejoyed your time with us. Hope you come back and visit us again for your next birthday. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "gailcollins", "reviewer_origin": ["West Byfleet, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "38"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r620722722-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This restaurant was a surprise for my 60th birthday. It exceeded all my expectations. The bottomless prosecco flowed. The three courses were tasty, well presented and the chocolate pudding with mint sorbet delicious. Then I got a beautiful cake and a birthday song. It was so sweet. The staff were attention very, polite and professional.", "The views to die for. Thank you for a very special day. Lots of young people. But still here I for a middle aged lady!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r615818947", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Absolute shocker of a restaurant ", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "11 September 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your feedback. We are terribly sorry to hear that we were not able to provide you a memorable experience during your visit at our restaurant. Please allow us to inform you that we are presenting a meticulously crafted menu of premium locally-sourced ingredients. Nevertheless, rest assured that we will take your comments under consideration for the improvement of our performance, and we do hope that you will give us another chance in the future as you can see from most of my reviews on here, they are excellent. Louisa & The BOKAN Family. "], "reviewer_pseudo": "553darrens", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r615818947-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went for a bottomless prosecco lunch with friends, with the only plus coming from the flowing prosecco. ", "The Ni\u00e7oise salad came with no tuna. When this was pointed out, a saucer of extremely poorly prepared tuna was slapped down on the table.", "I ordered a smoked pork starter that was a disgrace. I can\u2019t explain what it was. Green tasteless slop with a few saffron sized strands of pork.", "Three of the party ordered steak but weren\u2019t asked how we\u2019d like it cooked. When it arrived it was dry and again, tasteless. ", "The cheese board consisted of cheap cheese straight out of the fridge.", "After requesting the service charge be removed from the bill the waitress said she didn\u2019t care why we were dissatisfied.", "One of the worst meals and service I\u2019ve had at a supposedly \u2018fine\u2019 restaurant. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r615228886", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent - need I say any more?", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "9 September 2018", "answer_text": ["On behalf of myself and the whole team at Bokan, thank you so much for sharing your recent experience at Bokan, we are just thrilled with your feedback. We are really proud of Chef Aurelie and her team who create such amazing and very delicious food and we love welcoming children to experience this too. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon and we are looking forward to it. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "eeZeeman", "reviewer_origin": ["Singapore, Singapore"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r615228886-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I v rarely, if ever use the word 'excellent', but we had a wonderful dining experience at Bokan.", "Brother's 40th birthday dinner - accomodated for 5 adults and 2 kids with a table that had a marvellous sunset view of the London skyline.", "It is important to mention the children diner policy - Bokan are v welcoming and accommodating with a catered kids' menu) because you would not believe how snobby some restaurants are, not allowing kids below 7 years of age to dine.", "Staff were attentive, knowledgeable and professional. ", "I will admit to having a small degree of apprehension with the menu after having been burned on a couple of previous dining experiences elsewhere.", "However. I was v pleased with the quality of the food and preparation. We went a la carte and the food was delicious. As was the dessert.", "Yes - you pay a little bit more of a premium, but the quality of the food, the service, and the location/view is all worth it!"]}
