{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r613162785", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Second visit to this fantastic bar and restaurant, with very high quality food and service. Feels really special.", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "2 September 2018", "answer_text": ["WOW PennyPurples we just love your review, thank you so much for sharing your special experiences at Bokan. Your photo's are fantastic.We are all really looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Thanks again. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "PennyPurples", "reviewer_origin": ["Orpington, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "619"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "345"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r613162785-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["2nd visit and very glad I've returned. This time ordered A La Carte rather than tasting menu and was again wowed by the food, its presentation and the generosity of the portion sizes. Excellent service throughout the meal. Those wonderful views. Absolutely love this place! My descriptions won't do it justice: please check out my photos."]}
