{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r607478168", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "One if the best restaurants and bar in London", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "17 August 2018", "answer_text": ["WOW Lliyana we love your 5 star review and to consider us one of the best restaurant bars in London is just fantastic, thank you so much. Ventsislava is just a fantastic host with the biggest smile to welcome our guests. Looking forward to seeing you soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family."], "reviewer_pseudo": "iliyanaig", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r607478168-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I\u2019ve been living in London for over three years, visited most of the \u201chip\u201d bars in both West End and Shoreditch, and I can easily say that it is one of the best places in town. Bokan is amazing because of the incredible view of the city, delicious gourmet food and banging house music tunes. It is in the beautiful area of Canary Wharf so the crowd is pleasant and it is also not so busy - there is plenty of room across the three floors. Must go!! Thanks to the lovely host Ventsislava provided nothing but the best experience."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r608574627", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Incredible tasting menu and delightful service", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "20 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Happy Anniversary first of all Amanda F and thank you for choosing Bokan to celebrate it. Florin of course is thrilled with his mention and as always he will be rewarded for this. Good luck with the new arrival to your family when they arrive and we are looking forward to welcoming you back. Jacqui, Florin and The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Amanda F", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r608574627-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked a table at Bokan for our anniversary. It was our first time at the restaurant for both my husband and I. As I had made note of our anniversary when booking the table, the staff seated us in a private section with Thames views - very romantic! The staff were attentive, and even catered to my dietary needs during pregnancy. Course after course the flavours continued to impress! The food was divine and we cannot wait to return for another meal. Great value for such exceptional food and service. And a big thank you to Florian for making our evening that much more special!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r607625497", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Great views, not service", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "18 August 2018", "answer_text": ["We are so sad Gero T to read your review, I am so sorry we disappointed you. Of coursed the views are great but we let you down on the service which please be assured that I will address. As always with most bars and restaurants in London, the service charge is completely optional and you can always ask to have it taken off the bill. I do hope you will give us another chance in the future as you can see from most of my reviews on here, they are all excellent. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "gerot992", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r607625497-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["First of all the views of London are stunning and I wanted to pop by for a quick glass of wine on a Friday evening to show my friend the wonderful view.", "After waiting, and waiting at the bar I finally got served after 20 minutes.", "I ordered two glasses of wine (circa \u00a37.50 each) and was told it was not available and would I like a similar Pinot Noir. I agreed and was charged \u00a325.88 for the privalidge. ", "I don't really think that's on and charging 12.5% service for people getting their own drinks is frankly ridiculous."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r608074314", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Made great memories ", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "19 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Making great memories at Bokan is exactly what we want to achieve, and we are thrilled to read that you will be talking about your dining experience for a long time. The presentation of the food I agree is super innovative and makes you want to eat it more, I am very proud of Aurelie and her team. I look forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "adrianob299", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r608074314-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Without a doubt, Bokan is one of the most romantic places London has to offer.", "The view on the Thames and the whole city is breathtaking, and the informal but professional service of the floor staff makes you always feel looked after without being inappropriate or too formal.", "The food is greatly cooked and with a very innovative plating. It's amazing to be able to have good food made with passion in a laidback, informal place.", "Will talk about this dinner for a very long time."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r609433899", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Dinner", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "23 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you Alexander for this fabulous 5 star review about your experience at Bokan. Great that you will recommend us and we are all looking forward to seeing you again soon. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "alexanderlG6066YG", "reviewer_origin": ["Vienna, Austria"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r609433899-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My friend and I enjoyed a very pleasant evening at Bokan. We were very impressed of the view, menu and the staff. I would definitely recommend Bokan to anyone that visits London."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r611108600", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful evening", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "27 August 2018", "answer_text": ["We love our 5 star rating for your recent experience in Bokan. Thank you so much for taking the time to write this fabulous review. Veni of course is thrilled with her mention and of course she will be rewarded for this. We look forward to welcoming you back soon. Kind regards. Jacqui & The Bokan Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "xaxobgpld", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r611108600-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I enjoyed a very pleasant evening at Bokan. I was very impressed of the view, menu and the staff, especially Veni, she was an amazing hostess. I would definitely recommend Bokan to anyone in London."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r610287158", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "just above expectations", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "25 August 2018", "answer_text": ["WOW, congratulations Barbie & Ana on your engagement! Thank you for choosing Bokan to celebrate this fabulous occasion and of course I am delighted that my Bokan team were so amazing. Hope to see you again soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "barbiejansik", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r610287158-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Me and my girlfriend Ana, celebrated my 25th of birthday in the Bokan restaurant, where my girlfriend proposed me to get married. Absolutely was fantastic, the best and one of the most important night in our life. I would like to say a big big thank you for the team and the fantastic kitchen, and you guys Guillaume, Jerome, Constantin, Georgiana, Pedro, Nelson,Chef Guillaume, Emanuele,Adam you are guys just amazing! Thank you for everything, you guys made our night fantastic and guys you are doing amazing job. ", "This is the place where we feel absolutely good with so many many good memories. Can not wait to go again. :) ", "Barbie"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r609801848", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nice Place for Drinks with a View", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "24 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you FOttoC for your review, I am so pleased you enjoyed the view. I am sorry that you felt that the drinks were watered down, however of course I can assure you that they are not. The Orange juice we use is fresh orange juice. The service charge is completely optional and you can choose to have it removed. I hope we can welcome you back and I hope you saw the Sunset as it is the best time to visit Bokan. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "fottoc", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "107"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r609801848-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We brought our guests for drinks on 2 occasions. The first time we were there, 2 people ordered a double gin tonic which we thought was watered down. As I could not drink alcoholic beverages during the second time we were there, I ordered orange juice which was also watered down. The view of the city is nice, but alcoholic drinks seem pricey; I guess you pay for the view. There is already a 12.5% service charge, so tips should not be expected but their system indicates otherwise and servers still ask if you want to give a tip or not."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r607019394", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing view", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "16 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Thanks so much for the 5 star review, we are just thrilled. I agree sometimes having to go into Central London to get a venue like ours is not ideal and I am so pleased that you popped in with no reservation and had such a lovely time, I would recommend though if you are coming in over the weekend in the evening, please book as we are getting more popular. We are looking forward to welcoming you back. Jacqui & The Bokan Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ChristaKatarina", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "71"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "29"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r607019394-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I read a few other reviews, and while some people think this is 'out of the way', I think it's great to find a nice place like this in other locations than just central London. We came here for drinks on a weekday afternoon (without booking), and were greeted by a host who showed us a window table. The waiter then showed us the cocktail menu, and gave us recommendations. Drinks are expensive, but that's expected with this kind of view. Service was great, and we had a lovely time. Will definitely be back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r604521205", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Won\u2019t visit again", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "9 August 2018", "answer_text": ["We are so disappointed to read that you won't be returning :(. As you can see from many of the reviews here, this is not the normal feedback we get so we are sad to read your review. If you would like to discuss this further with me please do not hesitate to contact me on h9057-gm@accor.com. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Rissacsw", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "119"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "58"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r604521205-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited here at the weekend after a day in Canary Wharf. Whilst the view is good the novelty wears off quite quickly. The staff are so rude and I felt very uncomfortable. I didn\u2019t like the vibe so after 30 minutes I left. I was really disappointed as I had been looking forward to the rooftop bar but based on my experience at the weekend I won\u2019t be returning"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r604612379", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Mesmerising views..!", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "9 August 2018", "answer_text": ["So pleased to read that you loved the ambience of Bokan, we really love it too. However I am sad to read about your cocktail experience, I am so sorry for this and I hope we can welcome you back in the future and I promise we will do better! Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lazzari", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "85"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r604612379-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Beautiful place Nice ambient, with singer and live band. ", "They have a huge liquor display but unfortunately a bit disappointed about the cocktails timing arrived to table and quality check drinks. 3 negroni 3 different glass.and garnishes", "Ambience 8/10", "Food 5/10 ", "Service 6/10", "Drinks 4/10"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r604381383", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great food, great vibe, ok food", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "8 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Thanks Liam for taking the time to write a review about your experience with us, I am delighted to read that you loved our vibe. We are looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "liamdowd", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "45"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r604381383-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I ate here with my wife and friends. Found the views breathtaking and the vibe lively in the bar, whilst relaxed in the restaurant - perfect. The food was ok and reasonably priced. It is a restaurant with amazing views, but next time I'll return just for drinks and the view. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r605258466", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great Views to enjoy a cigar and a drink", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "11 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for taking the time to write a review and I am glad that you enjoyed your time with us. I too am sorry that we do have to close the terrace at a certain time and this is due to our Licence which I am trying to extend... so watch this space. I hope we can welcome you back though to enjoy your cigar and the views. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "dn0ne", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r605258466-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Breathtaking views of London to enjoy a cigar and a drink at night. ", "Unfortunately they close the terrace quite early which is difficult to understand since surely no neighbors around who would complain on the 39-40th floor. ", "Would have loved to stay longer and enjoy more drinks during an amazing summer evening and under a sparkling firmament. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r603773198", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Gread food, amazing views with a terrible experience !", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "7 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you Slagian for your review. We are thrilled to read how much you enjoyed food and it was beautiful and tasty. We are so sorry that a glass of wine was spilt over you and I know how upset my talent was as it was an accident which do happen. Of course I am sorry that we ruined your night and hope you will return in the future. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GEORGE C", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "10", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r603773198-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Yesterday 06/08/2018 we booked a table of 3 under my name,George Capita.We arrived there,2 nice bulgarian girls were all smile and happy to show us the table.So far so good.", "We decided to take the tasting menu with wine pairing because my friend had that before and he said is amazing and so it was.The food was beautifully cooked and tasty.", " Until something shocking happened.The waitress spills a full glass of red wine on my Hugo Boss white jeans and my Dior shirt and ruined my night.", "The head waiter ,Constantin came to say sorry and he was very nice and he decided to drop the service charge from the bill but still we had to pay a bill of more then \u00a3300.", "We supposed to go to bar in the area after the restaurant but I had to take a uber 1 hr and 30 min back home in north so I can change ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r604337735", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A truly wonderful experience!", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "8 August 2018", "answer_text": ["We are all thrilled that we gave you such good and happy memories at Bokan and thank you for this amazing feedback. I love that you bring your friends to visit us when they are in town! I am sure we will help you make so many more memories in the future and we look forward to this. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lawrenceandsallyg", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r604337735-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["A really welcoming sky bar with fantastic 360 views across the whole of London - great service with very friendly staff! We always bring our various friends here when they visit from overseas, and they are always, without fail, stunned by the experience. Thank you Sky Bar at Bokan for giving us so many good and happy memories."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r605692820", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Very, very good.", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "12 August 2018", "answer_text": ["WOW, we love our 5 star review.... and of course that we cooked your steak to perfection! The views are fabulous and when backed up by great food and attentive service what more could you ask for. I am sure we will welcome you back soon and we are looking forward to it. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sarzp", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r605692820-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The food is sublime none of us could fault what we had and my steak was cooked to perfection. The service was excellent, we were a group of 5 and they ensured when requested that we had a window side table to enjoy the views. Very attentive when a food allergy risk was raised. Would recommend to anyone, menu may seem pricey but the food served is worth every penny"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r606466284", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Top-Notch-View with perfect Gin-Cocktails", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "14 August 2018", "answer_text": ["We just love your review and of course delighted that you also rewarded us with 5 stars at Bokan. The Gin cocktails are a favourite with many of our guests so I am thrilled that you enjoyed them and of course the fabulous view. I am sure we will welcome you back soon and we look forward to it. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "loftistanbul", "reviewer_origin": ["istanbul"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r606466284-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Very attentive employees which want to help in every way to offer a great service. We had a couple of Cocktails up at the Bokan-Terasse (40th floor) with it's incredible view over London"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r606636091", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Outstanding from start to finish! Thank you!", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "15 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much LJW0983 for sharing your outstanding experience with us, I am so pleased that we looked after you so well. we were really excited about the Royal Wedding and wanted to share this with our guests. What a beautiful day we got for it too :). we are really looking forward to welcoming you back to Bokan. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LJW0983", "reviewer_origin": ["Reading, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r606636091-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been meaning to write this review since our visit to Bokan. We actually visited on 19th May, which is our wedding anniversary as well as being the date of the Royal wedding. The place was absolutely buzzing with wonderful happy vibes due to the special occasion that many were there to watch on the large screens. We watched a bit and I have to say it was nothing short of spectacular to be able to watch the royal wedding with the London skyline as the back drop. They really had set things out nicely for those wanting to come along and partake in this celebration. We were made to feel extra special as it was our anniversary and every member of staff we encountered gave us their best wishes. We were seated and the views were, in my opinion, the best I have ever experienced in London. We were served by Guillaume and also the husband and wife team. They were effortlessly friendly and professional. Nothing was too much trouble. Honestly top notch staff! The food was delightful - we had the three course set menu, including the royal wedding cake. We even got a little bag of token chocolates to take with us, which was a lovely touch. The drinks flowed and we had an absolutely fantastic anniversary; and it was down to the incredible location and views, the food, the fabulous atmosphere and the amazing staff. Thank you! We will be back again for sure."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r602785912", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Dinner ", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "4 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for taking the time to write a review about your experience at Bokan, I am thrilled that overall you enjoyed your time with us. Why not next time, book a table in our amazing restaurant on Bokan 37 after drinks on the terrace, I promise you that you will fall in love with our 2 AA Rosette Restaurant. Look forward to seeing you again. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "manvsfood40", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r602785912-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The view over London was amazing especially as the sun was setting. The ambiance had a buzzy vibe and the staff were efficient. The menu wasn\u2019t vast but what was available was adequate.", "I would definitely go here again for drinks but not sure if i would for dinner "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r598459540", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Good food!", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "22 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Thanks Lukas, we love the 5 star review. Sorry you thought we were understaffed and of course I will be addressing this. Ah the famous Bokan Burger, we will never be able to take this off the menu. Looking forward to seeing you again soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "70lukasf", "reviewer_origin": ["Vienna, Austria"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "78"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "75"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r598459540-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice food and excellent view. Prices are reasonable for a suchlike location. Service friendly but understaffed. I recommend the burger."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r596300280", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "BAR AND VIEWS STOP OFF", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "15 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you MartiniGold for sharing your fabulous experience at Bokan. We love the fact you like our views but of course your feedback about the outstanding service from my team makes me so proud. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon and we are looking forward to it. Many thanks, Jacqui McMillan & The Bokan Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MartiniGold", "reviewer_origin": ["London -East"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "150"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "66"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r596300280-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great location . Very nice views and the service from staff outstanding. Friendly and welcoming . ", "We visited for drinks reasonable price for a hotel and super strong so not watered down drinks here ! Very nice and worth the money", "Will definitely be returning sometime soon but will make sure we reserve a table but we didn't have any trouble finding a table", "Thanks for the great service.", " "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r594237671", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful Experience", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "9 July 2018", "answer_text": ["We are thrilled to read what a \"Wonderful Experience\" you had with us at Bokan. The views are simply stunning I agree and of course when it is then followed by an amazing meal and I am so glad you took the wine pairing, then really what more could you wish for. I hope and I am sure we can welcome you back again soon. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Deirdre Y", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "119"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "62"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r594237671-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This restaurant is at the top of the Novotel which is just a little away from the main area of Canary Wharf so it takes a bit of finding but is worth it. We started with drinks on the roof terrace on the 38th floor which is amazing, especially as it was a clear, sunny evening. The atmosphere is fun and lively and of course the view is breathtaking. We had the Tasting Menu with paired wines and enjoyed every mouthful with special mention for the Salmon with mint & pea velout\u00e9. Service was good with friendly young staff and, although it was busy, it was still possible to hold a conversation across the table. We were there quite a long time and enjoyed every minute. Highly recommended"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r595465718", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Hotel buffet breakfast", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "12 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Thanks Mark P for sharing your breakfast experience with us! I am glad you enjoyed the fruit salad and of course the amazing views. Hope we can welcome you back for a drink next time as Sunset is truly spectacular. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mark P", "reviewer_origin": ["Hampshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "676"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "170"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r595465718-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Breakfast meeting at Bokan with some colleagues. Excellent views over London from such a high floor.", "Breakfast was buffet style. Reasonable selection. I enjoyed the fruit salad.", "Had Rooibos tea which was excellent."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r598608449", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent Brunch", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "22 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Your review really has made me smile and I have to agree with you on London during the summer break! I am so glad you enjoyed our bottomless brunch it is getting really popular. My team of course will be thrilled with their feedback. I am sure we will be welcoming you back soon and we look forward to it. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LondonFlash", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "26"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r598608449-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Firstly, it was cool up there and a great escape from the hot London summer we\u2019re having! ", "Next, the views are amazing. Given I live near Canary Wharf it is intriguing to get a bird\u2019s eye view of the local area from 38 floors up. ", "Brunch was the usual Londin \u2018unlimited\u2019 (but not really unlimited, since it\u2019s only 2 hours) Prosecco thing! Food was great and enough and staff were super attentive and friendly. Best thing was it was quiet on the day we went... maybe because summer holidays had kicked in and everyone has left the city. Fine by me!!! Stay away, I say. London feels much more tolerable during summer breaks and on any of the bank holidays."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r595056627", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Bar - Brilliant views", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "10 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Wow, thank you for this fabulous review and we love that we delivered to WOW factor! We agree that we have one of the best views in London and we are very proud of it. I am so glad that you ended a stressful day with us and I hope we can welcome you back in the future. Many thanks for sharing your Brilliant experience here. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "pdamci", "reviewer_origin": ["Wirral, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "40"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r595056627-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Bokan looks like not very much from street level but the roof-top bar - 39 floors up - at night delivers the wow factor big time!! We arrived late when the bar was about to close (and were not as well dressed as other clients!!) but were still made welcome and ended a stressful day in very memorable surroundings. We have been to various roof-top bars but this one showing off London at night, rates very, very highly!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r599097194", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food to equal an amazing view", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "24 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Wow Ray, we just love your review and I think you should put us forward to be one of the best views in town :). We are really popular with our local residents from the Wharf and we just love this as it really creates a fabulous atmosphere. Thank you for recommending us and we are so looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Thanks again Ray we really appreciate you sharing this experience with others. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan and the Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "rayc625", "reviewer_origin": ["Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "63"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r599097194-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["How is this restaurant not on the list of best views in town?! The food and service was terrific. A big plus was that it felt to be a popular haunt for locals which meant that it wasn't swamped with only tourists. I got there early and was seated immediately without a reservation. The staff were really professional and swift in their service. Definitely highly recommend. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r598718922", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Consistently excellent", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "23 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much John, I really love your review. Consistency is the key to being successful and I am thrilled that this is your 3rd visit to us and once again we lived up to your expectations. The view is great and of course we do love it but it would be nothing without the great food and service. We look forward to welcoming you for our 4th visit soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JohnRPearson", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "187"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "94"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r598718922-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Our third visit did not disappoint, once again. The food is wonderfully presented and with generous portion sizes. The view is fantastic and the staff are always very friendly. We will be back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r602278168", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Superb view", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "3 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Love your 5 star rating for your time with us at Bokan, thank you so much for taking the time to do this. I am so pleased to read how well we looked after you and especially your feedback about my team. Look forward to seeing you soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "drpeterr23", "reviewer_origin": ["Chester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "451"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "132"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r602278168-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great Location and superb views. Staff are great and excellent Cocktails and Drinks. worth getting near window"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r594218766", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing Business Dinner at Bokan!", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "9 July 2018", "answer_text": ["WOW WOW WOW, thank you Lallalie for this fantastic review and thank you so much for sharing your experience on here. Of course we are thrilled that you enjoyed the tasting menu and matching wines but of course when you specifically mention my talent like Jerome it makes me so proud to have him as part of my team here. We are looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Lallalie", "reviewer_origin": ["Thionville, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r594218766-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I had the pleasure to work with the Bokan Team last week to organise a Business dinner with 20 VIP guests.", "I would like to congratulate the Chef for her excellent and creative food and the Service Team who did an amazing job for us! The wine selection with the tasting menu was just perfrect!", "Special Thanks to the Maitre d'H\u00f4tel J\u00e9r\u00f4me who was a Perfect Partner. He took care of all of us with a lot of professionalism and made everything possible to please us. ", "I strongly recommend this new restaurant in Canary Wharf. ", "On top of all the above compliments I must say that the view from the Bokan restaurant is a \"must see\"!", "Many thanks again for this lovely and tasty evening!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r590092531", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Simply the best!", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "23 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Great review, thank you!!!!! Aurelie is amazing and so passionate, she was delighted to read your feedback. See you soon Louisa. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "louisadaxer", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r590092531-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been here a few times now and Chef Aurelie and her team always cook simply the best food! Without a doubt the best food in Canary Wharf and some of the best in London."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r590127458", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Delicious food but stressing atmosphere", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "24 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for taking the time to review your experience with us. I am sorry that we let you down with the service, I will certainly address this. I am glad you enjoyed the food though and of course the views and I hope we can welcome you back. Kind regards. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sofiek742", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r590127458-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My family and I stayed at the hotel and went eating at the restaurant our last evening. ", "Upstairs a party was going on (The restaurants is in more than one floor) so there\u2019s was pretty noisy but that happens...", "But the servers was really stressibg and ran around (no seriously ran). The kitchen is semi open and they garnished the food on both side of the kitchen counter. I DONT think this is very appealing it was almost like you sad in there busy kitchen,,,", "Beside the party the restaurant was very noisy too", "The decoration is kind of hip and hipster. Pretty cool maybe a bit dark if it hasn\u2019t been for the window walls. I don\u2019t say I didn\u2019t like it. Don\u2019t say I love it. It\u2019s a matter of personal taste and I\u2019m pretty neutral about the decorating. ", "We waiting way to long on our food - I think they were sending plates kind of slowly out of the kitchen in general...", "Most of the waiters did not talk very good English and had a heavy accent (maybe French?) ", "But I must admit the food was really good! Got to staters cause no mains seems appealing to me. I will put the pictures up. ", "(The menu hasn\u2019t changed in a long time)", "I must also mention the view! It is stunning!!", "You can see so much of London! Even London eye. It is turning the other way if the big skyscrapers so again it is an amazing view! (Just like the hotel rooms\u2019)", "I would maybe say it worth a visit for the food and the view!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r592023139", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "What a view!", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "1 July 2018", "answer_text": ["We think Bokan is beautiful and we're thrilled that you do as well nashbob127! Thankyou for coming to visit and enjoying our amazing restaurant and bar!", "Warm regards,", "The team at Bokan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Bob N", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r592023139-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Beautiful venue in the earth of canary wharf. Definitely go there if you wanna enjoy a nice drink on the top of Canary wharf!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r591900275", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The absolute best!!!", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "30 June 2018", "answer_text": ["We're so happy you choose to celebrate your aunt's birthday with us gamarteifio and that everyone had an excellent time! Thankyou for choosing us and we can't wait to welcome you all back again soon!", "Warm regards,", "The team at Bokan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "_gamarteifio", "reviewer_origin": ["Maidstone, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r591900275-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I booked a table of 6 for my aunt's 70th. There was a slight confusion on arrival but that was cleared up. Staff allowed us to sprinkle confetti on the table to decorate and attach 2 helium balloons to her chair. ", "The food was beautifully presented and the taste was EXCELLENT.", "We had a great evening, staff were welcoming and attentive, decor was nice, the panoramic view was simply beautiful from the 37th floor and the overall ambience was nothing short of perfect. My aunt was made a fuss off and would I go again? OF COURSE!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r591978686", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great for drinks", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "30 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Thankyou for your lovely review AdamBilgy. We're thrilled to hear that you enjoyed your time in Bokan (especially our wine list) and look forward to welcoming you back again soon for another great experience!", "Warm regards,", "The team at Bokan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "AdamBilgy", "reviewer_origin": ["Trowbridge, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1115"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5398"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r591978686-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Sky bar situated in the Novotel.", "Brilliant view over London, especially the sunset. Lots of comfortable places to sit, with very welcoming staff. Reasonably priced wines, with a good varied selection. Would definitely return. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r590122283", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Friday evening cocktails ", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "24 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much Samirs64 for sharing your experience. I know exactly what Duty Manager you are talking about and he makes us laugh al the time. So gad you found our little Gem and see you soon! Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "samirs64", "reviewer_origin": ["Lymm, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "91"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "48"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r590122283-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["A wonderful gem near Canary Wharf in a Novotel. No really inside a Novotel. It is on a really high floor with fantastic panaromic views of London. Much more reasonable than the shard and great cocktails. We had a moijto and a rhubarb version. Pictures attached. Abt \u00a312 each plus 12.5% service charge. The duty manager is crazy and funny. We asked could we sit on a reserved table by the window. He said let me check. Let\u2019s call a friend like on who wants to be a millionaire. Then after a few funny comments gave us our table. We were served by a lovely Italian lady and service was great and almost endearing. If you visit Canary Wharf or just want to have a wonderful view and not pay shard prices then come here. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r592426056", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Maybe the most incredible dining experience of my life.", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "2 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Lincoln, honestly I think you brought a smile and a tear to most of us at our morning meeting today when I shared your review and the most amazing experience you had with us at Bokan. The best of it was that \"Jerome\" who was the gentleman that looked after you and made sure everything went well (despite your nerves) was in the meeting and we gave him a round of applause. I am so thrilled and proud when I read a review like this and THANK YOU for not only sharing this special moment with us at Bokan but also to share this experience with others on here. We are really looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Congratulations from all of us at Bokan - Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Lincoln S", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r592426056-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Friday 29th June may just have been the most incredible day of my life and The Bokan played a very large part in making this happen, particularly the restaurant manager, who regrettably i did not catch the name of in all of the excitement.", "I had planned a day out for my now Fiance's birthday and to her knowledge it was simply a day to celebrate just that. I however had other plans, that would see me propose to her and catch her completely unaware. ", "I called the restaurant earlier in the week to ask them if they could help me make this proposal special by giving me access for a brief period of time to the roof terrace. On my first call it did not sound too promising, but after calling a second time, i was told that our server on the day would allow me to view the platform for a short period of time and during this i would be able to pop the question, whilst looking over the simply incredible view of London that The Bokan has to offer. ", "I was still slightly unsure how this would pan out but i had everything else ready, the ring had been purchased, the after-celebrations were in place - I just needed to keep the surprise under wraps and hope that our server on the day would pull through in helping me to co-ordinate things perfectly. ", "On arrival we assumed with reading the brunch menu and immediately had our glasses filled with prosecco, to my very nervous delight. ", "Between enjoying perhaps the most delicious and exquisite 3 course meal i have ever had the pleasure of eating, i found a moment to speak to the manager (our server) in private and discussed my phone calls earlier in the week. He very quietly assured me that he had received my request and after our meal he would offer us both a 'tour' of the bar and the roof terrace, which was not scheduled to open until 5pm onwards. ", "We finished our desserts and the moment arrived.. my palms started to clam. It was time for me to pull through on my part of the deal. The Manager (who had been welcoming and hilariously funny throughout, might i add) asked my fiance and i if we would like to take a tour, as it was our first time in The Bokan. ", "He proceeded to take us upstairs and we looked through the bar's windows to see the view of the o2, he then asked my Fiance if she would like to see the roof terrace. She was very excited, as was I. ", "We got to the roof terrace and the restaurant Manager said to us that if we liked we could spend some time here to take in the views, take photos etc and then left us to enjoy the moment. ", "My then Girlfriend looked at me with a very puzzled but ecstatic face and asked me why i thought he was being so incredibly nice to us in particular. It was time for me to explain the reason for this... ", "I dropped to one knee and told her exactly what she meant to me and the rest is history: SHE SAID YES! :D", "Moments later, after the screams of happiness and tears had ensued, the Manager had re-appeared with 2 glasses and an ice bucket of prosecco in the other. ", "He congratulated us and assured us that we could take our time and enjoy the terrace for a while longer, as we took in the moment. The gods were seriously in my favour that day, as the weather was magnificent and i really cannot serve justice to the views on offer, with my limited vocabulary.", "I'd like to thank everyone at The Bokan for helping me to orchestrate this special moment in our lives so perfectly and for going above and beyond. ", "I recommend this restaurant to anyone and all the better if you are looking to celebrate a special occasion. we will certainly be returning for the brunch in the future and i will be telling the story of how you helped me to nail my proposal plans. ", "Lastly, i want to apologise again that i was unable to catch the restaurant Manager's name as i of course had a lot on my mind that day, but he was just incredible throughout. We wanted to thank him personally but by the time we came to leaving, he was on his break and not in the building. ", "I hope the next time that we visit i can see him again and thank him personally for his help that day. ", "As far as fine dining in London goes, it will be very hard to top the experience that The Bokan provides.", "Thanks again and kindest regards", "Lincoln"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r594133049", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "BEST BAR EVER!", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "8 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Wow, Liam is so happy and proud to read this amazing review about him! Thank you so much Josh for sharing this and of course Liam will be rewarded for this fabulous mention. Love the fact you got a picture too! Peter has a great team and is a great Manager and I am delighted to see this shows in his team. I am sure we will be welcoming you back to Bokan again soon. Thanks again for sharing your experience. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "jb01201", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r594133049-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I stayed at the Canary Wharf hotel the week of July 1 on a visit from America and the entire experience was fantastic. Tim and his staff were great but the highlight was easily the Bokan. I spent a good chunk of time there each day during the week and the service was always amazing. Peter and his team were all super professional, but the Star of the show, and my personal favorite bartender (now friend!) was Liam. If you ever visit this bar, do yourself a favor and have Liam serve you. The guy is a beast at his craft and made some of the best drinks I've had in my life. Liam was a huge part of the trip's success so definitely request him if you stay there, he's hilarious! My friend and I loved him so much we even got a pic with him! (see attached)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r592465612", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Tremendous restaurant", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "2 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Thanks Christopher for this fabulous 5 star review, we love it. I absolutely agree that dusk is the most beautiful time to spend with us and the sunset is stunning. We look forward to seeing you again soon. Many thanks. Jacqui & The Bokan Team"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Christopher V", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r592465612-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Best to book for dusk when the sun is setting on a clear night. Ask for a table next to the window. Food is outstanding."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r589291648", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great location ", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "20 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Oh we love Antonella too! Thanks Christian and I so happy to hear that you love the G&T's, we have 60 to try so you need to come back and see us soon. Jacqui & The Bokan family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ChristianW273", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r589291648-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Best thing about Bokan was the lovely Antonella super service ", "Food and bar snacks great ", "G&T are fantastic "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r587740243", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great views and food", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "16 June 2018", "answer_text": ["We just love your review Mark, thank you so much. We are thrilled that you enjoyed the tasting menu and of course the view is spectacular! Looking forward to welcoming you back soon. Jacqui &The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mark8888", "reviewer_origin": ["Singapore, Singapore"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "120"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "88"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r587740243-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went with a friend for dinner and tried the tasting menu which was excellent. Friendly & helpful service with some great recommendations. Decent affordable wines to pair and the salmon was spectacular. Lovely way to relax looking at the views of London."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r588491391", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Our 2nd visit - another fantastic meal with amazing service", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "18 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Katherine, what can we say \"amazing\" review, thank you so much!!!! To have feedback such as this and being able to share it with the Bokan family is fantastic and they are thrilled. We cannot wait to welcome you back. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Katherine J", "reviewer_origin": ["Twickenham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r588491391-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Amazing, Amazing, Amazing.... ", "We had the tasting menu with the matching wine as it was a special occassion. The food was stunning, the service was fantastic and the sommelier actually had the patience to explain to 2 non wine connoisseurs without us feeling stupid as to why he had chosen the wines that we were served. We drank wines we would not normally have which opened our eyes to some different options. ", "We had a stunning table with a stunning view over the Thames. We asked to have a little more time between courses and we didn't feel rushed, so we could enjoy the food and wine plus be able to have some time to talk. We will be back. If I could give this restaurant 6 out of 5 I would!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r586677471", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Really bad food poisoning", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "11 June 2018", "answer_text": ["With regards to your allegation about food poisoning I am very surprised you have not let us know directly about this issue, We have full traceabiity on all of our suppliers so we could have investigated this and of course if you had this proven by a doctor we would take it very seriously. If you would like to contact us directly, my e-mail is Jacqui.mcmillan@accor.com. I look forward to hearing from you. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "penguinprint", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "70"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "113"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "20", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r586677471-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Would not touch with a 10 foot pole. Yes, the view is great (assuming you're there on a good day). But the service was painfully slow (took them 45 mins to get our food out after taking orders) and you could tell the staff would much rather be elsewhere. When the food arrived, it was... below average. Not even average. At least, that was the case for me (I had a fried salmon... it seemed like their twist on fish and chips but the flavours were not a good combo, shall we just say). Now if you asked my fiance, the response is more like \"the food was horrible\" because he got a terrible case of food poisoning that very evening, after the lunch we had there. We didn't have anything else unusual that day so that lunch at Bokan was the likeliest culprit. His food poisoning was so bad he had a fever and missed two whole days of work afterwards. Long story short: not worth the pain and never going back again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r587357790", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Views", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "14 June 2018", "answer_text": ["WOW, you were here for the lightening storm. How amazing was that looking over London! You chose a great night. Glad you had a good time for the birthday drinks and look forward to welcoming you back. Kind regards. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Hi_tower1000", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "56"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r587357790-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Very nice setting.", "Went for birthday drinks and turned out having a really good time. ", "Attended on the evening of the lighting storm so that just made the night even better."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r587064197", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Pricey drinks but you get a great view of the London skyline.", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "12 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Thanks NezD I really appreciate your feedback about your time with us! The view is amazing and I am glad you enjoyed it. Hope to see you again soon. Many thanks. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "nezd2016", "reviewer_origin": ["Huntington, New York"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "856"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "238"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r587064197-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Amazing views of London's Skyline. Worth the premium price on the drinks as you can see the city of London all lit up while you enjoy a drink. Of course make sure to pick a night without fog or rain."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r588739856", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "The views make this place", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "19 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Thank you patercake for sharing your experience with us, we love it. We do a great Vegan tasting menu so let us know next time if you want to try a few dishes. See you soon. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "patercake", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "38"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r588739856-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Bokan is a laid-back with a warm wood/industrial interior - with views spanning up and down the Thames. There's a bar on one floor, and restaurant below. The menu is compact (I've been there 3 times in 3 months and the menu is the same). The chef favours undercooked fish, but will cook meat to your taste. The vegetarian options are tasty and include cheese, but I think a vegan may struggle to find something unless the restaurant is advised in advance. Definitely a place to go - if you don't eat, hang out in the bar."]}
