{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r588768230", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Mesmerising views..! ", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "19 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Thanks Nicola and I love the title of the review which is truly mesmerising! I am sorry about the delay in the cocktails! Hope we can welcome you back soon. Jacqui McMillan - General Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lazzari", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "85"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r588768230-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["A recommended place to be,have a cocktails and some food to. ", "Nice ambient, with singer and live band. ", "They have a huge liquor display,a bit disappointed about the cocktails timing arrived to table. ", "Cocktails level. 6/10. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r586584759", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Pricey", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "11 June 2018", "answer_text": ["We really appreciate you taking the time to review your experience with us at Bokan. I am so sorry about the issues with the ladies and please be assured we have briefed the security team on this to ensure they are aware and will certainly address it if it occurs again. The view is amazing though and I am so glad you enjoyed it. I hope to see you back soon. Jacqui & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Talldavem", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "88"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "51"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r586584759-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went with friends on a Saturday evening after a few other \u2018premium bars\u2019 in town and I have to that the entrance was nice, stylish and classy without being too pretentious then the view is amazing! You can right over London with its lights and skyline so well worth it. The bar itself is decent and well in line with others in town although the service can be slow and the cocktails are at best almost half the size of anywhere I\u2019d been during the day yet the priciest I\u2019ve seen in quite a while. But this is London and your basically paying for one of the best views....... a comment I will make to the detriment is that we were twice approached by ladies of a \u2018working disposition\u2019 this didn\u2019t make the ladies in our group comfortable.", "Nice but pricey is my shortened review."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r581296615", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Fantastic location; seriously let down by service", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "19 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you very much for sharing your feedback.We're so sorry to read that we did not fulfill your expectations. Our will is to share and contribute to our guest\u2019s memories so we're obviously disappointed and terribly sorry to hear about your recent experience. What you are describing is certainly not the service we aim for nevertheless, we want to ensure you that each member of our team always strives to provide a high-quality service to every guest without favoritism. We would like to hear more details about your visit so that we can understand what was the exact situation. Feel free to email us at jeevan.thej@accor.com with your full name, date and time of your visit and we would be more than happy to continue this conversation. We do hope to welcome you back soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "rascal021e", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r581296615-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Location and venue amazing - 5 stars - but really let down by poor bar service, particularly by one of the staff on this evening who appeared to discriminate against certain customers in favour of others. He was rude, inept and really tarnished what was a lovely night at a spectacular location. What a shame."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r583008777", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Love this place", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "27 May 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "alexlondon15", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r583008777-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited several times, love the Sunday jazz afternoons on the rooftop. ", "I only had drinks here but will definitely try the restaurant too."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r583025491", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful food and splendid views", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "27 May 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "markhP6094NG", "reviewer_origin": ["Dallas, Texas"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "75"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "38"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r583025491-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Was on a bit of a hunt to find somewhere interesting to eat with the family while staying at the Hilton Canary Wharf. TripAdvisor came through for me. Would have never guessed that such an outstanding restaurant would be part of a Novotel. Restaurant is on the 37th floor, bar on the 38th floor and rooftop open air lounge on the 39th. All with great views back to central London. ", "The food was amazing. We had the tasting menu and kids picked just an entree. 1 or 2 courses a bit heavy on the creamy sauces for my taste, but flavors all good nonetheless. Service was super attentive.", "Can highly recommend this for a romantic dinner as well as after work drinks on the roof with some colleagues."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r583013267", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": " Nice views but service could be better", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "27 May 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JJ_211217", "reviewer_origin": ["Leeds, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r583013267-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited Bokan as part of our stay at the Novotel.", "The Bar offers stunning views of the city and is modern and has a good atmosphere.", "We visited the bar for drinks on Saturday night and our main criticism would be that the security staff were very rude indeed.", "We were told that we could not go up to the roof terrace as it was closed, despite the fact that other couples and individuals were going upstairs.", "The last orders were around 2330. A polite and pleasant member of the bar staff approached us and asked if we wanted anything else, but then around half an hour later, the same rude bouncer approached us and abruptly said \u201cSame goes for you guys, we close at 1am and we want you done and out\u201d. Not even an \u2018excuse me\u2019. ", "Unfortunately, this individual\u2019s attitude ruined our experience. He was unnecessarily rude and abrupt.", "Other than that it was a pleasant bar with good staff, but let down by poor security."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r583463482", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent Bar", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "28 May 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Eddie020173", "reviewer_origin": ["Staines, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1697"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "566"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r583463482-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited this bar whilst staying in the hotel below the bar itself is located on he rooftop of a hotel in the middle of docklands the views are amazing and the staff excellent,", "although the bar is on the rooftop the temperature is ideal"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r580796996", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Appalling, inept service", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "17 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for taking the time to write this review. It is most concerning to read your comments in regards to your recent experience at BOKAN, especially when our team of passionate hospitality professionals is generally a highlight among many of our valued visitors. The service is our priority and we want our guests to have a great and memorable experience with us, therefore, we are terribly sorry to hear about your dissatisfaction. Every feedback is a gem and we would love to have more details about your recent experience. Please feel free to contact us directly at jeevan.thej@accor.com with your full name, date and time of your visit so that we can investigate further address the issue accordingly. We are looking forward to hear back from you soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "papamcb", "reviewer_origin": ["leith"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r580796996-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited as part of office group and service was appalling. Order was taken and laboriously handwritten onto a sheet of paper, then tsrnascripted into the order till. Bar staff are \"supposed\" to print off order and prepare and then waiting staff relay to table. Simples?! Except the wrong drinks were transposed, the bar staff didn't bother to print off order, waiting staff didn't bother to check that it had been started on even after a number of queries about delays and the non-alcoholic cocktails were served with alcohol. And that was after a 55 minute wait. Next round marginally better - except this time the insisted on alcohol free drink (Tequila Sunrise - without tequila) taook 45 minutes to arrive. Lovely venue but a classic case of style over substance. Beyond parody"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r583579655", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Stunning bar, super atmosphere, great service", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "29 May 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Mstravelandiscover", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r583579655-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My friends and I went to Bokan bar, ", "really amazing place in Canary Wharf, the view is stunning and the bar has a wide choose of spirits and cocktails.", "I would like to take the opportunity to thanks again Federico for the birthday cake surprise and to be so welcome to us.", "We will definitely come back soon ", "Highly recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r585263636", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "I've been so many times", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "5 June 2018", "answer_text": ["We always love feedback Er V, especially from our regular guests and we're so sorry to hear that your most recent experience was not consistent with the service we want our guests to receive when they dine with us. Please know that I will share your feedback with our Bar and Restaurant Managers so that they are aware and can address this with the team. We hope that despite this you will return and experience Bokan as we would love to show you that we have addressed this.", "Warm regards,", "Sarah Martin", "Guest Experience Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Er V", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r585263636-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I always visit Bokan because I am simply impressed with the views - they are stunning. We always walk-in and very kind reception ladies try to accommodate and find a table for you. 6 of us went to the restaurant a couple of weeks ago and had an amazing time - bill was \u00a3500 but we had great food, amazing wine. However, let me tell one very important thing - bar team and waitress are always rude (not restaurant's). I never complained to any of the managers but I cannot hide it anymore. The last time I went there - we were 3 ladies and ordered a bottle of wine. The waitress brought 2 glasses only but and I kindly asked to get 1 more glass (obviously). We waited for 15 minutes but there was no one and still didnt get the glass. I went to the bar, no one paid any attention. Then I found the same waitress and again KINDLY asked to get an empty glass because we are 3. She was so arrogant and started to show her embarrassment by saying: \"I told you that I'm bringing it.\" I cannot believe.. I said I cant wait any longer because it has been more than 15 minutes! Then she was putting an order to the till and just ignored me completely. I turned to the bar and waited for anyone to look at me and requested a glass by raising my voice: PLEASE Is anyone can pass me an empty glass? It was such an awkward situation.... After 25 minutes we finally had a possibility to enjoy our wine. Next time I tried to get a recommendation about Riesling wine which they used to have on the old drinks menu. The bartender didn't show any interest in even trying to find my taste. And there is always issues with the bar team and this particular floor - I don't understand why? General manager and restaurant manager need to look into this as I can see from the other reviews - it's happening very often. I think they are all demotivated or tired. To be honest with you, I will try to look for another good place in Canary Wharf on the top floor (didnt try any of other yet) because of this bar and team's attitude as I can't bother anymore - it always changes my mood."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r585947600", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great views", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "8 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Thankyou for your review Luca D and your feedback regarding your experience in Bokan. It's a pleasure to hear that overall you enjoyed your time with us and we look forward to welcoming you back again soon for more negronis!", "Warm regards,", "The team at Bokan"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Luca D", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "26"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r585947600-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["A fantastic location occupying the top 3 floors of the Novotel in Canary Wharf. ", "The interiors are very cool, think of modern post-industrial New York lofts, you get that sense of style immediately as you enter the lifts that what appear to be made out of rusty metal box but are instead lined in a luxury thick wallpaper. ", "The restaurant is on the 37th Floor. We are welcomed with a smile and escorted to our table. the views are great. The food is uncomplicated but sophisticated in its presentation. The grilled octopus is delicious and goes surprisingly well with the served ricotta.The rump is decent but not exceptional.", "After dinner we move to the 38th floor bar for some drinks. Over the next 2hrs I drink 2 negroni and I was a bit disappointed that each time it came garnished differently.", "The roof top terrace on the 39th floor has amazing views across the city but curiously you are not allowed to carry drinks from the bar.", "All in all, a great place and one I am happy to go back to over and over again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r578383868", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Super friendly service", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "6 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Miriam,", "We appreciate a lot your feedback. We always strive to make sure every Guest has a great time with us at Bokan therefore, we are happy to read your positive thoughts. We will inform Antonella about the kind words and we hope to welcome you back soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MiriamG2006", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r578383868-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Bokan is a great spot in London. The view is amazing, and even going to to toilet there is Instagrammable. We wanted to go there for experience, but it was thanks to Antonella that the night was unforgettable. Her service was really friendly and welcoming, and made Bokan seem much more approachable than we though it would be. Definitely looking forward to coming back, especially if she is working!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r576962694", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Worth your time !", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "30 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for the kind words. Your praises and comments on our friendliness are surely one of the best compliments you could ever make to us. We will share the love with the rest of the team and we are looking forward to welcome you again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "phrepe", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r576962694-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I just came back from a nice evening at Bokan. You need to have a budget but you get the unusual view, a nice atmosphere, an interesting deco, a choice of surprising cocktails and the service; Antonella did add a bit of spice to our evening as she combined professionalism with a relaxing sense of humour, a cheerful side and an easy-going way. Happy to enjoy it again. Philippe."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r577884287", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Evening at Bokan", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "4 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Ayman,", "We are glad to hear that our hospitality professionals provided you with caring and attentive service during your visit. All the BOKAN team is very proud to read your kind words.", "When are you coming back, we are already missing you!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ayman E", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r577884287-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I've been in Bokan for a friend meeting and I need to say that the place was amazing. Not only for the view but also for the great waitress Antonella who served us. Professional and kind. The food is incredible and drinking with your friends with a London view can create a nice atmosphere. Recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r580704843", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Really good views, quite good service", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "16 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for taking the time to write this review. We really wish to thank you for your kind comments about our fabulous team. It is always a priority for us to provide a smooth experience to all our guests from the moment they entered BOKAN. It makes us proud to read that you loved our meticulously crafted menu and astonishing views. We can't wait to welcome you back!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Firiurr", "reviewer_origin": ["Palma de Mallorca, Spain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "108"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r580704843-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great rooftop in London. Good service and quality food enjoying really good views.", "Highly recommended experience."]}
