{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r577866111", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Nice food and fantastic view on 34th floor!", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "4 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Bonnie, ", "We are over the moon to read your amazing feedback. It makes us proud to hear that you had a nice time with us at BOKAN. We are looking forward to welcome you again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MariaAlinaC", "reviewer_origin": ["Iasi, Romania"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "48"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "33"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r577866111-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Open until late, great wine , delicious food! We had burgers and some amazing bread with butter before, most delicious one "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r577033534", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great hotel, fancy restaurant!", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "1 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Jan,", "We are over the moon with your amazing feedback. We are glad to here that you enjoyed our meticulously-crafted menu with the astonishing views that our roof-top offers. All the BOKAN team is very proud to read your kind words.", "We hope to see you soon!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jan V", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r577033534-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were staying last weekend in Novotel Canary wharf, on Saturday night, we had table booked for two in Bokan, for my Mrs and I. The dining experience was an excellent one! The Head executive chef Aurelie, was serving and overlooking our table, everything was just spot on, also sous chef Robert was great and his team made their self's proud! Chef Istvan was serving perfectly cooked breakfast at morning buffet. Great service as well! Very friendly,positive, and attentive waiters and waitresses! Fantastic hotel and beautiful view, great staff! I can recommend this place for 100% to everyone! Thank you very much? Novotel Canary wharf, BOKAN."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r578444506", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lovely rooftop bar with Canary Wharf view!", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "7 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Stefano,", "Thank you so much for your lovely feedback! We're glad to hear you had a great time with us and you enjoyed our service. All the BOKAN team is very proud to read your kind words. We look forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "StefanoMalachi", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "213"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "185"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r578444506-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Was here during bank holiday weekend, it was perfect! From the food to cocktails selection, the staff were very friendly and welcoming! The bottomless brunch is a good choice to celebrate the weekend, the rooftop bar is great for private hire such as office / party! The view is amazing, especially when the sun shines in London! Definitely highly recommended and hope to come back soon! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r580063988", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Great view. Overpriced food", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "14 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Suleman,", "Thank you very much for your feedback. We are terribly sorry to hear that we were not able to provide you a memorable experience during your visit at our restaurant. Please allow us to inform you that we are presenting a meticulously crafted menu of locally-sourced ingredients, inspired by our Michelin chef and our prices are reasonable if you take under consideration our unique location. Nevertheless, rest assured that we will take your comments under consideration for the improvement of our performance. We will have a closer look at the email you sent us and we do hope you'll visit us again soon in order to ensure a better experience.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Suleman G", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r580063988-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Me and my friend staying at Novotel, heard great reviews on bokan. When me and my friend got to the restaurant ordered our food and drinks. ", "We where enjoying the amazing views with the drinks we had ordered but where still waiting for the salmon fish and sweet potato fries and Mac and cheese. After 40min waiting for the food we got our mains, just couldn't believe \u00a317 for two small pieces of salmon and small bucket of fries and my friend got his Mac and cheese which had more courgette than anything and was burnt on the sides, looked like a microwaved meal given to my friend. ", "Really enjoyed the views but the food overpriced for small portions, i sent an email to complain but have not received any reply. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r579814192", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "13 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Wow a perfect score! We couldn't be happier from reading your awesome review. It was our great pleasure to make your birthday memorable and we're glad to hear that you enjoyed the atmosphere and service of our restaurant. Our team of passionate hospitality professionals strives to offer the best experience to all our Guests, here at BOKAN. We hope you'll visit us soon, till then!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ashvin307", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r579814192-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife found this little gem for our birthdays and it was brilliant. Unfortunately the weather was not good but otherwise the view would be fantastic. We were very well looked after by the staff and manager. The drinks and bar food was very very good. Definately recommend this place and we will visit again soon. Thank to all the staff for making this a memorable occasion."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r576409478", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "My favorite place in London so far.", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "29 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Alexandre,", "We are over the moon to hear your amazing review. It is quite an honor to be called your favorite place in London and we would like to thank you for the kind words. At BOKAN, it is always our foremost concern to provide a memorable experience to all our guests. Thank you once again for the lovely feedback and for recommending us to your friends.", "Till next time!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Alexandre M", "reviewer_origin": ["Montpellier, Languedoc-Roussillon, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r576409478-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been living for quite a while in London and have been to several restaurant but Bokan is by far my favorite place. ", "The view is simply amazing and I just can not get bored of it.", "The staff is all the time really friendly and helpful. Guillaume is the one to ask when advises are needed, professional and knowledgeable on every aspects. ", "Jerome is the one you want to talk to when wanting to laugh for a while. He always know what to say to make a big smile appear on everyone\u2019s face. ", "The cooking is Mediterranean style, with the French touch that makes the dishes delicious. Aurelie, the French Chef, is always ready to come and answer questions. She is really passionnate and you can feel it when eating her dishes.", "I have recommended Bokan to a lot of my friends and I will come again everytime opportunities appear. ", "Thanks Bokan, those 5 stars are what you deserve !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r572818570", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Service slightly slipping downward", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "12 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Christian,", "Thank you very much for sharing your feedback. At BOKAN, we strive to offer the best experience to all our Guests and are disappointed to hear about your visit. It is most concerning to read your comments in regards to your recent experience, especially when our team's passionate and engaged service is generally a highlight among many of our valued guests. We wish you the best of travels moving forward.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ChristianW273", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r572818570-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I\u2019ve been here many times since it first opened, previous visits have been fantastic, however last night was a bit below par, we had bar food which took quite a while to come out and was staggered, also the waiter was a tad aggressive with his response to incorrect orders insisting that he was right despite the 3 of us saying \u201cno that\u2019s not what we asked for\u201d ", "The customer should always be right, on this occasion we were", "No need to follow up with emails just talk to your staff on the finer points of diplomacy ", "Push the standard up don\u2019t let it slip!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r573361198", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Mediocre...", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "14 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Kristina", "We welcome your feedback as it is the best way to improve our service. It is most concerning to read your comments in regards to your recent experience, especially when our meticulously crafted food menu and attentive service are generally two highlights among many of our valued Guests. In addition to that, we are disappointed to hear that you found our restaurant prices high, but rest assured that our Michelin awarded chef is trying to provide the best selection of locally-sourced products for our Guests in reasonable prices. ", "To sum up, please rest assured that we will take your comments under serious consideration and we will address the team accordingly. Should you wish to share more details, please send us an email at jeevan.thej@accor.com with your full name, date and time of your visit and we would be more than happy to continue this conversation. We wish you all the best."], "reviewer_pseudo": "KristinaA1498", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r573361198-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Came here on a Saturday around 8 for dinner with my boyfriend, and my review in a nutshell:", "Views - 5/5", "Service - 2.5/5", "Food - 3/5", "Without the views... this restaurant is mediocre and not worth the prices.", "We had to wait 20 minutes for the starters - crab and octopus... the crab had way too much going on and wasn't that great. The octopus was very bland and very disappointing. The steak however was fantastic - the only thing I would say is order one above how you normally like it. My boyfriend asked for rare and got it blue, I asked for medium rare and it came rare ... even though it came different to how We asked, we still ate it as it was a fantastic steak.", "The service is appalling! A few of the staff members weren't the friendliest, and seemed to try and get you out as quick as possible. One of the waitresses kept coming over to our table asking if we were finished - she could clearly see we were still eating and done that for both the starter and main. ", "If you did want to visit here, I'd recommend visiting for drinks at the bar to admire the views. I wouldn't recommend the restaurant. It is highly overpriced and the food isn't fantastic."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r572251541", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing Diner ! ", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "9 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Jonathan,", "Wow a perfect score, thank you so much! We're happy to hear that you enjoyed the astonishing views and atmosphere BOKAN has to offer. Thank you for recommending us to future Guests and we hope to welcome you back very soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jonathan P", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r572251541-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Amazing diner, Amazing view, the rooftop are really cool! Perfect for romantic diner or after work with mate ", "highly recommended ! ", "Thanks to the chef ", "JP"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r573336603", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing Saturday evening ", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "14 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you so much for this amazing review! It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed our attentive and caring service along with the panoramic views of the city. All the BOKAN team is very proud to read your kind words and we would like to thank you for considering us one of your favorite bars in the area.", "We can't wait to see you again!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Roli1212", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "53"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r573336603-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Love Bokan! ", "We came here at 6pm, the girls at the reception were really nice (Bulgarian girls) they give us seats straight from the door ", "One of my favourite bars in this area.", "Great service as usual. The view.... sensational... "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r573475669", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect ", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "15 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for taking the time to write this review. It is truly amazing to read that our team of passionate hospitality professionals provided you with attentive, caring service throughout your stay. Our goal is to provide a great level of service and excellent quality of products to ensure a memorable experience for all our Guests. It was a great pleasure having you with us here at BOKAN and thank you once again for this review. ", "Till next time!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Callumdunn", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r573475669-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Me and my girlfriend visited this bar on a Friday afternoon- I would recommend booking a table so you ensure you sit by the window to get the best views. The drinks are in the higher price bracket but well worth it. The staff were brilliant, table service and fizz/wine top ups when you have a bottle. We ordered chips, olives and focaccia with hummus and they were lovely and decent sized portions. Our waiter knocked one of our glasses over and immediately requested a new full glass to the table. All round great experience, will definitely be returning! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r574794804", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "One amazing dinner", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "21 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you so much for your amazing feedback! We're glad to hear you had a great time with us. All the BOKAN Team is very proud to read your kind words. We look forward to welcoming you back soon and thank you for recommending us to future visitors.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ferghal O", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r574794804-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Absolutely cannot speak highly e Pugh about this restaurant on top of Novotel hotel Canary Wharf. Food was absolutely incredible. Service impeccable and the views over London incredible. We absolutely loved the incredible flavours of the food. A must try. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r574026807", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Dinner", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "17 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you so much for your amazing feedback! We're glad to hear you had a great time with us. All the BOKAN Team is very proud to read your kind words. We look forward to welcoming you back again!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "bahi107", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r574026807-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Superb Saturday evening out! I met my friends at Bokan and our table was next to the window. As it was a clear sunny day, the views across London were spectacular during daylight and night time. All three of us loved it. The staff gave us a warm welcome and looked after us very well throughout our visit. Their knowledge about the food and wine pairing was very good. We went for the tasting menu which was amazing. It was a successful evening and cannot wait to go there again. Thank you."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r575024398", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Outstanding place", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "22 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Angelique,", "Wow a perfect score, big thank you for this awesome review! Guest Satisfaction is our foremost concern and our team always strives to provide an experience that will exceed expectations. Therefore, we are very happy to read your kind words. We can't wait to see you soon again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Angelique K", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r575024398-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The food is absolutely delicious with local products, the view of the city is astonishing, always had a warm welcome and service from the staff, the cocktails are inventive and the style and decoration is very trendy. I love this place, coming here as often as possible and never ever disappointed."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r576235066", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Bar service", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "28 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Raimonda,", "Thank you for the feedback. We are terribly sorry to hear that you were dissatisfied with our service during your visit at the rooftop bar. At BOKAN, it is our foremost concern to provide caring and attentive service to all our guests. We would like to hear more in regards to your recent experience in order to better address the issues. Could you please send us an email at jeevan.thej@accor.com wit your full name, date and time of your visit.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Raimonda G", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r576235066-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Horrible service!!! I wais waiting for 40 minuets to order one drink when the bar was totally empty..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r572174148", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Heaven does excit on the 37th floor!!", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "9 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Laurent,", "Well your review is breathtaking! It's quite an honor to be called a must visit place in London for 2018, and we would like to thank you for that. At BOKAN, Guest satisfaction is our foremost concern and our team always strives to provide an experience that will exceed expectations. It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed our signature dishes, presented by our Michelin recognized chef, in reasonable prices if you take under consideration the unique location of BOKAN.", "We would like to thank you once again for your kind words and we can't wait to welcome you again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family "], "reviewer_pseudo": "laurentF447", "reviewer_origin": ["Paris, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "42"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r572174148-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This is probably the one must visit place of London in 2018!! at the top of this hotel is a hidden restaurant called Bokan. The chef has a serious background of fine dining restaurant and you'll will sample a fantastic revisited French diner. The tasting menu is a very good value for money and gives you the chance to try some of the chef signature dishes", "Not to miss the exeptionnal view of London to discover one by one all the famous building when night falls on the city. Great service from a professional team", "Thank you for such a special evening"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r567231628", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "It\u2019s not a dinner it\u2019s an experience !!!! ", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "18 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Well your review is breathtaking! We always strive to make sure every Guest has a great time with us at BOKAN. Thank you once again for sharing your thoughts and for recommending us to future Guests. ", "When are you coming back, we are missing you already!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Lv88", "reviewer_origin": ["Londra"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r567231628-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to Bokan on a Friday night to invite some friends over for dinner and impress them with the kitchen of Chef Aurelie Altemaire! Once again again we were amazed by the unique flavours and textures of her dishes. From the starter to the dessert it\u2019s a journey of surprise and different tastes that will not disappoint you. It\u2019s a place I would definitely recommend if you want to treat yourself or impress someone. The service and the location are an added value to this amazing culinary experience! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r568119180", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic even before you consider the view", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "22 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Adam,", "Thank you so much for your amazing feedback! We're glad to hear you had a great time with us. All the BOKAN team is very proud to read your kind words. We look forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Adam P", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "29"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r568119180-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Situated on the 37th floor of the Novotel near Canary Wharf we were expecting good quality hotel food rather than the beautifully presented and fantastic tasting fine dining experience we got. So often even at a great restaurant there will be the odd dud course but this one was perfect in every respect. By the standards of some of London's Michelin starred restaurants this is right up there and considerably better value too.", "The service and wines were all up to the same standard to make up a great experience with only one little complaint to stop this being perfect. Our complaint (which might be an attraction to some) is that the restaurant is a floor below the bar at the Novotel which is really quite noisy. As such do not go here if you want to enjoy a superb meal in a quiet environment.", "Finally, the view. Just stunning."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r568610021", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Poor service", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "25 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "We appreciate a lot your feedback as we believe it is the best way to identify our flows and improve our service. It is disheartening to hear that you encountered some issues, so please rest assured that we will take your comments under serious consideration and we will address the team accordingly. Thank you once again for sharing your thoughts and we do hope to welcome you again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "abofer", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "39"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r568610021-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Our order could not have been less complicated. 3 coffees with soya milk (bcause of allergy)... At first, it turned out that they just simply forgot to prepare. When I asked, we had to wait for another 30 mins and then guess what.. we got 3 cold coffees with normal milk!!", "We decided not to give 'Terrible' overall rating because after our (semi-loud) complain to the restaurant manager they re-made the coffees and also made it complimentary."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r568352685", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Breakfast, Lunch & Dinner", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "23 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest, ", "Thank you for the kind words. It was our great pleasure to welcome you and we're glad to hear that you had a great time with us. We hope to see you again very soon!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MisaelD980", "reviewer_origin": ["Dallas, Texas"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "91"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r568352685-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This is a breathtaking place that you must visit if ever in this area of London. While the time of day does not matter, you would be amazed by the view of the skyline at night. ", "Go and have a drink!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r568388317", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Food / Atmosphere", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "24 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Wow. Thank you for such an amazing review!! It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed our meticulously crafted menu and the stunning view BOKAN has to offer. Our passionate,hardworking and engaging team always strives to offer the best experience to our Guests. ", "It was a great pleasure having you with us and thank you again for this lovely review. Till next time!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "NHANSEN68", "reviewer_origin": ["Metro Minneapolis-Saint Paul, Minnesota"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "88"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r568388317-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited Bokan for dinner one night while staying at the Novotel (different review). ", "The menu was very modern European and a little different than I was used to as an American traveler that prefers traditional American food - I know, I need to expand my horizons. ", "I wound up having a sirloin and mashed potatoes and they were both very good. The best thing about this experience were the servers - two people worked as a team (guy and a girl) and were fun, happy, enjoyed their job and really made our experience a memorable one. Just super friendly, attentive and professional staff. Couldn\u2019t ask for more.", "This restaurant is on the 37/38 floor of the Novotel. The views of greater London are fantastic. It\u2019s worth stopping by just to see the view."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r569021909", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing views and excellent food", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "27 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Shirley,", "YAY, Big thank you for your awesome review. It was our great pleasure to welcome you and we're glad to hear that you had a great time with us. At BOKAN our passionate hospitality professionals always strive to offer the best experience to all our Guests. We are really flattered to hear that you enjoyed our amazing cocktails, meticulously crafted menu and relaxing atmosphere. Thank you once again for your kinds words and we can't wait to welcome you back.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Shirley R", "reviewer_origin": ["Reading, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "32"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r569021909-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been here twice now - first in July 2017 and then again in Dec17 and I know I will keep coming back again. Whether it\u2019s in summer when you can watch the sun set over the London scene or whether in winter when the sparkling lights of London and the meandering Thames becomes your backdrop to an amazing evening, Bokan never fails to impress.", "Surprisingly, the cocktails are reasonably priced and each and every seat in the restaurant has a amazing view - hell even the bathroom sink\u2019s view doesn\u2019t disappoint.", "The food is great - if I had to pick a few, I would say the beef carpaccio, the rack of lamb and the summer berries cheese cake are a must.", "Above all, what this place offers is a beautiful setting to have a romantic evening or a place to wind down after a long week."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r569916662", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great drinks with a view which deserves a toast", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "31 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "YAY, Big thank you for your awesome review. Our will is to share and contribute to our Guest's memories, so we're thrilled to hear that you had a memorable experience with us. It makes us proud to read that you enjoyed the caring and attentive service we offer, our breathtaking views and meticulously crafted menu. Our passionate, hardworking and engaging team is truly an asset for BOKAN. We are looking forward to welcome you for dinner and thank you for recommending us to other travelers.", "Jeevan & The B\u014dkan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "coffeentraveladdict", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r569916662-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["On my three visits to Bokan I've had a great experience. In terms of location the bar, restaurant and rooftop terraces all offer amazing views across the city overlooking many of the capital's landmarks. The environment is modern and comfortable and our host Veni ensured we found an ideal location from a choice of available spaces. The selection of beers and wines available is extensive and the team demonstrated their deep knowledge to make recommendations which exceeded our expectations. I haven't had the opportunity to dine at Bokan yet but look forward to this with the options on offer. If you want a highlight to your visit to London Docklands Bokan comes highly recommended."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r570055197", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Cannot fault", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "1 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for taking the time to write this review. It is truly amazing to read that our team of passionate hospitality professionals provided you with attentive, caring service throughout your stay. Our goal is to provide a great level of service and excellent quality of products to ensure a memorable experience for all our Guests. It was a great pleasure having you with us here at BOKAN to celebrate your best friend's birthday. Till next time!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "madi600", "reviewer_origin": ["Bracknell, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r570055197-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I came here with my best friend to celebrate a birthday. The menu was amazing and as a pescatarian there was still plenty of seafood and Veg options to chose from. At first glance the prices look a bit expensive ( I\u2019m a student so don\u2019t have a big budget) but when the food arrives you know why it\u2019s priced. I\u2019ve never eaten food with so much flavour before, it was totally worth the money. And the service was amazing, every member of staff made us feel so welcome. Not to mention my friend was given a birthday treat with a selection of mini desserts and a little pastry/ cake to go. ", "Planing on returning later in the year"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r571783276", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Overall poor", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "7 April 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Jonas,", "We appreciate your feedback a lot as we believe it is the best way to identify our flaws and improve our performance. It is most concerning to read your comments in regards to your recent experience with us, especially when our team of passionate and engaged professionals is generally a highlight among many of our valued Guests. We would like to apologize for any inconvenience and we would like to know more about your visit at BOKAN in order to better address the issue. ", "Could you please send us an email at jeevan.thej@accor.com with your full name, date and time of your visit? We are looking forward to hear back from you soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jonas R", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r571783276-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Overall a poor experience, we were three mates looking for quick dinner before going out. Arrived at the restaurant on the 38th floor, there was no hostess to be seen for at least 5 minutes and no one had greeted us, so we decided to make our way to the restaurant which is a floor below, once we got there again there was no one to greet us. After wondering around the restaurant a waiter appeared we asked if we could have a table for three. His response was you need to go back upstairs to the hostess desk and they will allocate you a table. Once we got upstairs there was a lady which didn't seem too happy to see. Anyway she brought us to the table.", "Once at the table we ordered some wine and main courses, friends ordered a fish I ordered steak medium rare. Drinks arrived fast and the waitress was very good, however once the main courses arrived steak was cooked well done. I immediately said it to the waitress however her response was you asked it like this however I will change it, it took some time for my plate to be taken back to the kitchen. While I was waiting for my steak to be redone my mates were enjoying their cod which they mentioned was very good, while they were eating a team of waiters began breaking down one of the communal tables, while this was happening one of the tables fell to the floor making a load noise and getting all of the restaurant to turn around. This was not an appropriate time to be breaking down tables while the restaurant was still half full. There was no presence of management at all.", "Once my food was ready I could see it on the counter, with severel people touching it with their fingers to see if it's cooked properly. (the only person touching it should be the chef).", "Once the food arrived waitress was very sympathetic and apologised for the mistake. However no manager checked if it was okay.", "Once my food arrived my mates were already finished their meal and we're in a rush to go. Also the side of fries that was ordered with the original meal was not changed and was left on the table so once my replacement meal arrived they were already stone cold.", "Anyway overall poor service, limited menu, however has a lot of potential with the right management."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r567059608", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Its becoming a family like experience", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "17 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Rolandas,", "Well your review is breathtaking and we are over the moon to read your amazing compliments! We really wish to say a big thank you for your kind comments about our fabulous team. At Bokan, we always strive to make sure every Guest has a great time with us. ", "When are you coming back, we are missing you already!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "rolandasm654", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r567059608-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["So, those who know me, known how much I LOVE Bokan at Novotel hotel! Coffee \u2615, mid day lunches , mid day drinks, late night drinks , jazz evenings , friends reunions\ufe0f, dates or just chilled afternoons are so far just a few reasons for why I keep ending up on that 38th floor with all them stunning views. ", "The best part of it all- it's becoming almost like visiting a family. Except you obviously have to pay at Bokan... haha! Team is genuinely what makes my every single time so much more exciting and so much better. Veni and Teodora are usually two faces meeting you the moment you step out of elevator and God is it a gorgeous duo! And then there's this young gentleman, who's name I still can't remember for some reason, sorry ( he's having his haircut in Canary Wharf ), but he's your guy if you want not only a good service, but also to explore some of the best cocktails! ", "In summary, I could probably be Bokan's ambassador by now, but I know how important and nice it is to hear about good experiences, not only negative ones. Trust there are not many of those though. Thank you guys "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r563355652", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "28 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Wow a perfect score! We are thrilled to hear you enjoyed every aspect of what we offer. We really wish to say a big thank you for your kind comments about our fabulous team. We are looking forward to welcome you again on our roof top bar.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CoVo13", "reviewer_origin": ["Glasgow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r563355652-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I wasn't sure what to expect and it turned out to be fabulous!", "Lovely welcome, very nice and friendly staff. Amazing food and breathtaking views. I like to dine and experience different places around the world. This is definitely one of my favourites.", "I will be back to explore the roof top bar when the weather improves."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r564377774", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great place for a special occasion", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "4 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Victoria,", "Well your review has us blushing. Our team of passionate hospitality professionals always strives to offer caring and attentive service to all our Guests. It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed our meticulously crafted menu and stunning views BOKAN has to offer. ", "Thank you once again for your kind words and we can't wait to welcome you again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Victoria V", "reviewer_origin": ["Rickmansworth, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r564377774-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for dinner on Saturday night. Great experience from the first minute. The place is excellent in every aspect: breathtaking view over the river and the city, relaxing atmosphere, friendly and attentive staff, superb food. We went for the chef\u2019s tasting menu with every course being a masterpiece. Our special thanks to the sommelier, his vision of pairing made our food journey even more exciting."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r564254480", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Love love love", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "4 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "We are over the moon to read your amazing review. It was our great pleasure to make your boyfriends' birthday memorable and we are glad that you enjoyed our amazing views and fabulous cocktails. When are you coming back, we are missing you already!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "grxcli", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r564254480-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Came here for my boyfriends birthday was staying in the hotel! gorgeous views and fab cocktails xxxx"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r563324172", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic Bar", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "28 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for sharing your impressions. At BOKAN, Guest Satisfaction is our foremost concern and our team always strives to provide an experience that will exceed expectations. We are happy to hear that you enjoyed your visit and thank you for recommending us to future Guests.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jack_Carter1987", "reviewer_origin": ["Scotland, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "102"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "62"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r563324172-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Enjoyed a night here recently. The ambiance is lovely in the bar and the views are spectacular. For those staying in the hotel this is a must visit. Great cocktails, friendly staff. All in all a great place."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r564853059", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great dining experience", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "6 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Well your review is breathtaking. It is always our most treasured reward to make our Guests happy and it was our great pleasure to make your mothers' birthday memorable. We are happy to hear that our team of hospitality professionals provided you with attentive and caring service throughout your dinner. Thank you once again for your kind words and for recommending us to future travelers. Till next time!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Gianangel", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "253"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "75"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r564853059-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I went again to Bokan having had a great dinner a couple of months ago.", "I booked to celebrate my mom's birthday. We went for the tasting menu. Everything was delicious and well executed. Service was great, fast and personalised.", "They even gave us a small cake with a candle as a treat.", "Would definitely go again, and you should too."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r565330501", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Mixed Bag - not great if you have allergies", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "8 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "We appreciate a lot your feedback as we believe it is the best way for us to improve our performance. At Bokan, everyday we aim to offer the best experience to all our Guests, therefore what you are describing is certainly not the level of service we aim for. It is most concerning to read your comments in regards to your food intolerance issues, especially when our team's passionate and engaged service is generally a highlight among many of our valued Guests. We are sorry to hear that you felt you were not receiving a high level of attention, however our team treats always in a discreet way any Guest who has specific dietary restrictions. Could you please send us an email at jeevan.thej@accor.com with your full name, date and time of your visit so we can look further into it?", "In any case, we would like to inform you that your comments will be taken under serious consideration and we will address the team accordingly. We do hope to welcome you again.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Tiff113", "reviewer_origin": ["Skipton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "37"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r565330501-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I was staying in the hotel so reception kindly booked me a table. I stated I had food intolerances upon booking and this was noted. I was greeted and shown to a table and although initially service was attentive I was not given guidance on allergens in the menu and I had to try ordering a few options until I got one I could have. I would have expected the waiter to be more clued up on allergens and to be more helpful. It\u2019s not like it\u2019s a cheap restaurant. When my steak came the meat was cooked medium rare as requested but it wasn\u2019t a good piece of meat and was quite chewy. I\u2019m from a farming family so I know good steak and that wasn\u2019t the quality I\u2019d expect at a restaurant of this calibre. Something had been excluded from the dish due to my gluten intolerance but that had not been pointed out when I ordered. So, great that it was omitted however this should have been mentioned at the time of ordering. The \u201cAmuse Bouche\u201d was just brought to me and I had to request the waiter check the ingredients before I had it - again disappointing. I actually felt like I was a pain to the servers because of my allergies and other tables seemed to get more attentive service as I was sat there with an empty glass for ages and being ignored. All in all, great views, nice wine list but below par steak and below par service - specifically around allergens. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r566883676", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delicious ", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "16 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "YAY, Big thank you for your awesome review. It was our great pleasure to make you feel special during your visit. At BOKAN, our mission is to offer a memorable experience to all our Guests and exceed their expectations. We are proud to hear that you enjoyed our meticulously crafted menu along with the attentive and caring service from our fabulous team. We can't wait to welcome you again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "dazzer2001", "reviewer_origin": ["Rochford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "196"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "92"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r566883676-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We stayed at the hotel and booked a table before,which I feel is a must as this bar is very very busy.", "Upon arrival we had welcoming that was warm and relaxing. Shown to the table by the window which has amazing views over London.", "The waitress was friendly and really really knew her cocktails.", "I had the burger and was so so delicious and cooked exactly how I wanted it. My wife had the mac and cheese. Now I\u2019m not into M and C but tasted this and really enjoyed the bit I had. Presentation was excellent and the meals where reasonable price for London.", "We spent most of the night having cocktails and really didn\u2019t want to leave the table as you feel relaxed here and just ended up enjoying ourselves that much.", "The price was right for all the food and drinks.", "Definitely will return and hopefully have another excellent meal and drinks. ", "Just to say thank you to our waitress who made the night a special one on her knowledge and friendliness."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r566614213", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great place ", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "15 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you very much for the amazing feedback. It was our great pleasure to welcome you and we are glad to hear that you enjoyed our meticulously crafted menu, breathtaking views and amazing atmosphere. We are looking forward to see you again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "155nikv", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r566614213-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Amazing restaurant, food, atmosphere and service was outstanding. You also have great views of London city. Even the toilets are fantastic. It is pricey, so it would definitely be one of those special occasion places you go to. - the lamb main was some of the best lamb I\u2019ve had. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r565619016", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Great view - shame about the food", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "10 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for your comment as we believe that Guest feedback is the best way to identify our flaws and improve our service. It is most concerning to read your comments in regards to your recent experience, especially when our meticulously crafted food menu is generally a highlight among many of our valued Guests. Please rest assured that we will take your comments under serious consideration and we will address the team accordingly. Should you wish to share more details, please send us an email at jeevan.thej@accor.com with your full name, date and time of your visit. We wish you all the best.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "jac1999", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "84"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "80"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r565619016-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went here a couple of days ago and has the tasting menu. Whilst the drinks were great and the views fabulous the food was disappointing. In one dish, coffee overpowered an over cooked and underwhelming piece of veal. In another grey dish, truffle dominated a fake celeriac pasta tube. It was almost universally disliked by my party. Dessert was a drab affair; some off-the-shelf chocolate three ways. ", "The was only one was for me, and that was towards the exit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r563120344", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "A couple of key points for reference", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "27 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you so much for taking the time to write this review. We welcome and encourage feedback as only through that we are able to gauge how guests perceive our service and facilities. The service is our priority and we want all our visitors to have a great and memorable experience with us. Therefore, we are terribly sorry to hear that it was not the case for you last Saturday evening. Please allow us to inform you that the satisfaction of our Guests is our foremost concern and our team always strives to show its utmost consideration and empathy. Consequently, what you are describing is certainly not the level of service we aim for. It is true that sometimes our bar can get busy however, we can ensure you that our staff tries to provide attentive and caring service to all visitors without ignoring anyone. We would like to hear more about your experience in order to properly address these issues. Could you please send us an email at jeevan.thej@accor.com with your full name and time of your visit to further continue this conversation? ", "We are looking forward to hear back from you soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "angelinahuxleys", "reviewer_origin": ["Manama, Bahrain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r563120344-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Good afternoon Jeevan, ", "Saturday night .. 24 February . we are a couple, i am Romanian by origin, British national my boyfriend is Saudi Arabian, future husband , we had celebrated our engagement and love . Unfortunately we had a really bad experience from beginning at Bokan Bar . We came to the bar as we heard is a really good one .", "1) The location is too out of reach , it means that I have to take in consideration to locate the venue . The transport is not a problem . Anyway this was not the main one reason . ", "2) The main reason why I do this review is when we got to the mini reception Bokan bar upstairs, we needed to greet the staff not her to greet us . She finished with the ex client taking care of their coats, etc, then we asked for a table, she was in rush saying i wlll find one for you next to the window. She went to find something, we were following her as we didnt know what to do, wait at reception or what / she stops at one table and start chit chat with that clients or friends . She forgot about us or what? we dont meean to be rude, but finally we asked her, excuse me could we have a table please ? the second time. she got nervous and said oh sorry about it , let me find then she starts moving . Finally she gave us a table opposite the bar , no view. Then she ignores us again. ", "Thats reception girl. ", "3) we ordered finally our drinks and we were happy we got the table.... till we got water x 3 times and the drinks didn't arrive. We asked for the drinks but we felt completely IGNORED We were waiting more than 25 Minutes there . ", "4 ) Finally we decided to leave the place... no drinks, no customer service, nothing. Most of luxury bars they serve nuts or small snack as beginning free or as from the menu and have been asked by waitress.", "What is missing ? The Bokan Bar is a very highly recognized Bar in London. You guys are competing with the bars and hotels around you The Pearson Room , Cinnamon restaurant Hilton, Scoff and Banter in Edwardian, etc but I have never had this kind of experience nowhere in such as 4 stars bar and Hotel . I have stayed in Dubai in Novotel, in Bahrain, and other places but never had this experience in my life. We travel a lot and stay in 5 stars hotels. ", "I would really want to come back but the customer service destroyed our evening. ", "And not the last one , we needed to spent time to get a taxi to re arrange our night out in the same time, time , energy, not good night out , money the last ... we lost . ", "I believe to get good customer service you need to have good waitress and waiters who works in team and for the same goal to achieve the highly customer service and make each customer happy in order a business to be run properly. if you want keep your clients and business of course . That is a priority. ", "very dissapointing"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r559678901", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Best view is at night", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "10 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you so much for your feedback. We're happy to hear that you appreciated the astonishing view and meticulously crafted menu BOKAN has to offer. Please allow us to inform you that we are providing an excellent quality of drinks and food, presented by our Michelin recognized chef, in reasonable prices if you take under consideration our unique location in London. Nevertheless, rest assured that we take your comments under serious consideration and we will address the team according. ", "We do hope you'll visit us again soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JH72", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1168"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "662"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r559678901-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Four of us went to Bokan. Great views at night seeing London lit up. The service was great and the food very well presented and tasted superb. The views are beautiful. Bottle of wine, 4 beers, 2 tasting menus and 2 a la carte menus with starters, main and desserts \u00a3332 so not the cheapest place to eat out on a Saturday night. Not a child friendly place really as it\u2019s quite grown up and adult. 12.5% added automatically. Our last course was forgotten about on the tasting menu so we had to ask. No big bother really. Sweetbreads were deep fried and tasty. I think these were the pancreas gland ones due to the shape and not the thymus gland ones from the throat."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r559656890", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Absolutely amazing", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "10 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Rolandas,", "YAY, Big thank you for your awesome review. It is always a priority for us to provide a smooth experience to all our Guests from the moment they entered our surroundings. It makes us proud to read that you loved our service, high quality food and amazing cocktails. All the BOKAN team is very proud to read your kind words. ", "Thank you once again for this amazing review and we can't wait to host you again with your friend. Till next time!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "rolandasm654", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r559656890-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to this new and beautiful place at Novotel, Boka. Absolutely amazing experience, staff is super welcoming and friendly, great cocktails and fantastic food. In fact, taking my friend for an afternoon coffee back to Boka tomorrow afternoon "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r559731961", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best cocktails and better views than any rooftop bar! ", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "11 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Chlo\u00eb,", "Wow a perfect score! We couldn't be happier from reading your awesome review. We are very excited to hear that you enjoyed our unique panoramic view of the London skyline and amazing collection of cocktail drinks. ", "We hope you'll visit us soon, till then!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "chlo_m820", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r559731961-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Hidden gem in the heart of canary whalf. Ditch the tall well known rooftop bars for something more unique and stunning views of the London skyline. Must try cocktail called isle chapel which tasted like a lemon meringue pudding! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r561765319", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food with an amazing view", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "20 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Mark,", "Wow, a perfect score! We're thrilled to hear you enjoyed every aspect of what we offer. It was our pleasure to make your Valentine's Day memorable and thank you for recommending us to future Guests'. ", "We can't wait to welcome you and your wife again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Mark D", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r561765319-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife and I thoroughly enjoyed this 2nd visit to Bokan to celebrate Valentine's Day. Very warm welcome! We went for the tasting menu which was excellent. Amazing view looking West towards the City at night. Not pretentious at all. No pressure to move off the table. Strongly recommend."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r561913510", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Cocktails for every taste", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "21 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Elitsa,", "We appreciate a lot your kind words. At BOKAN, we always strive to make sure every Guest has a great time with us. Thank you once again for sharing your thoughts and we hope to welcome you back.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "EliDimitranova", "reviewer_origin": ["Sofia, Bulgaria"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r561913510-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This place offers the best view and variety of tasty cocktails. A lot of people are visiting this bar after work "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r561212953", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Outstanding food amazing view", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "18 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "We\u2019re over the moon to hear your amazing review. It was our great pleasure to make your birthday memorable. It is truly amazing to read that our team of passionate hospitality professionals provided you with attentive, caring service throughout your stay. At BOKAN we always strive to make every Guest feel special from the moment they pass through our door. ", "Thank you for your kinds words and we can\u2019t wait to welcome you back again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "AnasHcayat", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "208"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "36"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r561212953-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Super high quality of food, great service and amazing view.", "Nevertheless what I loved is that the venue and the service is not pretentious, it feels warm confy and friendly.", "I went there for my birthday we took the chief d\u00e9gustation menu, just superb I recommend taking the matching wines "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r562125261", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent in every way", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "22 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "We're over the moon to read your amazing feedback. It was our great pleasure to provide you with a memorable experience and we would like to thank you for appreciating our meticulously crafted menu and astonishing views. Your praises and comments on our friendliness are surely one of the best compliments you could ever make to us. All the BOKAN team is very proud to read your kind words. When are you coming back, we're missing you already!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lb414", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r562125261-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I recently dined with a group of 15 of us for lunch and the meal was perfect in every way. Firstly, the staff could not be more friendly and were superb in tending to the table. Secondly, the restaurant offers exceptional views which give The Shard and Heron Tower a run for their money! Finally, the food was exquisite - not only is the presentation a wow factor (every course was Insta-worthy!), but it was delicious, fresh and cooked to perfection. I would say given the quality, it is very good value for money.", "Thanks Bokan for a memorable lunch and we'll be back soon!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r562544020", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Stylish on 38th floor, but service should never...", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "24 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you very much for your feedback. It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed the strategic location of our hotel and our special industrial design. We're sorry to read that you were disappointed with the service but rest assured that our team of passionate hospitality professionals always strive to offer a memorable experience to all Guests'. We do hope to welcome you back again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MikQuadrat", "reviewer_origin": ["Konigstein im Taunus, Germany"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r562544020-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["... say \u201eit\u2018s not my fault!\u201c when they failed to deliver drinks even after two reminder. This was disappointing.", "However, location is great and offers a nice view towards London City. Interior is stylish, a mixture if wood and metal."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r562946410", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Pricy, good views and good for a date", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "26 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for taking the time to write this review. We're glad that you were overall satisfied with the amazing view and unique selection of cocktails that BOKAN has to offer. We are sorry to hear that you found our cocktail prices high, but rest assured that we strive to offer excellent quality of drinks in reasonable prices if you take under consideration the unique location of our bar, which offers panoramic views of London. ", "We are looking forward to welcome you again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ife f", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "83"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "36"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r562946410-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["went for drinks. great views of London. best to search around for a place to sit or book table in advance. its in the middle of nowhere and the area is a bit dead at the weekend. ", "drinks were so yummy but also expensive. ", "lots of different types of alcohol"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r559069237", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "7 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Natalie,", "We're over the moon to hear your amazing review. Our team of passionate hospitality professionals always strives to offer a memorable experience to all our Guests. We appreciate a lot your kind words and we're happy to hear that you enjoyed your time with us. Till next time!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "nataliegrimston", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r559069237-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I had a most enjoyable burger cooked exactly how I wanted it cooked, bravo ", "Wine was no more expensive than I would of paid at any bar in Canary Wharf let a lone a hotel - most enjoyable evening "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r555501596", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Dinner at Bokan 37", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "22 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Wow. Thank you for such an amazing review. It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed our meticulously crafted menu and the stunning view BOKAN has to offer. Our passionate,hardworking and engaging team always strives to offer the best experience to our Guests. It was a great pleasure having you with us and thank you again for this lovely review. ", "Till next time!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Puffertwin", "reviewer_origin": ["Birmingham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r555501596-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What a great place to visit. The views were on the 38/39 floors of the associated Novotel Canary Wharf and you pretty much had a wrap around view of the city. There is an outside deck area too, which will be amazing when they get the outdoor heating in place.", "Food was served with style and the servers were very well versed and knowledgable about the menu. He presented our plates, and explained them to us all so we knew what they were. They looked stunning and tasted even better. ", "As the evening progresses it starts to morph in to a bar, so you can comfortable have dinner and stay for more drinks without having to leave. Is definitely worth a 2nd visit, and a 3rd and more."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r554287301", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic diner", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "16 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest, ", "Yay, Big thank you for your awesome review. It was our great pleasure to make your dinner memorable. It is truly amazing to read that our team of passionate hospitality professionals provided you with attentive, caring service throughout the evening. At BOKAN we always strive to make every Guest feel special from the moment they passed through the door. Many thanks!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "arsenal7533", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "167"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "90"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r554287301-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had diner with 5 friends at Bokan. First of all the view is breathtaking. The service is impeccable and friendly. The sommelier is just great. We described the type of wine we enjoy and he made us discover a South African amazing wine that we all loved. Food is excellent. We all loved Bokan and will go back soon. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r554216124", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing dinner", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "16 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Adrien, ", "Wow. Thank you for such an amazing review. It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed our meticulously crafted menu and the stunning view BOKAN has to offer. We're really flattered to read that everything was perfect during your dinner and we do hope you will visit us again soon!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Adrien A", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r554216124-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Everything was perfect.", "From the beginning to the end .", "The scallops with celery and black pudding was fabulous.", "The view is amazing.", "Thanks to all the team ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r555413498", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Panoramic view is all when dining", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "22 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "We always strive to improve our services therefore, your feedback is very much appreciated. We read very carefully your observations and we will share them with our team. Please rest assured that this is not a true reflection of our service standards.", "We are looking forward to welcoming you back in order to ensure a better experience for you!", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "endis", "reviewer_origin": ["Vilnius, Lithuania"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "330"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "262"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r555413498-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We (6 persons) dined here before Christmas. Service was good, no complaints about starters, however welcome starters were very simple for the restaurant level (warm breads with selection of butters), wine list is on a pricey side. The biggest disappointment were main course - beef entrecote ordered medium arrived completely overdone and dry. Octopus was well prepared and not gummy. Avoid the area near the open kitchen, better get seated further away because of heat. Maybe a wrong day for us to visit ? Will give it another try at Easter."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r556664210", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Dinner with a view", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "27 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Neil,", "Thank you so much for your amazing feedback. Your praises and comments on our professionalism and friendliness are surely two of the best compliments you could ever make to us. It was our great pleasure to welcome you and we're glad to hear that you had a great time. Please allow us to inform you that at BOKAN we're always trying to provide the best quality of service and products at the most reasonable prices. ", "We look forward to welcoming you back very soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "NeilPike", "reviewer_origin": ["St Albans, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "373"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "121"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r556664210-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Fabulous views, delicious food stylishly presented by professional and friendly staff. As you'd expect the price is reflective of this, especially the wine-list - excellent sommelier though."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r556747839", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Great location, Poor service", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "27 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for taking the time to write this review. The service is our priority and we want our guests to have a great and memorable experience with us, therefore, we are terribly sorry to hear about your dissatisfaction. Every feedback is a gem and we would love to have more details about your experience. Please feel free to contact us directly so that we can address the issue accordingly. ", "We hope you'll visit us again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MssDillinger", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r556747839-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Is not the first time we are going to the bar at Novotel Canary Wharf. The location and views are amazing, but the service we always find is rude and very inefficient. ", "They seem not happy with their job, always in rush and they have no time even for say hello when you are arriving to the place"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r558603304", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good Views but they need to work on the bookings", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "5 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Sophie,", "Thank you very much for sharing your feedback. We're terribly sorry to hear about your disappointing experience. Everyday we strive to offer the best experience to all our Guests, therefore what you are describing is not the level of service we aim for. Please allow us to clarify that our brunch commence at 12.30 and finishes at 14.30, in order to avoid any future misunderstandings. ", "We are sorry to hear that you experienced difficulties in terms of communication; our team is consisted of people from all over the world which is very common in the hospitality industry. Therefore for some of our team members English may not be their native language but they are fluent English speakers and always willing to assist in any possible way. ", "Every feedback is a gem and we would love to hear more about the issues you've encountered so that we can address the team accordingly. Could you please send us an email at jeevan.thej@accor.com with your full name, date and time of your visit, so we can look further into this? ", "We apologize for any inconvenience and we're looking forward to hear back from you soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "109sophiea", "reviewer_origin": ["Sutton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "191"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "174"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "20", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r558603304-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The view is lovely, as is the food. You enter the building prime time on a Saturday afternoon and expect to see someone on the podium of the entrance but there isn't. So you have to work out for yourself how to use the lift and which floor you need to go to. We ended up in the bar, but the woman at reception couldn't understand a word we was saying. Despite us being locals. She thought we was wanting to book a table, despite us repeatedly saying \"we are here for our 2pm booking\". Then we was seated in the bar area at a table that was practically on the floor. I asked to be moved to a table where we wouldnt have to eat with our food on our laps. He then gave us a bar menu. We asked if we could have the brunch menu which we booked for. He said this was downstairs but the brunch was now over. I advised I had checked online and that I was sure the last SEATING for brunch was 2pm and it started at 12. However it get very confusing as he couldn't really understand what we was saying either. We were just about to leave when we checked to say are you sure we cannot have a table and he said that we could but we had to order as the kitchen takes the last orders for brunch at 2:30pm. Finally when we got around it all we had a table booked downstairs and we were able to enjoy the meal however, it was a lot of stress for us."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r558635716", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Poor and slow service", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "5 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Jing,", "Our will is to share and contribute to our Guest\u2019s memories so we're obviously disappointed and terribly sorry for any inconvenience caused to you.We can assure you that this is not a true reflection of the service we want to offer here at BOKAN. Unfortunately, our bar/restaurant can get busy sometimes, nevertheless we want to ensure you that our staff always strives to provide a high-quality service. We would love to hear more details about your visit so that we can better address the situation.If you wish, please send us an email at jeevan.thej@accor.com. ", "We do hope to welcome you back soon.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "kisaalicat", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r558635716-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We want to have some drinks and food around canary wharf area, apparently Bokan is the highest bar/restaurant within the area so we decided to check it out.", "It takes 20 minutes for the staff to come to the table saying a \"Hi\" and take orders..", "The whole atmosphere with the service we felt no difference than going to weatherspoon or other pubs. The food was ok, takes ages to wait for our drinks. No waiter or waitress come to ask if we need another drink. Someone finally came to clear the table after the empty plates on the table for quite long time..We decided to leave and we have to walk to the bar to ask for the bill. And we paid the bill with the full service charge while we didn't felt it was worth it.", "Anyway, will not recommend it to any of our clients or friends."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r558888412", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Cracking views from 38th floor", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "6 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you very much for sharing your feedback. It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed our meticulously crafted menu and the stunning view BOKAN has to offer. Please feel free to reach out to us should you wish to share any detailed concerns and we will be more than happy to listen. We do hope to welcome you back again.", "Jeevan & The BOKAN Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Beejay993", "reviewer_origin": ["Aberdeen, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r558888412-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice restaurant, service a bit impersonal but efficient. Menu limited but nice. Food presentation was outstanding and very nice."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r550647915", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "New Years Eve fun", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "1 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Gary,", "Thank you for taking the time to write this amazing review. Your praises and comments on our friendliness are surely one of the best compliments you could ever make to us. It was our great pleasure to welcome you and we're glad to hear that you had a great time with us. We will share the love with our Fabulous Team and we are looking forward to welcome you again soon. Have a Happy New Year!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GaryJamesC", "reviewer_origin": ["Stockton-on-Tees, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r550647915-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were here for the New Years Eve 6 course tasting meal and can only praise the restaurant for the very well organised evening. The entertainment was great and the food exceptional while the staff were very friendly but also lively and fun making it a really warm atmosphere. The views across London in all directions are worth making a visit for, in themselves. Well done all involved at Bokan, we had a great time. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r546569341", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Sunday evening dinner with friends", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "11 December 2017", "answer_text": ["We're terribly sorry to hear about your disappointing experience. Everyday we strive to offer the best experience to all our guests, therefore what you are describing is not the level of service we aim for. Please know that we take your comments under serious consideration and we will address the team accordingly. We do hope to welcome you back soon in order to ensure a better experience.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MoonLanding", "reviewer_origin": ["Whitchurch, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "253"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "56"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r546569341-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["On a recommendation, we made a reservation for dinner on the 38th floor!!! Great ambience and views. Not exceptionally busy, but service was slow and laborious. Not many menu choices, but choices made. Again, service was slow and one member of party returned their main course which was cold (Not under cooked) for reheating. Overall, very disappointed."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r546282222", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Solid 3*", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "9 December 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your comment. We're so sorry to hear we did not fulfil your expectations.The satisfaction of our guests is our first concern and our team always shows their utmost consideration and empathy. We will share your feedback with our team in order to ensure that we continue to improve our services. We hope to welcome you back soon in order to ensure a better experience.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "PeanutButterJellyTom", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r546282222-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for drinks only. Amazing views, nice ambience, nice drinks. Thoroughly enjoyed it.", "That said, the service was very slow (& they struggled to actually charge us for all of our drinks...) and also our cocktails were inconsistent. The same drink ordered twice came once on the rocks and once in a martini glass. Odd. Probably the upstairs and downstairs bars were working differently..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r547507053", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "My Birthday", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "16 December 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Terence,", "We would like to thank you for sharing your feedback. Our will is to contribute to our guest\u2019s memories so we're obviously disappointed that we didn't meet your expectations. Our goal is to provide a great level of service and excellent quality of products. It is most concerning to read your comments in regards to the level of our service, especially when our team's passionate and engaged service is generally a highlight among many of our valued guests. Also we take great pride of our menu since our chef strives to create unique dishes by using the best quality of products, mostly from local producers. Thank you again for your review so we can ensure we are continually bettering our service for our future guests.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Terence M", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r547507053-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The ONLY reason for going to this restaurant is for the view, which is really wonderful. from the top of this tower, especially at night, you have extensive views of the lights and sights of one of the great cities of the world. Enjoy this!", "It certainly is not the place for a romantic dinner. As far as we could figure, the highest floor comprises a bar with bookable table seating, with a limited bar menu, and VERY loud music. No conversation possible. On the floor below, down a short staircase, is the main restaurant, where we were booked. The 'music' noise from above resounds, but the volume is thankfully lower. Although is was Friday, and a couple of weeks before Christmas, this lower area was sparsely populated. This was a surprise.", "The menu, in our opinion, is very limited and fairly boring. The service is not too bad, but rather mechanical: eg. you are asked if you are 'enjoying' at critical points. The food is nicely and artistically presented on the plates, but too our surprise is not vey tasty. 'BLAND\" is the word that came to mind. My first course was 'Octpus and Beetroot\" and it was hard to get the taste of either of these components. Seemed like it had been boiled for hours. Second course was lamb which was equally 'non-lamby' in taste. The wine list was all highly priced, and from unknown vineyards. We had a Spanish wine from an area with which we are familiar. The wine was good, in that it had no bad qualities, but not much going for it either. BUT THE VIEW FROM THE RESTAURANT IS FANTASTIC. A meal for two with wine set us back \u00a3175. I rationalise this as good value, being \u00a3125 for the view and \u00a350 for the rest."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r546964579", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sunday brunch was lovely!!!", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "13 December 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Veronika,", "Your praises and comments on our friendliness are surely one of the best compliments you could ever make to us. It was our great pleasure to welcome you and we're glad to hear that you had a great time with us. We will share the love with our Fabulous Team and we are looking forward to welcome you back soon!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "veronikag402", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r546964579-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["On Sunday I have been in this lovely restaurant with my danish friend for brunch. Even though the price \u00a349 per person, it\u2019s worth. Firstly for extremely amazing view, second delicious food with touch of French cuisine , which I am totally in love. Also, prosecco included in the brunch menu. So, definitely will be back. By the way, staff especially receptionist Veni was extremely welcoming and polite. Many thanks for making our time even more nice. Totally in love with this place\u2764\ufe0f\u2764\ufe0f\u2764\ufe0f"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r547633070", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Incredible view, everything else average", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "17 December 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for sharing your feedback. The satisfaction of our Guests is our first concern and our Team always shows their utmost consideration and empathy. What you are describing is not the level of service we aim for and we would like to apologise for your disappointed experience. Thank you once again for sharing your thoughts with us and we hope to welcome you back to our restaurant soon.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lewispb", "reviewer_origin": ["Bristol, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r547633070-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The view of London is lovely. The food is mediocre, limited choice and the service was arrogant. Very expensive, 2 courses with wine was around \u00a375 per person. Food was rather bland."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r547712452", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Christmas drinks and canapes", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "17 December 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for this incredible review! It was our great pleasure to welcome you and we're glad to hear that you had a great time with us. We will share the love with our Fabulous Team. Many thanks.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sejal P", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r547712452-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Amazing views and ambience. Extremely attentive staff, especially Peter @ the bar. Food and drinks very good."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r547894231", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Dissapointed", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "18 December 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for taking the time to provide our team with feedback. The satisfaction of our Guests is our first concern and our Team always shows their utmost consideration and empathy. We are disappointed to hear that our restaurant didn't meet your expectations. Thank you once again for sharing your thoughts with us and we hope to welcome you back to our restaurant.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "guest0217", "reviewer_origin": ["Stockholm, Sweden"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r547894231-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice view, good food, but extremely loud due to dinner party in the restaurant. At times, it was impossible to understand the people sitting in front of you. Very unfortunate, were looking forward to a nice dinner."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r550533237", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "New Year's Eve at Bokan", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "31 December 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Roy,", "Thank you for your amazing review. Your praises and comments on our friendliness are surely one of the best compliments you could ever make to us. It was our great pleasure to make your New Year's Eve memorable. All the B\u014cKAN team is very proud to read your kind words and we will be sure to share the love with Peter for doing such a great job. We are looking forward to welcome you back soon.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Roy J", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r550533237-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Absolutely great night service was amazing from when we arrived great table with wonderful view of the fireworks and London great service in regards to the drinks our waiter Peter was absolutely spot on and nothing was too much trouble we live local so will be back on a more regular occasion thanks Peter for starting our 2018 the way we expected see you soon "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r549297763", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Wonderful view, but ...", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "26 December 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for sharing your feedback. It is disheartening to read that we could not provide a memorable experience for you during your stay and wish you only the best of travels moving forward. The satisfaction of our Guests is our first concern and our Team always shows their utmost consideration and empathy. Please know that we take your comments under serious consideration and we will address the team accordingly. We do hope to welcome you back soon.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Andrew R", "reviewer_origin": ["Gillingham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "132"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r549297763-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Fantastic views from the top floor of Novotel Canary wharf, looking back towards the centre of London. Ordered 2 drinks, cider and one of their cocktails, plus chips to snack. Drinks and mayonnaise/tomato sauce arrived promptly. Had our drinks, no sign of chips, waited and waited, the waitress came over to take away empty drinks, said haven't you got your chips ... no ... she went away, and they arrived soon after, so obviously forgotten about. Bill came to \u00a326 so expensive for 2 drinks and chips."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r542687200", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Bellowed at over bar food", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "22 November 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review. We are sorry to hear we did not fulfil your expectations. Our restaurant is usually very busy, therefore we always recommend to our guests to book a table in advance. Also we are disappointed that you didn't enjoy the live music, since we receive mostly positive feedback in regards to the events that we organise, including bands and dj's at Bokan. We will take your feedback under consideration and we do hope to welcome you again soon in order to ensure a better experience.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "J P S", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "228"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "67"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r542687200-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I was taken there for my birthday. The restaurant was full until 9pm, and so we had to settle for the bar. The place was very dark, and finding the table was not the say (for me, anyway). The awful din emitted by a woman squealing into a microphone (they tell me that it is singing; but it has nothing in common with Covent Garden) was so loud because, apparently, it has to carry over three floors in the building. The occasional breaks which she and her organ grinders took were the best bit - I could hear what was being said to me.", "I was not impressed by the requirement to hand over my bank card before an order could be taken. What might have been done with it while it was out of my sight was a concern, although it seems to have been all right. Clearly, this Novotel has had more than its share of dodgy customers, although how they could escape easily from the 38th floor was a mystery to me.", "I was assured that the food in the restaurant is better than what is available in the bar. This view was shared by our waiter. In my view, the meal was significantly overpriced", "The views across London were certainly breathtaking but, apart from the wonderful company I was in, these were the best part of the evening. If I could get into the restaurant itself on a quiet night (i.e. no squealing) I might try it again, but otherwise, for me, it lies between the very disappointing and a ripoff"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r542276462", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Great views - Terrible Service from Front of Desk woman!!", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "20 November 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Zeena,", "Thank you so much for your feedback. We're terribly sorry about your disappointing experience. We can assure you that this is not a true reflection of the service we want to offer here at Bokan and Novotel London Canary Wharf. I would very much appreciate if you can send me an email at jeevan.thej@accor.com with your full name, date and time that you visited us so that I investigate further the situation and address the issue accordingly. I hope to hear back from you soon!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "90zeenab", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r542276462-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked Bokan as we had visited previously and thought the place had a wow factor. We had our nephew and niece visiting from Switzerland and wanted to share a special evening with them. The evening was ruined by the woman at the front desk (Julia?) who is quite frankly the rudest person we have ever had the misfortune to encounter in any restaurant. Despite having received an email confirming our booking she kept us standing in the corridor for 10 mins and kept insisting that we did not have a booking!! I even showed her the email. She was disingenuous and disinterested. In the end I asked to see her booking screen and was able to locate the booking immediately. She had no sense of how much embarrassment and upset she was causing to us all. She didn\u2019t even apologise for her error. Atrocious level of service from her. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r542608129", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing meal", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "22 November 2017", "answer_text": ["Well your review fantastic! Thank you so much for your kind words and for choosing Bokan to spend your boyfriend's special day! Great to hear you liked our restaurant and our fabulous team. Hope to see you soon!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Harrietgracem", "reviewer_origin": ["Guildford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r542608129-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Took my boyfriend here for his birthday (as we were staying in the hotel) before going to see Micky Flanagan at the O2. Mushroom risotto was to die for- best meal of my life, views were stunning and staff were lovely!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r542384579", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great rooftop bar", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "21 November 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your feedback! It was our great pleasure to welcome you and we're glad to hear that you had a great time with us and you enjoyed the drinks and the view! Hope to see you soon!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LGBfund", "reviewer_origin": ["Epsom, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "403"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "119"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r542384579-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What a great venue with amazing views over London / Canary Wharf", "Ideal for a quick drink before heading out or even if you want to stay in and enjoy the views.", "We used the bar here a couple of times during our stay, enjoying the setting sun over London, and London by night when we returned to the hotel.", "The bar is very busy in the evenings and it can be hard to find a seat, but we managed to find an area outside to enjoy the last of the evening, and even enjoyed a complimentary drink from the bar.", "Great venue, and worth heading to for the views."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r542859799", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Cold English Breakfast ", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "23 November 2017", "answer_text": ["We would like to thank you for sharing your feedback. At BOKAN we are concentrating our efforts towards a common goal, making every meal a unique and unforgettable experience and we are very disappointed to hear about your experience with us. Rest assured that our breakfast buffet is being constantly replenished in order to ensure that the food is fresh and in the right temperature, therefore what you are describing is not the level of service we aim for. We will definitely take your feedback under consideration and we do hope to welcome you back soon in order to ensure a better experience. Many thanks!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ch2013", "reviewer_origin": ["Neuchatel, Switzerland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "157"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "96"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r542859799-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I've stayed here 3 times on business. ", "Each time I have taken breakfast early (served from 06:30 during weekdays). ", "Each time the English breakfast items are cold, at best tepid. ", "I can imagine the chef starts cooking everything around 05:00 to be ready for 06:30, then places the serving dishes under an infra red light arrangement to keep it warm. Trouble is, it doesn't work! ", "Nothing worse than a cold clammy sausage and cold baked beans. Only thing I ate at a decent temperature was a fried egg, coz the chef cooked it while I waited!", "Come on Novotel, find a better solution!"]}
