{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r540877487", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Just amazing moment...", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "14 November 2017", "answer_text": ["Wow. Thank you for such an amazing review! It is always our most treasured reward to make our guests happy and we are glad to hear that you enjoyed the dining experience with us. All the B\u014cKAN family is very proud to read your kind words. We hope to see you again very soon too!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "harleyandjoker", "reviewer_origin": ["La Crau, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r540877487-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We spent a dinner at Bokan. What a really good \u00ab\u00a0gastronomic\u00a0\u00bb moment! ", "Despite the view which is amazing and so romantic, the decoration so confortable (wood, carpet, leather, slow lights....) and nice. Our culinary tasting was a very perfect moment. We choose \u00ab\u00a0\u00e0 la carte\u00a0\u00bb dishes. Mozzarella and avocado very nice and tasty fish, scallops were so good and perfectly cooked. And even though the Paris Brest : waouuhh! ", "Thanks for this nice experience. I would not avoid to come back during my next trip in London for sure! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r537563457", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing Food & Service", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "1 November 2017", "answer_text": ["Your praises and comments on our friendliness are surely one of the best compliments you could ever make to us! Our brunch is one of our priorities and we're thrilled to hear your loved it! Hope to see you soon!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lucyjupp", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r537563457-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I booked this for my mothers birthday and opted for the bottomless brunch at the weekend. I could not fault the cocktails, food and definitely not the flowing prosecco. Great atmosphere and stunning views. Staff are very friendly and always on hand to help!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r537615994", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great location, average food", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "1 November 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for sharing your impressions. Each day, the entire team strives to deliver a unique and memorable experience for each guest. We would like to apologise for the inconvenience with the elevators. We will definitely take your feedback under consideration and share it with our Team. We do hope to welcome you back soon!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "103StuartM", "reviewer_origin": ["Vale do Garrao, Portugal"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "87"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r537615994-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Bokan", "Situated approximately a 5 minute walk from Canary Wharf tube station, Bokan sits atop the Novotel London Canary Wharf.", "Bokan is spread over three floors (37th, 38th and 39th). The 37th is the formal restaurant, the 38th is the bar (serving bar food) and the 39th is a secondary bar area with an outdoor deck (see photos).", "The lighting throughout Bokan is very low, which on the whole works well but definitely makes reading the menu difficult! ", "We decided to eat in the bar area on 38 and then have a drink in the bar on 39. The service on the 38th floor was fine but not great, the service on the 39th floor was much better. The bar menu is somewhat limited with approximately 5 or 6 'main' options. I ordered the burger, which was good and which came with some fries.", "It's the location of Bokan that really makes this place. The views across Canary Wharf and back towards the O2 are great.", "The only real negative was that on the evening that I was there, 2 out of the 4 elevators weren't working, which caused a bit of a queue when I was trying to leave.", "Overall, not the best place to eat in Canary Wharf but it probably has some of the best views."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r538765198", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Friday evening dinner ", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "6 November 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Alison,", "Well your review is fabulous! Thank you so much for your kind words! Great to hear you liked our new place and our attentive team. Hope to see you soon!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "A4389GUalisonp", "reviewer_origin": ["Dollar, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r538765198-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Fabulous views from this restaurant on the 37th floor. The food was also 1st rate, although there is a cocktail bar above you it\u2019s still possible to have a conversation over dinner. Staff very attentive - maybe just a wee bit too much but better that than feeling adrift. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r538850044", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great views and food!", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "6 November 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Elena,", "We're thrilled to hear you enjoyed every aspect of what we offer here at B\u014cKAN!", "Thank you for your kind words - see you soon?", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Elena Y", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r538850044-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice service too! Great cocktails. ", "Nice spot for a dinner and cocktails overall. If you ask for a table by the Window, they would most likely accommodate your request:) thanks Bokan! I would go back:)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r538156966", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Complete lack of service ", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "3 November 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear James,", "Thank you very much for sharing your impressions. Each day, the entire team strives to deliver a unique and memorable experience for each guest. What you are describing is not the level of service we aim for and we would like to apologise for your disappointed experience. Could you please send me an email at jeevan.thej@accor.com with your full name, date and time that you visited us, so we can investigate further? Many thanks!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JimJones92", "reviewer_origin": ["Belfast, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "47"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r538156966-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["While there is no doubt Bokan is a well thought out, impressive bar & restaurant, it seems the emphasis is on the initial wow factor and stops there. The service leaves a lot to be desired.", "We visited on a Friday afternoon, the venue was not overly busy, maybe around 30 customers. After taking a seat, we waited for someone to take our order and kept waiting. Eventually we gave up and attempted ordering at the bar, but we were completely ignored by the staff. After returning to the table we were finally able to place an order, 40 minutes after arriving.", "There seemed to be one bar man with responsibility for making drinks, meaning we waited a further 20 minutes on our drinks coming.", "We decided to order another round, and this time we're helped by a very friendly and helpful member of staff who was happy to answer our questions regarding the drinks list. The list looks great and you are really spoiled for choice.", "A separate member of staff then came back to us informing that two out of the three ingredients from our Negronis were not available.", "Bokan is not short of staff, with around 8 staff on the floor at the time of our visit. However they were not not overly interested in serving us with a couple leant over the bar on their phones for the duration of our visit.", "This bar has the potential to be one of the best in the area, with fantastic views over London. But it is hugely let down by lack of service."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r538842962", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing Views", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "6 November 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your comment. We're glad to hear you had a great time with us. When are you back, we're missing you already!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "GlobeTrotter280", "reviewer_origin": ["Majorca, Spain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "82"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r538842962-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great views & atmosphere ", "Price is \u00a3\u00a3\u00a3 = Views ", "Service is slow, but the bartender was nice & once they get to you finally, they\u2019re nice i guess.."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r539422009", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "super food and view", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "8 November 2017", "answer_text": ["The service is our priority and we want our guests to have a great and memorable experience with us. Therefore, we are terribly sorry it was not the case for you last Friday evening. Please know that we take your comments under serious consideration and we will address the team accordingly. Thank you for sharing your feedback and we are glad to hear that you enjoyed the food and the view! We are looking forward to welcome you again and ensure a better experience for you and your friends.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "TamworthSpidey", "reviewer_origin": ["Tamworth, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "53"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r539422009-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["As a party of four we ate here on Friday night (3rd Nov)", "We were shown to a corner table with great views of London and the O2 arena.", "Mix up with ordering our wine meant we waited longer than we should. Also our friends had a gift card for two free drinks which the staff could not fathom!!! and therefore only one free drink arrived.", "The lighting was low(probably for effect) which meant we had to use our phone torch to see the menu.", "However the food was superb, the rib-eye and mash was to die for.", "One criticism, I understand that a large percentage of staff in the service industry are from overseas but a grasp of the English language would be a help.", "My partner always worries if the staff do not understand gluten free and it did take a while to communicate this, sorry but \"I am French \" is not the answer we were seeking.", "However she was guided through the menu (in a fashion) had a very nice meal. the gf bread rolls were delicious."]}
