{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r534775091", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Top view, great location! ", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "21 October 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Roli,", "We are over the moon to hear your amazing review! Thank you so much. We are glad that you enjoyed the view and the friendliness of our staff. Hope to see you again!!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Roli1212", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "53"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r534775091-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great place! The atmosphere can take you to the sky! The staff is very friendly, they can make you drunk easily.. The view is unforgettable! Great for drinks and food also! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r533784088", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "A Gem in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "17 October 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear David,", "Thank you for your kind words! We are thrilled you had a good time with us. We look forward to welcoming you back very soon.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "David B", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "156"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "74"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r533784088-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We arrived at 2pm for the 'Brunch' and was impressed not only with the food but also the service, the views and the chilled atmosphere. The bonus was the live Jazz band at 4pm. (which plays until 7pm) They do an offer for \u00a349.00 which includes as much Prosecco as you can drink from 2pm till 4pm. And to be fair, the waiters do not stop pouring it! Which is nice. They also serve water and ice at the table without charge. One of our group does not drink so she was given an option to choose a Mock-tail instead. Overall the food was tastey and very satisfying. There was my pet hate of the discretionary 12.5% service charge but we didn't mind paying it because the service was very good. Definitely a place I would highly recommend and a place I would look forward to returning to."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r536474333", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Top of the world", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "27 October 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear baobabjim,", "Thank you for the kind words! We are thrilled you had a good time with us. ", "The service is our priority and we want our Guests to have a great and memorable experience with us so feel free to email me at Jeevan.thej@accor.com and we'll continue the conversation.", "Looking forward to hear from you soon.", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "baobabjim", "reviewer_origin": ["Bedfordshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "117"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r536474333-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Astounding night views across the city and Thames, welcoming staff, loft-style decor. Good looking restaurant. Food is v.good value. Chef knows her stuff with excellent fusion of styles. On this occasion, starter was Scottish venison carpaccio - clever mixture of ingredients (like pomegranate and pear) truly heighten the flavours of the venison. My main was scallops and my friend had the lamb. Lamb looked and must have tasted great as the plate was clean! As with the starter, interesting mix of flavours to bring out the best in the scallops. Most notable was the black pudding accompaniment and purees. Excellent meal. ", "The one area they can improve is staff knowledge of the wine list. I asked if they had any SA wines and our waitress did not know and searched the menu for us. Small detail, but ability to romance the menu would have scored them Excellent."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r535447829", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Dinner ", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "23 October 2017", "answer_text": ["YAY, Big thank you for your awesome review and the perfect score! It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed your experience with us and that you are willing to share it with your friends and work colleagues. Come back soon!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "BG0608", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r535447829-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Waiting staff very friendly and helpful. Food excellent and good value, cost is in line with central London restaurants, but has the added value of great views across London.", "Have been for both lunch and dinner, can\u2019t fault either, will be going again and telling my friends and work colleagues "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r536920143", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Excellent food but not a clue what the waiter said", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "29 October 2017", "answer_text": ["The service is our priority and we want our Guests to have a great and memorable experience with us. Therefore we're terribly sorry that you experienced difficulties with your communication with the waiter. We will definitely address the issue and thank you for pointing this out to us. We hope to welcome you back soon and ensure that you have a great experience with us!", "Jeevan & The Bokan Family"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Docklander20", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "176"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "51"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r536920143-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This is my fourth visit here and the food keeps getting better and better. The menu has been shortened and offered exceptionally good food. There was a complimentary amuse bouche which was fantastic but had no idea what it was. We just could not understand the waiter and as each course arrived the waiter tried to explain what we were eating and we ended up having to resort to Google translate. This is becoming a bit of a London trait and such a shame for fantastic restaurants such as this."]}
