{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r526510845", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Nice venue but terrible service", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "22 September 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "We're terribly sorry to hear about your disappointing experience. We strive to make sure every Guest has a great time with us at B\u014cKAN. We do hope you will give us another chance in a near future to prove our worth."], "reviewer_pseudo": "fifimar", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "47"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r526510845-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Have been here twice just for coffee but the level of service has been appalling both times. First outing it took ages for someone to come to our table , though the place was quite. When the coffees came they were tepid at best. Next time I tried to order 2 coffees at the bar from one of waiters but he seemed to just look at me as if it was beyond him and pointed to his colleague saying he would make then and then just walked off without telling his colleague. Then I waited and waited and nothing so I gave up. That's a just a coffee God knows what happens when you have a meal there I hate to think..... "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r530719374", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food and great service ", "diner_date": " October 2017", "rating_date": "7 October 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Clarinda,", "You're a star! Thank you for this incredible review! It is always our most treasured reward to make our Guests happy. Thanks so much for giving a shout out to Guillaume - He is shining everyday a bit more !", "We hope to see you again very soon, I am sure Guillaume would love to thank you in person for your kind words... See you soon !"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Clarinda G", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "38"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r530719374-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to celebrate our anniversary and had been recommended Bokan by a few friends. And we were not disappointed!", "When we arrived we were taken to our table. While this was nice, we asked if we could switch to a table where both seats looked out at the view - the staff changed our table to suit our request with no hesitation. ", "Upon ordering our food, we asked if they could do a vegetarian tasting menu. Again, our waiter said \u201cof course\u201d and proceeded to explain exactly what each course would consist of, and how the could amend the fixed tasting menu to meet my needs.", "During the meal, we found all our servers attentive but not too in your face - the perfect level of service and we certainly didn\u2019t feel hurried or pressured in any way. We particularly liked how a few minutes was left between each course to let us digest before the next - this gave us time to chat and take in the atmosphere. The dishes themselves were spectacular - amazing flavours and well put together. We couldn\u2019t fault it. ", "We\u2019d also like to thank our main waiter Guilloume who was the perfect blend of informative, friendly and professional - he really helped to make it a special evening for us.", "We will 100% visit Bokan again, and recommend to friends! "]}
