{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r516817740", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Splendid views, food and service", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "23 August 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Harry", "Thank you so much for your amazing review, we are happy to hear that you have enjoyed the culinary delights and the service.", "Hope you to see you soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "HarryHotspur1959", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "158"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "60"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r516817740-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went there tonight for a business dinner. My colleague had the crab meat, which was amazingly presented. I had the crispy hen's egg, which didn't look quite as good, but was superb. We both had the halibut, which was excellent. The service was extremely attentive, polite and knowledgeable. The one thing that I really enjoyed was the combination with both dishes of the jus and the little blobs of various sauces around the plate. A beautiful combination of tastes.", "We were lucky in that there was a beautiful sunset this evening, so the view from the top of the building across to the Shard and the Eye was spectacular. My tip? Ask for a table next to the window, which can only enhance the impressive view."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r517759095", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Fantastic views, service needs improving ", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "26 August 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest", "Thank you for you valuable feedback, we are sorry about the shortfall on your recent visit. Hopefully we will exceed your expectations the next time you visit us."], "reviewer_pseudo": "if661", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "132"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r517759095-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The views are stunning and it had a nice chilled out atmosphere, with a pretty good mix of people. However the service was disappointing especially as service is added even when you get a drink from the bar. Mistakes were made and we simply ordered a bottle of wine, nothing complicated and the wine wasn't good. At a place like that even the cheaper wines should be decent."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r517760609", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Nice view - perfect sunset", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "26 August 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Carlos", "Thank you for choosing us as the Roof top destination. We are happy that you have enjoyed the drinks and food in our Skyline Bar BOKAN. Hope to have you back soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Carlos G", "reviewer_origin": ["Sao Paulo, SP"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r517760609-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Very Nice bar, with good drinks and food. As a guest of Novotel, was surprised with the fancy rooftop bar and it's perfect view of London's skyline. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r518129283", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Untruthful booking policy", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "27 August 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest", "Thank you for your valuable feedback, we are truly sorry for your disappointing experience with the change in booking policy and the mis-communication. We hope you will give us another chance to shine."], "reviewer_pseudo": "konstantinos447", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r518129283-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Yes the views are amazing, yes the cocktails are good but these mean nothing if the service does not live up to the expectations. Their booking policy for the terrace appears to be simply untruthful and misleading. It's understandable that during good weather it will be busy. What is unacceptable is when you ask them to book they say that the system is blocked. Even if you say that you will call later they say that you cannot book and that you will have to walk in early. You walk in early and surprise surprise, everything is already booked for the day! So basically they will not tell you that they are fully booked and you're lured in by the hope that there will be availability. This might seem like a small detail to some but the lack of decency and honesty are definitely things that will stop me from going to this place again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r518173110", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Average restaurant , nothing special except view ", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "27 August 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest", "Thank you so much for sharing your feedback, We are sorry that the food wasn't to your expectations. BOKAN bar has become a hot spot and due to this we highly recommend guests to reserve if a table preferred. I hope you will give us another try to experience BOKAN fully."], "reviewer_pseudo": "HarryEssex777", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r518173110-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Will I recommend this restaurant ,I don't think so.Food is ok, but portions are tiny ,and I mean it.", "Funny think is you have to book roof top bar as well if you want to use it after dinner....but booking have to be done in advance hahaha even waitress said that after diner, drink in bar is must. So Im a bit confused...."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r519407802", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Stunning view, average service...", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "30 August 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest ", "Thank you the review, I am pleased that you has a relaxing time. Apologies that the cocktails were not to your liking. I hope you will come soon to try the new list going live next month."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Miki-H01", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "74"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r519407802-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited the rooftop bar to \"escort\" the sun down behind the city of london...", "We only tried 3 cocktails to chill, walked in with no reservation.", "We were seated with a bit half hearted manner but the outstanding view balanced the experience.Cocktails were nicely garnished, but tasted avarage for \u00a313-\u00a315 each.", "I would strongly recommend to check out the view and the atmosphere of the 38th floor terrace, take your photos, sip your drink and relax.", "Miki"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r513865258", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good food, great service and amazing view!", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "16 August 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your amazing feedback! It was our great pleasure to welcome you. We're glad to hear that you had a great time with us and that you love the food! We do hope you'll visit us again soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Vanessa d", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r513865258-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The restaurant has a nice selection of food, about 6 choises for starters, and mains and an extensive winelist, but no need to consult the list as the sommelier will be at your service to provide you a matching wine with whathever it is your table has ordered. ", "I regularly visit the restaurant when I have friends visiting as the view over the city and the Thames is amazing, and the restaurant has a nice funky ambiance. Being greeted back after only visiting twice over the past 4 months shows the eye of detail of the waiters and they go out of their way to make you feel welcome. ", "Thank you Bokan for yet again an excellent experience and hope to see you soon!"]}
