{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r509743960", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Tasty ", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "7 August 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Davidh1977", "reviewer_origin": ["Northallerton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "398"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "169"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r509743960-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Grabbed a takeaway pizza as I passed.", "Not the cheapest takeaway but it was a a light and crispy base and flavoursome topping.", "An easy pleasant option"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r510833365", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Spectacular view with nice food ", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "10 August 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your review, we appreciate your feedback. We're thrilled to hear that you enjoyed the food, and the views! We also understood that they were a few lapses that we can easily correct to make your next visit perfect! We hope we will have you back very soon !"], "reviewer_pseudo": "hsiehhan2", "reviewer_origin": ["Singapore, Singapore"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "45"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r510833365-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We tried their \u00a360 testing menu. ", "The overall food quality was good. Out of the six courses meal, I love four out of the six dishes. Despite being rather new, you can feel the chef is trying very hard to demonstrate his creativity and the culinary technical skills.", "The services was also decent, and all of them were very helpful and friendly. The only complaint we had was that we were sitting around the corner, so sometimes the staff may not notice us when we needed some help. ", "The best of the restaurant is its unbeatable view overlooking canary wharf and the Shard. It's amazing to see the change in skyline from sunset to evening view. Even the view from restroom is amazing ! ", "All said, I think this restaurant got a lot of potential and will be happy to make my 2nd visit soon. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r509082622", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Lovely view ", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "5 August 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for sharing your feedback. We're so sorry to hear we did not fulfill all your expectations this time. ", "We apologise that you did not receive our usual level of service and I do hope that we get the chance to show this to you in the future !"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Marco B", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r509082622-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Beautifull view, one of my favourite place in east London for a drink with friends. Unfortunately once again lack of service. 23 minutes for a Cocktail, never seen smile any bartender in 3 hours. And why I should pay for the service charge if I collect by myself one bottle of prosecco from the bar shell. Please make sure that you apply the service charge when you offer a service and not impose ro your customers to pay for something not delivered. And probably your staff will be more pleasant with the guest to earn more tips. ", "I hope next my visit will be less disappointing. "]}
