{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r511130778", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "After work drinks. Great views limited wine and food selection", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "10 August 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "im666_1999", "reviewer_origin": ["United States"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "328"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "91"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r511130778-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for after work drinks. Huge outdoor space on the rooftop and lots of indoor space too. ", "Fantastic views of canary wharf , Greenwich and central london. ", "Lots of cocktails but limited wine and food menu ( at least where we were sitting outside). Options were olives some food on stock and chips. Also cheese at \u00a39 per person. They could offer additional snack options. ", "No beers on tap which was disappointing and wine list was really limited. ", "Service was fine. There were 2/3 waitresses who were extremely busy. Some orders took a while and final bill took 10-15 mins of Waiting to materialize. ", "Will visit again but hope that the food and wine / drat beer choices are improved. "]}
