{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r507694357", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nice view, nice ambiance", "diner_date": " August 2017", "rating_date": "1 August 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for sharing your feedback . We strive to be the very best and every single comment is very important to us .", "We are delighted to know that you enjoyed the food and the views here at Bokan .", "Hope to see you back soon !"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CarlV75", "reviewer_origin": ["Paris, France"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r507694357-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["the reastaurant by itself is beautiful, very modern and trendy !", "the food is amazing together with the cocktail !", "Need some improvements regarding the service, specially those who welcome the guest who just exit the elevator.", "Very nice bar and terrace, the view is spectacular !! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r505910328", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "You need lots of patience to get a drink", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "26 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for sharing your feedback. We're so sorry to hear we did not fulfill your expectations this time. ", "We apologise that you did not receive our usual level of service and I do hope that we get the chance to show this to you in the future. "], "reviewer_pseudo": "luxe_travelLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "44"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r505910328-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to the bar on the 38th floor to have drinks. Decor is great, and views obviously breathtaking. ", "However, the staff are in serious need of some training. The hostess seemed very stressed by having to deal with a few people arriving at the same time, and it showed in the service we received. Then it was 25 minutes from the time we ordered drinks for 6 people, until they finally arrived. The cocktails were ok, but nothing special - lots of ice in them! 2nd drink of a glass of Taittinger champagne was flat, so didn't finish it. All of that for prices which are astronomical. Would I go back? Maybe, but I'm not in a rush."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r504834233", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sunning view - Sunday Brunch", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "23 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much Thomas for such an amazing review! Charlotte and All the B\u014cKAN Family are very proud to read your kind words. We hope to see you again very soon too!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "thomasgF2673NN", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "75"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r504834233-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Sunning view at the top of the Novotel Canary Ward tower. Well furnish and designed dinning room. Nice and tasty plates. Definitely the place to go on Sunday brunch for any occasion. This place worth a detour.", "Charlotte our waitress has been very kind and professional."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r506052539", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Absolutely Perfect Evening", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "27 July 2017", "answer_text": ["You're a star! Thank you for this wonderful review! We are extremely proud to hear how much you had a good time with us.", "It's hard indeed to choose one dish among the variety, we hope that we will have the pleasure to see you soon so you can try more!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "smiles19602016", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r506052539-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The views from each floor looking down over the Thames up to Tower Bridge and far beyond are wonderful. The tables in the restaurant are positioned well so that every guest can appreciate the vista. ", "The waiting service was impeccable, polite and well informed on each dish and the wines offered. However the real reason you must go to this restaurant is the food! Each dish is beautifully presented and very well composed. The combination of flavours and colours make choosing a course very difficult, every guest thought they had chosen the perfect plate. Aurelia, Head Chef, watched service with an eagle eye and it was interesting to see her so visible in the kitchen with her team.", "All in all a perfect meal.", "I highly recommend this restaurant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r505011471", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Needs to loosen up", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "24 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for sharing your comments about your recent visit at BOKAN. We are terribly sorry to hear that your experience was not perfect. What you are describing does not reflect our standards and please be assured that we have addressed your comments. ", "We hope that we will have a chance to welcome you again at BOKAN and at the hotel in a near future."], "reviewer_pseudo": "woznloz", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r505011471-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We paid two visits to bokan on Saturday first around 7:30pm where we were directed to the bar on the top floor this was fine and the barman prepared two rounds of three drinks as my brother came to meet us before we headed out for a meal. The cocktails were good and the service was too however when we walked over to the roof terrace to take in the views where no one was sat because of the incremental weather it felt like the security had joined our party, on taking a picture on my phone of the skyline I turned and almost bumped into one of them who was so close behind me.", "We sat on a dry table to finish up our drinks whilst being stared at and by that time was ready to go.", "We went for our meal and returned around eleven.", "This time we were greated well and politely taken to a table on the lower level the guy was very nice and explained that if a booked table wasn't claimed in the next ten minutes we could have that as it had better views.", "We chose a cocktail each this time just the two of us and I went to the bar.", "The whole ambience of the place had changed staff felt very cold and unwelcoming and stressed. We had another round and headed up to see the now darkened skyline where we were actually followed up the stairs out onto the terrace. ", "To add to this upon looking at my receipts I have been overcharged on three of the four rounds and a service charge added even though I went to the bar for every drink.", "I am in no way a penny pincher but why have I been overcharged and what service am I paying for? ", "There didn't seem to be any chance of a waitered service in the bar.", "I stayed at the hotel and the room was excellent."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r506821248", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Good potential but need to work on service", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "29 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for sharing your feedback. We're so sorry to hear we did not fulfill your expectations this time. ", "We apologise that you did not receive our usual level of service and I do hope that we get the chance to show this to you in the future. "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Koalar06", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "112"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "33"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r506821248-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I booked a table for the 39th floor in a sunday evening. When we arrive to the 38th the hostess was not paying atention to the lifts and not even lift her head when we pass throught ( we thought that there was another one on the top floor) and the security stoped us asking if we need something, we mention the reservation and he pointed to the hostess. After confirming our reservation she took us to our table. The place have amazing views and the decor is fantastic. The cocktail menu is creative but maybe a bit to long. We ask for 2 cocktails that took around 20 minutes to arrive. for the second round we choose a glass of wine and a beer as we didn't wanted to wait such a long time but it took more than 30 minutes to arrive. Besides the wait for the drinks we ask for some food that never came, when we ask why the wait we've been told that nothing was ordered. The staff was friendly but unable to manage the floor. About the price, a bit expensive if we take in consideration the service."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r506803935", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Treat people with dignity and as paying customers! Not numbers! ", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "29 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for sharing your comments about your recent visit at BOKAN. We are terribly sorry to hear that your experience was not perfect. What you are describing does not reflect our standards and please be assured that we have addressed your comments. ", "We hope that we will have a chance to welcome you again at BOKAN and at the hotel in a near future."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Princygirl", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "209"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "81"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r506803935-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Recently I've discovered this place and decided to bring different friends to have drinks here and spend some time together over a nice prosecco glass!", "This place is split on 2 floors of which both have an internal part, with just the top floor having also a roof terrace. It's at the 48th floor. ", "The majority of the internal design is made of wood and pastel fabric, with big cushions, chairs, and a stunning view! Literally you can see all of London!! I have the feeling of being in a winter cottage in the Alps, but with the view of being in a modern side of New York! I absolutely love it. ", "The restrooms are also very nice and clean, and while washing your hands you still have the opportunity of looking outside and admire the view- yes from the restroom! A Big, enormous glass will give you this!", "The only downside that I've found every time I visited this place and spent money from the Bar, that I'm starting to be seriously annoyed by it - is that when you sit down even before you ask for drinks, they say \"you can be here just for 1 hour\" even when there is no message on the table saying \"reserved!\". ", "The best part is that after one hour NO one comes to tell you \"hey you need to move!\". Honestly they just need to try and tell me that - they would have no idea of how I would react. ", "I find pretty frustrating that in a rich and expensive place like this, they could have the authority to make me move because someone else needs to sit! If the manager reads this - I have enough money to stay there for hours and hours to drink and eat and I would like to be treated with the respect I deserve as a paying customer!! ", "I really like this place, but the service and attitude I've received every time I visited this place, is disappointing. Please improve. ", "Value on the view: 10/10", "Value of the service: not applicable", "General value: 7/10 "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r507130998", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Really friendly staff", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "30 July 2017", "answer_text": [" Thank you so much for your very nice review. We're so pleased to see how much you loved BOKAN... and the views!", "Hope to see you again very soon! "], "reviewer_pseudo": "a-girl-in-goal", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "40"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r507130998-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Breathtaking views, really friendly staff, excellent selection of locally brewed beers. Perfect for cocktail hour."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r507234778", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful place to stay for sure!", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "30 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for sharing your feedback. We're so sorry to hear we did not fulfill all your expectations this time. ", "We apologise that you did not receive our usual level of service and I do hope that we get the chance to show this to you in the future !"], "reviewer_pseudo": "PatriceB1031", "reviewer_origin": ["Ottawa, Canada"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r507234778-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Before booking my hotel for my trip, I took the time to read many many many reviews on hotels and especially this one. I have NO regret for booking this hotel. I would definitely stay there again and recommend it for sure. The only \"negative\" comment I had read about the hotel was the very slow service at the bar or the restaurant. OMG, beyond SLOW.......staff walked by me and totally ignored me and my friend. I even stood at the bar wanting a glass of wine, was standing right in front of the bartender who was YES I KNOW very busy, but he could have at least acknowledge my presence......It took for ever to get a glass of wine, and than had to ask for my check......Having said that the staff for the brunch if wonderful and if this obvious they are there to serve you and make sure your visit is as enjoyable as possible. Another comment, is that there doesn't seem to be enough tables on the 3 floors to accommodate the number of guests staying at the hotel. Also, there was NO information in the room for phone numbers such as room service, front desk, wakeup call, etc....and no visitor guide or magazine. I do have to say that these are minor issues and the hotel still deserves a 4.9 stars our of five........."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r507281117", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Views ", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "31 July 2017", "answer_text": ["John,thank you so much for your very nice review. We're so pleased to see how much you loved BOKAN... and the views! ", "Our friendly staff is always more than happy to accommodate any requests when possible ! ", "Hope to see you again very soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "B9160BAjohnp", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r507281117-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went to Bokan early Saturday evening for family birthday drink the views were stunning of docklands the staff were very friendly the only fault was they tried to put us on a table outside in the rain but did move us when we complained "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r502808260", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Amazing Views!", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "17 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Lauren, thank you so much for your very nice review. We're so pleased to see how much you loved BOKAN... and the views!", "Hope to see you again very soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "LaurenDobson90", "reviewer_origin": ["Bath, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r502808260-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Me and my partner recently visited the Bokan while staying at the Novotel (which it is attached to) and loved it! We went every evening for a drink (3 nights in a row) before going out for dinner and all I can say is that you never get bored of the amazing views! It can get busy (especially on a Friday evening) so I would ring ahead to book a table plus the drinks are a little pricey but that didn't put us off at all!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r501474245", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great view but be prepared to sweat during your meal", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "13 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Therese Jasmine,", "Thank you very much for your review - every feedback is a gem and we appreciate you took the time to share it. We are truly sorry to hear that your experience at BOKAN was disappointing. What you are describing is not our level of standards and we would like to express our sincerest apologies. ", "Please rest assured that the situation of the restaurant being too hot as been solved. ", "Therese Jasmine, we hope we will have the pleasure to welcome you again at BOKAN so we can show you the amazing service we can offer and that was just a one off."], "reviewer_pseudo": "tjlovetotravel", "reviewer_origin": ["Singapore, Singapore"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "74"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "113"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r501474245-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Had dinner twice at Bokan right up on the 38th floor with a excellent view but it was extremely hot as aircon is either switch off or very weak which was not pleasant if you are in business suit. Service was slow and not great. Waiter was not friendly. Receptionist on 37th floor was not helpful and unfriendly which is strange.. Breakfast was average but at least not as hot as compare to evening time."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r501559799", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Brunch at B\u00f6kan", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "13 July 2017", "answer_text": ["WOW, you made our day! Thank you very much for your beautiful comment. It was our great pleasure to have you and we hope to have the pleasure to welcome you again soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "735PLR", "reviewer_origin": ["Sitges, Spain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "374"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "144"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r501559799-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Very nice restaurant on 38th floor of the hotel. Wonderful views across London skyline.", "Took brunch menu at \u00a345 per person with unlimited prosecco during 2 hours.", "Food very nicely presented and full of flavour. Waiting staff all extremely plesant and attentive. Would be very happy to recommend it and would love to return if I was able to."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r500883517", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "It was ok, but not great", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "11 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review. We're so sorry to hear we did not fulfill your expectations. Every feedback is a gem and we would love to have more details about your experience so we can look into this further. I would appreciate if you could contact me by email justine.freytet@accor.com or telephone 020 3530 0550. ", "Looking forward to hearing from you soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "olucares", "reviewer_origin": ["Rochester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r500883517-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The views are good, but the food was just ok, not exceptional. I was there for a friend's birthday party."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r501255374", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nice food, good views, generally good.", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "12 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Many thanks for sharing your feedback. We're delighted to hear your recommendations about the steak and the lamb! Lamb is my favourite too! ", "We offer a 'Express lunch' menu offer. Please feel free to send me your contact details so I can send you additional information. My contact details are justine.freytet@accor.com , 0203 530 0515", "We're sorry to hear that you did not find the service enough attentive - Service is one of our priority and we want our Guests to have a great and memorable experience with us. We'd love to have you back to give us another chance to show you the amazing service we are capable of!", "I look forward to hearing from you"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sunny_2016", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "16"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r501255374-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I went here during a lunch time trip, the restaurant was generally quiet and offers good food. It's quite expensive for what it is. My general gripe was about having to order certain items separately. I think a set price lunch menu would work wonders for attracting more people from local businesses. ", "The food was good, I recommend the steak and the lamb cutlets. Despite it being quiet, we did have to flag the staff down a few times - you would have expected them to have seen us easily, but they sat us in the quiet end of the restaurant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r501676592", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "How one member of staff can ruin a night!!", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "13 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Dan,", "We are awfully sorry to hear that your experience which started so well ended up that bad! We'd like to understand better what happened - could you please contact me to continue the conversation? My contact details are justine.freytet@accor.com or 020 3530 0515.", "Many thanks! "], "reviewer_pseudo": "dan041187", "reviewer_origin": ["Ashford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r501676592-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for a friends birthday, and the surroundings, ambiance, and stunning views of London seemed like the ideal scene to have some drinks and celebrate. There were only 3 of us, and the staff seem friendly, the drinks kept coming, and we was having a great time. My friend accidentally knocked a drink over, and within 2 minutes the manager came over and said that security was watching us and to calm down. (Knocking the drink over may have been coincidence). We were having a great time before this and would have easily stayed in there until closing, and spent a lot more money, but this made us want to leave straight away. The gentlemen could have come over to make sure we was good if he had a concern, or seen if we needed anything, but it felt like because security said something to him, he came over as the man, and told us to calm down. It put us off and I don't think we will be going back. There are enough rooftop bars in London, which are cheaper as well, and you won't get accused of anything either. How one person can ruin a night!!!! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r501858482", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great view and great food", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "14 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much Charles for your awesome review! We're so pleased to hear that you had a great time with us - come back soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "56charlesd", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "91"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r501858482-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I attended a private event served with a delicious buffet at the bar. Canapes were varied and very tasty. The Sauvignon Blanc wine from South Africa (Te Awa Left Field) was excellent. I will definitely come back again with friends"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r502469761", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Views", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "16 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Dave,", "Thank you very much for your review, we're glad to hear that you loved the view! ", "We have a wide selection of crafted beer, lager, pilsner, IPA, served on 33cl bottles, from \u00a35 to \u00a37. ", "We're sorry that you would not be willing us to visit us for this reason - we would love to have you again."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Stepneydave", "reviewer_origin": ["London E1 ,UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r502469761-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This is the place to go for drinks if you want fabulous views over London.", "The outside area on the top floor is just wonderful on a hot summers day.", "The only down side is they have stopped selling draught beer, now it's only small bottles for more or less at the same price.", "I won't be going back because of this, but for a one off treat I would recommend you go and have a look."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r502162767", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "One has taste for fine dining", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "15 July 2017", "answer_text": ["You're a star Julie! Thank you for this incredible review! The Team will be jumping for joy to read your kind words. Hope to see you soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "julie b", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "165"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "55"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r502162767-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["39th Floor Good Lord!!!!!!!!", "It was beautiful, didn't feel like the 39th floor the left was soooo smooth, the cocktails girls were at it again fine dining. Magnificent views of the skyline across london. We had a two hour slot and cocktails were flowing. Waiting staff all extremely plesant and attentive. Defo coming back with hubby. A lovely meeting place with friends before dining."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r502204983", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful evening...", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "15 July 2017", "answer_text": ["A BIG THANK YOU Julia! We are over the moon to read your kind words. It was our great pleasure to make your celebration that enjoyable! We hope that we will have the pleasure to welcome you again soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "juliac680", "reviewer_origin": ["Isle of Skye, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r502204983-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["9 of us went for a celebratory evening. We started with drinks on the roof terrace, stunning views and attentive staff meant the evening started well. We all moved downstairs to our table. As there were so many of us, we sent our meal choices in advance. The waiter confirmed with us and noted who was having what. When the food came, everyone was served at the same time. The starters were magnificent, such intense and amazing flavours. When the main course came none of us were disappointed. The steak, fish and chicken dishes were cooked to perfection and accompanied with eye catching pur\u00e9es and foams that were packed with complimentary flavours. The wine was great, also full of flavour but not overbearing - just right! It seemed a shame to stop at the main course...the puddings and cheeses matched the quality and flavours we had already experienced and the sommelier picked us a wonderful wine to finish. Our waiter did a fantastic job and saw to all our every need. Thank you Bokan for making our celebration so enjoyable. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r500448641", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great food great view", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "10 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your review Karolina, we appreciate your feedback. We're thrilled to hear that you enjoyed the food, and the views! We also understood that they were a few lapses that we can easily correct to make your next visit perfect! We hope we will have you back very soon "], "reviewer_pseudo": "karolinag665", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "32"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r500448641-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We all enjoyed our food - the crab salad&scallops( slightly too sweet for my taste) for starters and then he boys had steaks (very good quality meat done to perfection), lamb & sea bass for the girls- all beautifully presented. A dessert - chocolate mousse was a bit of a let down, though. ", "Our waitress could be slightly more attentive. We were splitting the bill four ways, but I was paying for my boyfriend and myself, but she charged my card twice for a single person, instead adding up two numbers.. a bit weird. ", "Much as I enjoyed the restaurant, the bar lacked the ambience and comfortable chairs. Cocktails were not that great either even though they charge as much as the Beaumont in Mayfair. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r497431879", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Bokan - 38th Floor", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "30 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Oh, what a great review Amrita! We're absolutely thrilled to hear how much you had a great time with us. Luca is indeed a true asset and he will be over the moon to read your praises.", "Thanks for the comment about the olives, it's not nice indeed and we will make sure it is always the highest quality. ", "We think our restrooms are the best in London too ;-) ", "When are you back?"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Amrita D", "reviewer_origin": ["Glasgow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r497431879-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Went with a girlfriend for a \"couple of drinks\" to Bokan on the 38th Floor of Novotel Canary Wharf. The views from the Bar are really superb, having seen the views at 4.30pm, decided to stay all evening just to experience the night time views. We were certainly not disappointed, they are really really superb. As the bar has floor to ceiling windows, you get a spectacular view of central London. Luke who served us in the evening was also very nice and very friendly, he even made a bespoke cocktail for my friend. Jeevan who is the manager there came and checked on us often. To be fair we were there from 4.30pm - 1am, but even still it was very nice to be checked upon and so looked after by Jeevan. He also gave us a show around of the restaurant and the roof top bar. We will definitely return. The only small feedback would have is to change the olives in the bar, they really did not taste good, they were almost bitter. We had a great evening at Bokan and would definitely recommend to anyone to go there for a drink..friendly staff and amazing views guaranteed!! Just make sure you make a booking as it does get very busy!! Oh and before I forget, possibly the best bathrooms in London - even they have an amazing view!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r497998650", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Food with a View", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "2 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much Klaidas for your amazing review.", " ", "We are glad to read that you enjoyed your experience at BOKAN. Please be assured that I will share your beautiful review with All the team.", "When are you back??"], "reviewer_pseudo": "klaidask2017", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r497998650-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I was really excited about coming here particularly after all the hype, the restaurant and bar did not disappoint. The food was perfect and what you would expect from a restaurant like this. The menu is not incredibly long but it does have to offer a great number of dishes, I would recommend the squid as an appetiser and the lamb or to be on the safe side: go for the rib eye steak, you cannot go wrong with it. The interior is fantastic with its large windows that provide you with a great view of London from above. I will definitely be coming back, especially for the bar, which offers a huge range of interesting non-classical cocktails. A lot of the negative reviews of Bokan focused on the service, I honestly have no complaints about the service whatsoever, everyone seemed friendly, helpful and attentive to our needs."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r498035024", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing views in stylish atmosphere", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "2 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Such a great review! We are over the moon to see how much you had a good time with us, can't wait to welcome you for a lunch or a dinner!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "skyandsands", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "55"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r498035024-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What amazing view! 360 degrees over London, Thames, the docklands and the Isle of dogs. Incredible!! This place is very stylish and chique, so make sure you reserve a table, to make sure your trip is worth wile. Only went for drinks but they tasted delicious, staff was attentive, went during lunch it wasn't that busy. A must go!!! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r497597191", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Superb food, attentive service", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "1 July 2017", "answer_text": ["A massive thank you from the bottom of our hearts! The B\u014cKAN Team is concentrating their efforts towards a common goal, making every meal a unique and unforgettable experience. We're extremely happy to see you had a great time with us. The amuse-bouche is a Tomato emulsion, chick pea croquette and basil. We're sorry we've been clumsy - we will address it to make sure you have a perfect experience next time you visit us. We look forward to seeing you soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lauv", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "60"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "52"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r497597191-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Didn't quite know what to expect when I randomly chose this place for dinner. My first impression was bit reserved, as the restaurant felt really noisy. Is adjacent to the bar, which plays music loud. Menu however looked promising; short, simple but full of interesting combinations.", "Service was attentive from the beginning, but there was some clumsiness as well: waiter splashed good amount of wine on the table while pouring to my glass. First they served a beautiful amuse-bouche: some kind of tomato foam with a polenta (?) chip. My main course seared Sea Bass with green olive pur\u00e9e, artichokes, clams and olive oil was absolutely delicious, brilliant combination of flavours, I totally fell in love with the olive pur\u00e9e! For dessert I chose tropical meringue with coconut, mango sorbet and candied cashew: fresh, fruity and light in the mouth, mango gave lovely kick to the meringue and coconut. Jackpot! ", "Overall, this place is quite pricy and routines may not be polished yet, but the high quality of food, friendly attentive staff and brilliant flavour combinations would make me return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r498052864", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "A Humiliating Experience ", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "2 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Jamie,", "We have already been in contact in regards of this matter. We are sorry that your stay finished on a negative note and we truly hope we will see you again soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "JamieGla1732", "reviewer_origin": ["Perth, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "45"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "47"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r498052864-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Stayed at the Novotel with my family for three nights. Visited Bokan on the Friday night and it's clearly a popular venue for the beautiful people. However, on our last night I asked reception if it was ok to take my son up to the bar to see the London skyline, as it's spectacular. No problem he said.", "We went up to the 38th floor to be met by a young woman behind the desk who said if reception said it was fine to let a 12 year old in then it was fine. Juan behind the bar had other ideas. He said he weren't welcome and despite the place being empty, it was a condition of their licensing laws. First time I've been refused two glasses of Sprite in a hotel bar! ", "So, back down to the reception where the chap who said it was fine apologised profusely. Apparently if my son had been 13 rather than 12 it would have been fine. I lodged a complaint as I've never been humiliated like it by a hotel bar in my life. Another more sympathetic member staff agreed that it was outrageous. ", "On the Friday night I was in it there does seem to be a thread common in other reviews. Staff are unnecessarily rude and customers (including hotel guests,) are treated like we are lucky to be there. ", "Skyline is spectacular but if you want to be treated like a human being try AquaShard. ", "A horrible experience and one that really took the shine off a wonderful hotel. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r500119040", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Bookings required for drinks and dinner. Excellent service, fantastic tasting menu, and those views! ", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "10 July 2017", "answer_text": ["YAY, Big thank you for your awesome review! It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed your experience with us. Come back soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "PennyPurples", "reviewer_origin": ["Orpington, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "619"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "345"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r500119040-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited on a Friday night with two girlfriends. Arriving early for dinner, I just assumed I'd be able to go to the bar first. On arrival it was clear that the bar equally has to be booked but fortunately they could accommodate me. ", "Tip: Ensure you book at the bar as well as the restaurant if you want drinks before dinner.", "Service during drinks was really lovely: Attentive, friendly, and prompt. Cocktails are around \u00a313, well explained on the drinks menu, delicious and very pretty. ", "Dinner for us was a 6 course tasting menu (\u00a360) with bubbles and wine on top. See photos for the excellent food. Pretty, delicious, perfect sized portions so we went away full but not over stuffed. ", "Watching the city go from light to dark is stunning, as you'd expect, and the bathroom with a view is a fun touch. ", "Will definitely go back before the summer is over to experience all over again. At 10 mins walk from Canary Wharf station, the location is convenient too, and easy for taxis to find and pick up due to hotel (Novotel) entrance. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r499913787", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Brunch", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "9 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Awhh, your review is heart-warming! It is always our great pleasure to have you at BOKAN Alice and we're thrilled to see how much you loved the brunch.", "When are you back? We're missing you already!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "alicea559", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r499913787-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Amazing brunch with view/ food amazing/ bottomless bubbles/ live jazz on the terrasse from 4pm", "I had the melon soup with goat cheese gyoza and the beef. Just incredible. Getting even better everytime I come"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r500170401", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delicious brunch, amazing setting", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "10 July 2017", "answer_text": ["We love your review Gabrielle! We're over the moon to read you compliments, thank you!", "We hope we will have the pleasure to welcome you again very soon"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Gabrielle F", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r500170401-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a superb experience here - incredible brunch. The food was mouthwatering and looked and tasted incredible, staff were also excellent. I had the tortellini, highly recommended. The dessert was a standout experience as well, wonderful chocolate tart (everything was great though). You won't be disappointed by the view!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r500164126", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great views, slow service", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "10 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your review Marcus. We're glad to read that you loved the view! Guest feedback is imperative to maintain the level of personal service that we strive for and we're sorry that your experience was not perfect due to the delay of the service. We hope you will give us another try soon?"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MarcusHurley", "reviewer_origin": ["Bristol, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1563"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "631"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r500164126-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["If you want some superb views of the city then this is the place to be! You can see Tower Bridge, the Eye, Shard etc and have a panoramic view of the centre of London. ", "If you are in a rush then this isn't the place to be. We waited 20 minutes for 2 coffees on a quiet Sunday night."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r496525186", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Quality food, Great View", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "27 June 2017", "answer_text": ["YAY, Big thank you for your awesome review! It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed every single aspect of what we offer at BOKAN (even the wahrooms!). Come back soon!", "PS: please note that BOKAN Bars is accessible to +18 but people below 21 may be asked to show a proof of age. "], "reviewer_pseudo": "TRavelBug232323", "reviewer_origin": ["Los Angeles, California"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "291"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "243"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r496525186-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Wonderful view from the 37th, 38th and 39th floors of the Novotel Hotel at Canary Wharf . There is a street level entrance which gives access to an exclusive elevator that goes direct to the 37th floor . Fantastic 360 degree views of the city . Even the washrooms have views as you wash your hands . Great chef prepared meals from starters to desserts . Now this place serves quality over quantity food. On the pricey side but food definitely will excite your palette . The 37th floor is the restaurant , 38th floor are for cocktails which does not permit people below 21 yrs of age . The 39th is the rooftop bar . There are telescopes positioned around the place for free viewing of the sorroundings . Posting pictures of platings. Wonderful place , especially for special occasions. Service was good. Make reservations ahead."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r495539326", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "You have no right to be this rude to paying customers!", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "24 June 2017", "answer_text": ["We are very disappointed to hear that you did not have a good time with us. We are very surprised to read the poor customer service you are describing here. Service is our priority and we All strive for our Guests to have a great and memorable experience with us. We are very concerned by guests' feedback and I would be more than happy to discuss directly with you about this experience. ", "Please email me at jeevan.thej@accor.com or by phone at 07 767 846355 and we'll continue the conversation. Many thanks."], "reviewer_pseudo": "WaltonWanderLust", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r495539326-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The staff are incredibly rude and make the prices up as they go along. Avoid, it's not as good as the staff think they they are.....We were there last night and the entire staff force were some of the rudest people we have ever had the misfortune to be \"served\" by. At the door the front of house had the snottiness attitude and was not the least bit welcoming. The bar staff had unwarranted attitude and were argumentative at every opportunity irrespective of the amount of money we were spending. They had the utter nerve to keep changing the prices of our drinks because the menus were in the \"process of being updated\"! Here's a tip, update the menus and THEN put them on the tables! Don't tell your staff to come up with rough numbers and then get aggressive when we state our basic consumer rights.... Unfortunately we have to return here in a few weeks for a corporate event. We'll be passing this review to our events team Monday in case there's the possibility of moving to another venue."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r495544943", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Terrible staff", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "24 June 2017", "answer_text": ["We're terribly sorry to hear about your disappointing experience. ", "We can assure you that this is not a true reflection of the service we want to offer here at Bokan. I would like to have more details about your experience with us. Please contact me directly either by email at Jeevan.thej@accor.com or by phone at 07 767 846355."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Lise D", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r495544943-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This place is beautiful but it's a total rip off. Firstly the lady on the door didn't want us in the bar. We turned up early as booking an area for 2 hours was \u00a3600! She said if we could find a table then we could sit at it but she didn't like the idea of 20 people and not sure why as we all have jobs and money! It took a man in our party to get a table for us and then she gave me dirty looks all night. The last straw was the prices advertised on the menu were not what we were charged. The prosecco was \u00a310 more! Also they add 20% to your bill when you buy from the bar! Surely this is not legal! We have a company party there in 2 weeks time, I will be very rude when I go back because the staff are up themselves big time!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r495640082", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "A venue with great views and appalling service", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "24 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for sharing your feedback about your recent experience at BOKAN.", "We are truly disappointed to hear that you did not have a good time with us. Service is our priority and we All strive for our Guests to have a great and memorable experience with us. I would like to have more details about your experience with us. Please contact me directly either by email at Jeevan.thej@accor.com or by phone at 07 767 846355."], "reviewer_pseudo": "aj1487", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r495640082-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The bar lounge on level 39 has really lovely panoramic views. Unfortunetly, the service is dreadful. I have never come across such rude staff anywhere in London. My colleague's birthday drinks were totally ruined. The hostess on level 38 was abrupt with no customer skills. I was made feel unwelcome. Bar staff on level 39 were even worse. On several occasions when trying to buy a drink I was totally ignored. After waiting for some time I was told I had to queue somewhere else. No further details were given or explained to me. Buying a drink each time was such a challenge. Settling payments was another issue - each time different prices were applied for the same drink. A tall waiter kept coming to our area throughout the night reminding us how we should have booked a table, despite half of the reserved ones being empty. I don't understand why would you want to turn spending clients away when the place is half empty. The overall experience was very disappointing. As an employee based in Canary Wharf, I was very excited about the opening of this venue. I thought it would be great for team outings, Friday drinks, leaving parties, etc. There is no way I'm coming backing to Bokan and will not recommend to it to anyone in Canary Wharf. When you charge premium prices for food, drinks and service, you just have to do better than my last night's experience."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r495986231", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "lovely rootop resto", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "25 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your comment. We're glad to hear you had a great time with us. Hope to see you again!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "R H", "reviewer_origin": ["Brussels, Belgium"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "129"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "194"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r495986231-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["on top floors of Novotel hotel in Canary Wharf, great views of city, food excellent, prices pretty reasonable"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r496083983", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Great view- TERRIBLE SERVICE", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "26 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for taking the time to provide us with your experience. Guest feedback is imperative to maintain the level of personal service that we strive for and we appreciate your comment. ", "We're terribly sorry about this terrible experience and surprised to read your comments about our service. We would need to have more details about your experience so we can understand what happened and address accordingly this matter. I would appreciate if you could contact me to discuss further, either by email at justine.freytet@accor.com or by phone on 020 3530 0515."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Baron_de_Henley", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r496083983-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Such a shame that what could be a great venue is totally ruined by the attitude of the staff- This included adding unjustified charges and being offensively rude. One to avoid"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r495173182", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Rooftop bar with excellent views and great service", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "22 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your comment! It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed your experience with us. We look forward to welcoming you back very soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Thecrimsonidol", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r495173182-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Drinks in the roof top bar. Offered amazing views of the city in all directions. Food and drinks were great and the service was exceptional (they even put up with our questions about what was contained in the food. At one point the chef came to talk to us)"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r496101975", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "New Restaurant with Amazing London Skyline View", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "26 June 2017", "answer_text": ["WOW, Lisa, we love your review! Thank you for your praises on the food, the service, the view and the vibe! We hope we will have the pleasure to welcome you again and again and again"], "reviewer_pseudo": "lisabN5756FD", "reviewer_origin": ["Florence, Italy"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "92"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "60"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r496101975-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The Vibes:", " ", " ", " ", "It is undeniable that the core reason for visiting Bokan is the sensational view. However, the trip to the dockyard location is entirely worth while as the thoughtfully rustic decoration and slick service make for a stylish dining experience.", " ", " ", " ", " ", "What we Ate: ", " ", " ", " ", "The food menu has been created by Aurelie Altemaire, the former Head Chef at L\u2019Atelier de Jo\u00ebl Robuchon and the cocktails have been created by Danilo Tersigni, former GM at Mr Fogg\u2019s.", " ", " ", " ", "The seared scallops with a citrus tang served on a bed of organic pearl barley warm salad, limoncello and wakame.", " ", " ", " ", " ", " ", " ", "Premium Aberdeen Angus beef tartar served with crunchy sesame crisp and wasabi mayo for that extra kick.", " ", " ", " ", "The beautifully presented Whole lobster is served with green mango salad, orange & jasmine sauce.", " ", " ", " ", "Thoughts:", " ", " ", " ", "Along with the excellent views, the food in Bokan lives up to the setting. This is the perfect unique surrounding for celebrations and gathering. You can book this wonderful space for private hire to seriously impress for your summer party in Canary Wharf."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r496167242", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing value for the quality!!", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "26 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Wow, it seems you've been BOKAN-ized! Thank you so much for your praise. The Team will be extremely happy to read your review. Come back soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Breezers2014", "reviewer_origin": ["Barbados"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "120"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r496167242-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Fabulous 360' view of London from 37 - 39th floors. Fantastic table by the window, a lazy Sunday set menu lunch with bottomless bubbly, enjoyed by all of us!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r496387708", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Dining with a view", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "27 June 2017", "answer_text": ["We are over the moon to read your review, thank you so much! We love to see that you loved it and that you were full and sated! Come back soon! "], "reviewer_pseudo": "PipsyH", "reviewer_origin": ["Berkshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "26"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r496387708-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a great evening! We booked a table for pre dinner cocktails followed by a table for dinner. Both tables had an excellent view each from different sides of the building which was great.The cocktails were imaginative as was the food. We had the tasting menu so we could sample a number of things. We were both very full and sated at the end!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r494675032", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Awful - no customer service standards and ruined my birthday totally.", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "20 June 2017", "answer_text": ["The service is our priority and we want our Guests to have a great and memorable experience with us, we're terribly sorry it was not the case on this special occasion. What you are describing is not the level of service we aim for and we would like to apologise for your disappointed experience. ", "Please email me at jeevan.thej@accor.com and we'll continue the conversation. Thank you once again and we hope to hear from you soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ran89", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r494675032-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["What an awful place. The staff were hopeless, took forever to take our order and serve us. To top it off, they actually ruined my birthday surprise that was arranged for me by my friend. They did this twice by asking him if I wanted dessert or should they bring the cake out!!! Talk about incompetence. Yet they wanted a form filling in prior to attending which was done in great detail. Clearly they don't communicate with each other. Now they are ignoring our email complaint which has been outstanding for 2 weeks. Avoid it and go elsewhere."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r491986612", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Amazing night time views ", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "10 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your feedback! We're extremely happy to read how much you had a great time with us at B\u014cKAN! The views are pretty amazing indeed.", "We have updated our menus online - sorry for the inconvenience. ", "Hope to see you soon on a warmer and less windy day! "], "reviewer_pseudo": "sccs4", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "114"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r491986612-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The view here really is beautiful - especially at night. It was still sunny when we went for dinner in the evening (beware - it gets bright!) so I would probably recommend coming here when the sun has set. ", "Our waitress was super friendly. We also made a reservation for the terrace lounge after our dinner. ", "Food was pretty good. Not cheap, but for what you get and for the view, I think the pricing is reasonable. Although the menu online has the wrong pricing! A lot of the dishes went up by a few \u00a3s - would've expected prices to be accurate online!", "We ordered the scallops for starters, lamb and sea bass for mains with veg and chips for sides, and cheesecake for dessert. Starter was small, but delicious and both mains tasted good and were also pretty filling. Cheesecake was a bit different from your normal cheesecake - it was ok, but I wasn't a huge fan.", "We went up for late night drinks in the terrace lounge and the cocktails were reasonably priced. Shame it was quite windy and cold, as the views from up there are stunning."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r492474414", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Expensive but fun, amazing views", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "12 June 2017", "answer_text": ["We are over the moon to hear your amazing review! Thank you so much. Hope to see you again"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Scottishcari", "reviewer_origin": ["Orkney"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "207"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "71"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r492474414-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Worth coming here for the views. Needless to say the cocktails are great and the food was excellent. I dont normally go for burgers, but I had the burger here and really enjoyed it. It is expensive but what you really come for are the views. 38 storeys up with a great view of the London skyline - by day or night. We saw Tower bridge opening in the distance! There is loud music and lots of banker types, but we got a table both times we visited the bar (we only ate bar food here) and had a lovely evening. Definitely worth a visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r492672859", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Impressive service on a rooftop restaurant ", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "13 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Wow, we're blushing - thank you for your awesome review! We will pass on your praises to Guillaume and the Team - they will be jumping for joy to read your kind words. ", "It was our great pleasure to have you - hope to see you soon "], "reviewer_pseudo": "DavidM13666", "reviewer_origin": ["Birmingham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r492672859-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Our waiter Giullame made our special night even more special. His service was amazing.", "Compliments to the chef as our chicken with foie was excellent and the steak was cooked to perfection. ", "The views from the restaurant are impressive and the industrial decor amazed me. ", "Definitely one of the top restaurants in the city. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r494036427", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Bokan Bar - Best bar in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "18 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Wow. Thank you for such an amazing review! It is always our most treasured reward to make our Guests happy. We hope to see you again very soon too!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "YoyoT13", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r494036427-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We have visited the bar on the 38th and 39th floor of the new Novotel hotel. This place has a really relaxed chilled atmosphere during the day and lively in the evening. Well designed except maybe the chairs which lack of comfort, absolutely stunning views of central London and East London. More importantly the cocktail menu is original and if you don't fancy any of it, the experienced bartenders can be creative around your taste buds. The oudoor space is fantastic spot, although you can imagine in high demand. So book a table in advance. Has become our regular since it's opening. Quite surprising to find such venue in a Novotel. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r493782764", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Terrible rude service avoid", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "17 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Roy,", "We are terribly sorry to hear about your disappointing experience and we would like to express our sincerest apologies.", "As one of our regular guests, I am sure you would agree that this is not the usual level of service we provide \u2013 please rest assured that it was not Julia\u2019s attention to come across in a rude manner. ", "Please feel free to contact me directly at capucine.viguier@accor.com and I will personally organise your next visit.", "I hope you will give us another chance to show you the true hospitality and service that we are able to deliver."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Roy J", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r493782764-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Myself and my girlfriend have eaten at the restaurant a few times and also regular users of the bar and we have even booked New Year's Eve there. We decided to take two friends of ours for a drink for the first and although we didn't make a reservation we went upon arriving we was told all the tables are full which we accepted and went to have a drink at the bar whilst waiting for our drinks someone left and a table become available which we sat down to enjoy the bottle of wine and also cocktails we ordered. We was then approached by Julia who should not be working front of house and rudely said you cannot sit there even though there was no one else to take the table at the time truly disgusted with her attitude and really had put he of going to what is in theory my local bar I suggest Mondrian at London Bridge there rumpus room bar is a lot more better run with friendly staff."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r492992240", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delightful Evening", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "14 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for such an amazing review! We're thrilled to hear you enjoyed every aspect of what we offer here at B\u014cKAN. Thank you for your kind words - see you soon?"], "reviewer_pseudo": "smiles19602016", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r492992240-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["A last minute decision to have a meal with my daughter. The views and position of tables in the restaurant means that everyone can see the dramatic skyline towards the Shard. The waiting staff were kind, considerate, efficient, and very professional. The food was perfect, a great menu with a good selection for any palate, beautifully presented, and delicious to eat. The Chef came out to say hello and we heard her story of coming to work at B\u014dkan. All very interesting and made us feel very welcome. I would highly recommend this restaurant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r494167992", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Absolutely Appalling!", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "19 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for taking the time to share your opinion on TripAdvisor about your recent experience at BOKAN.", "We are very disappointed to hear that you did not have a good time with us. Service is our priority and we All strive for our Guests to have a great and memorable experience with us. We are very concerned by guests' feedback and we would be more than happy to discuss directly with you about this experience. Please, do not hesitate to contact our Bar Manager directly either by email at Jeevan.thej@accor.com or by phone at 07 767 846355 should you like to share more details.", "I hope you will give us another chance to show you the true hospitality and service that we are able to deliver."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Greg E", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r494167992-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited Bokan on Friday night for a few drinks in your rooftop bar (39) with a few friends for one of their Birthdays. We were always going out after but really wanted to visit this place as it has of course recently opened and looked amazing. ", "When we arrived we were a little early so fully understandable that the table wasn\u2019t ready but saying that, I called a good 30 mins before we was going to arrive and whoever answered the phone said the table was already ready. We stood there awkwardly in everyone\u2019s way by the entrance for a good 10 minutes waiting for someone to simply wipe down the table and clear the glasses so we could take a seat. As we finally got taken over to the table 3 of the 5 of us take a seat and 2 of us left standing as there was only 3 chairs when the booking was for 5! ", "As your waiter frantically panicked looking for 2 chairs, lucky another table offered us their 2 stools as your waiter came back saying he couldn\u2019t find any. By now you can imagine I wanted to just get up and leave due to the shambles going on around me. Couldn\u2019t get a table with enough chairs, could just about get my table and everyone seemed a little too busy to listen to what I was saying or to help. Seemed a little under staffed to me.", "Finally we are at the table and 15 minutes later we get given the menu so we can order a drink. After waiting another 20 mins for her to come back and take our order, we sat there patiently and waited for our drinks. By now I wondered if they were ever going to turn up but eventually they did. I didn\u2019t think it took that long to make a drink, we didn\u2019t even order food! Again, must have been understaffed as it wasn\u2019t particularly busy but all we have done so far is wait. Extremely inattentive.", "The drinks finally arrive! I have ordered my favourite cocktail (that isn\u2019t even on the menu) a Pornstar Martini. At first glance is looked amazing and by now I was so thirsty I was ready to drink it in 1! I sat there and thought, this is going to be so good and make up for the experience we have had so far, but\u2026. It was rancid. I don\u2019t know if your bar staff have ever had a pornstar martini anywhere else but I have never had such a sour tasting, dry, small pornstar martini in my life. Even the prosecco on the side was again, extremely dry and sour to the taste. I would never order a Pornstar Martini from here ever again, even worse that one I have had from the likes of Be At One or All Bar One and this is supposed to be an amazing rooftop bar competing with the likes of Radio Rooftop and Rumpus Rooms and it was just not even comparable. Id compare it from my experience so far to my local Weather Spoons.", "Right, ive had enough, we are leaving, attic bar is around the corner and ive been there before and know it is a safe bet. This is me trying to salvage what dignity I have left as I have recommended this to everyone and booked it for a friends Birthday and it was just a shambles. Trying my best to keep spirits high as everyone looks like they have just had enough and want to go home.", "I manage to finally get hold of someone to get my bill as no one is giving eye contact so unless you chase after them, you are out of luck. I hand over this little business card that you get free at the front with a little number on it to get my card back (cant even supply the plastic tabs) and 10 minutes later get my card, and guess what? The completely wrong receipt.", "You literally managed to give me my card back with someone\u2019s else\u2019s receipt order. You can imagine how this looks, you could have given my card to the right person or if I hadn\u2019t have checked it, I would have paid nearly a \u00a3300 bill for my 5 drink order.", "I flag this up immediately to get my correct receipt. With this one I ask politely to take the service charge off my receipt as I refuse to pay 12.5% for what was terrible service. Your waiter comes back with yet another receipt. This time it is our order but there appears to be an extra bottle of Rose wine on there! Again not what I ordered. Like how bloody hard isit to print a receipt out of what we ordered on our tab with our table number? Obviously very difficult.", "This isn\u2019t the end though, here comes the embarrassing bit your end. When she (the original guy was obviously too embarrassed to come over) comes over to take the payment she asks \u2018Why do you not want to pay the service\u2019, I hate to say it as I am not a rude person, but I laughed in her face, I said you cant prepare a table with 5 chairs, cant put correct orders onto a receipt and im surprised I even got my bank card back. And you want me to pay you for this? She stood there stunned and said \u2018the company make us ask\u2019. ", "If this is true then you should be ashamed of yourselves. You charge good money for drinks alone but then expecting me to pay the extra 12.5% for the worst service I have ever received. I have received better service ordering a Bic Mac at 4am. It is up to the people paying if they want to pay service charge, hence why it is optional. To make your staff ask as to why is horrendous, everyone was looking at them and to think that is going to put me on the spot like it would most people, you are very wrong. I raised my voice and explained exactly why as your other customers listened in, in shock.", "I don\u2019t know if this was just a bad experience I had or if this is just what to expect from this place. Big name, great advertising, well set up with amazing views and good money spent on the interior! But as to the service, staff and drinks, unless I see a lot of good reviews go in soon, I don\u2019t think I will be going back or recommending this to any one I know. This just really lowered the mood and pretty much ruined our night when it was supposed to be the highlight!", "I hope your service will improve so no one else experiences what I did on Friday night."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r494472034", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sublime Panoramic Views + Good Food = Perfect London Evening", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "20 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your amazing feedback! It was our great pleasure to welcome you. We're glad to hear that you had a great time with us and that you love the food! We do hope you'll visit us again soon. "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Tripserto", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r494472034-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The restaurant Bokan 37 is a must try in London. ", "Located in the Novotel Canary Wharf, this place will not disappoint you.", "The adornment is unique in its own style. ", "Being the tallest hotel in the area pays off: the restaurant offers sublime panoramic views of London\u2019s skyline.", "The cuisine is remarkable; a mix of British and French, the two cultures of time altogether at one place. The food is so tasty that it can\u2019t be expound in words. The Bokan 37 is bringing the best of the culinary industry; the Head chef is famous Aurelie Altemaire, formerly working at L'Atelier De Jo\u00ebl Robuchon therefore you can only expect food that lives up to a high standard. ", "I am definitely coming back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r494630826", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Should be great, but", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "20 June 2017", "answer_text": ["We would like to thank you for sharing your feedback. We're terribly sorry about your disappointing experience. We can assure you that this is not a true reflection of the service we want to offer here at B\u014cKAN.", "We'd like to have more details about your experience with us. Could you please send me an email at jeevan.thej@accor.com so that we can investigate further ?", "Thank you once again and we hope to hear from you soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Lee G", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "126"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "90"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r494630826-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great venue. Brilliant view and really well designed menu....", "Then the service comes in to play. ", "The waitress didn't understand English. The food took ages. The bottled beers were warmish and the overal experience despite the positives above were marred by the simple fact that the service was third rate.", "Please tell me why restaurants don't train their staff properly? Or perhaps they are trying to do it on the cheap but with main courses nudging 30 pounds and plenty of pass through clientele they done really need to care I suppose. I can't recommend this place"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r490945273", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice views and good design", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "6 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Many thanks for sharing your feedback. We're delighted to hear that you loved our view! We have indeed a minimum spend for parties of more than 6 people. Hope to see you soon?"], "reviewer_pseudo": "antreasole", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r490945273-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["It has a nice design and views. You can see the 360 views across the London skyline unlike the Shard where you only see one angle.", "The only thing is that there is a minimum spend (\u00a330 p/p for the bar and \u00a350 p/p for the restaurant) for booking a table for more than 6 people."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r488631086", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "A surprisingly long lunch", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "29 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your feedback. We're terribly sorry about your disappointing experience. We can assure you that this is not a true reflection of the service we want to offer here at Bokan. I would love to hear more detail from you about your lunch so we can better address these issues. I would appreciate if you could contact me at justine.freytet@accor.com or at 020 3530 0515 and we'll continue the conversation.", "Many thanks"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mrdavidnorton", "reviewer_origin": ["Hertfordshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r488631086-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Visiting for the first time we entered from the main road to find a warm welcome but a slow lift.", "As expected there is a great view but with various levels for eating and drinking it becomes slightly disjointed as restrooms are only on one level although very clean and uncluttered.", "Lots of staff but seemed lacking in organisation and service was slow.", "Food was acceptable but average and seemed obvious you were paying more for the view.", "Live music in the outside bar and nice place to have drinks.", "Lunch for five was around \u00a3250 including drinks and service ", "Would not rush back."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r488874141", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best Canary Wharf restaurant ", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "29 May 2017", "answer_text": ["WOW, you made our day! Thank you very much for your beautiful comment. It was our great pleasure to have you. Looking forward to seeing you soon to try more dishes!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "ShiniMari", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "52"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r488874141-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This restaurant is amazing: great view from 37th floor, good service, nice atmosphere, and fab food!", "I had: ", "- White Asparagus salad, blood orange, mixed nuts, fresh herbs", "- Seared Sea Bass, green olive puree, artichokes, clams & olive oil", "- Vanilla and lemon cheesecake, gariguette, strawberry and basil sorbet", "Amazing bred also. ", "I'll go again for sure! Amazing chefs, great team!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r488773518", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Extremely disappointing. Dreadful service.", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "29 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for sharing your impressions. We are terribly sorry you could not experience Bokan for your boyfriend's birthday. We have indeed a holding table policy and the available tables you have seen were surely booked for later reservations. ", "Our Team is multicultural with over 25 different nationalities & origins and making All our Guests Feel Welcome is in our DNA.", "We would love to have you back so we get the chance to offer you an amazing Bokan experience. Please feel free to contact me directly at justine.freytet@accor.com and I will personally organise your next visit."], "reviewer_pseudo": "suziewoozie2017", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r488773518-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Extremely disappointing. Will not be returning or recommending to others.", "We booked this restaurant for a special occasion, a birthday meal for my boyfriend. Initially the doorman to the hotel at the entrance tried to turn my boyfriend away despite the fact he was wearing a shirt and trousers, he was also wearing white converse and therefore 'trainers'. As we were not informed there was a dress code upon booking a table, I have suspicions this could have been because another reason such as his race and nothing to do with what he was wearing. I did look on the website post our visit under their policy section to describe the dress code as .....", "'Smart casual. No athletic sportswear and shoes, no flip flops, no beach wear. Denim is acceptable. The team reserves the right to deny entrance should a guest\u2019s attire and overall presentation not adhere to our dress code.' ", "After making it up to the floor of the restaurant we were then told that as we were now 10 minutes late and therefore could no longer seat us at a table. Instead we were told we could have a seat at the bar if we wished. However, as the restaurant was not even half full this seemed unreasonable why staff flat out refused to seat us at a table for lunch. Needless to say we swiftly left and instead dined at The Big Easy, a few minutes away on the DLR. ", "I suggest that the policy on dress code as well as the cut off for on a booking is explicitly made clear when booking a table so others do not also waste their time.", "We will not be trekking halfway across London to this establishment again. Dreadful."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r488983654", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Brunch", "diner_date": " March 2017", "rating_date": "30 May 2017", "answer_text": ["We think your review is divine too! We're thrilled to read how much you had a great time with us ; we hope to have you again soon soon soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Clairewk", "reviewer_origin": ["Swansea, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r488983654-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Beyond amazing. The view is phenomenal, the staff are fantastic and the setting is absolutely divine. It is very worth visiting, go, go, go x"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r489286692", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "An excellent meal and great view's", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "31 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your comment. We're glad to hear you had a great time with us and that you will visit us again soon. When are you back?"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Aldeby", "reviewer_origin": ["Beccles, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "74"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r489286692-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We had dinner at Bokan. Could not fault the meet and great. The care and knowledge from all the staff. The food appearance and taste was exceptional. The view with the well spaced tables over ", "London and despite its location quite well priced at \u00a350 a head including drinks. Will definitely return. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r489842347", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Good food, spectacular views", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "2 June 2017", "answer_text": ["We feel fantastic to hear that you enjoyed every aspect of what we offer here at B\u014cKAN! All the B\u014cKAN Team are very proud to read your kind words. We hope to see you again very soon too!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "PandGK", "reviewer_origin": ["London, England"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "106"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r489842347-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice friendly helpful people. Lady showed us the 39th floor bar area. At 7:30pm last Wednesday the area was very busy, outside there were some guys smoking. The views all around were spectacular.", "Went down to 37th floor for our meal. A bit away from the window but the views (sunset in particular) just great, when we left it was dark so lights had come on all around. The food was very good and well presented. Stephan, the restaurant manager, was very friendly and helpful - we had an enjoyable conversation. Our waiter was very professional and described each dish.", "We will return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r490059699", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Absolutely Fantastic! ", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "3 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Your review has us blushing! This is why we're here; to give you a fantastic time! Thank you for the praises - we will share the love with the entire team.", "We look forward to have you again and again!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "aemanna173", "reviewer_origin": ["Bydgoszcz, Poland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "95"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r490059699-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I am enjoying London more and more with every visit and this time Bokan made my night truly great!", "It is impossible to describe that beautiful view which welcomes you when you enter the top floors! Great design, you can see that everyone's paying attention to details, decor is so interesting! Super friendly but professional staff, delicious drinks, nice music. Bokan is a perfect place for going out with friends, enjoying time with your family or having any type of meetings. Entire Hotel looks impressive and promising. This is a great new place on the map of London and definitely a MUST VISIT! I'm looking forward to stopping by again and again... ", "Big thanks to all bartenders, waiters and everyone who's making this place so great! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r490457749", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent Lobster!", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "4 June 2017", "answer_text": ["A BIG THANK YOU for your review and praises! We are delighted to hear that you had a great time with us and that you loved the lobster. We look forward to welcoming you again soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "BGIWorldTraveller", "reviewer_origin": ["Barbados"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "376"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "598"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r490457749-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Stayed at the Novotel London Canary Wharf recently and this amazing restaurant occupies one of the top floors. The food and service was superb. I cannot forget how tender my lobster was. It's highly recommended!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r490571220", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Service as bad as view is amazing", "diner_date": " June 2017", "rating_date": "5 June 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your feedback. We're terribly sorry about your disappointing experience. We can assure you that this is not a true reflection of the service we want to offer here at B\u014cKAN. ", "We are very concerned by our guests' feedback and I would be more than happy to discuss directly with you about this experience. I would appreciate if you could contact me directly either by email at justine.freytet@accor.com or by phone at 020 3530 0515.", "Service is our priority and we hope you will give us another opportunity to shine?"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MarieDjinn", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r490571220-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["It is the second time we have visited the Bokan 38, and although the food is amazing, the service once again was very poor.", "The hostess welcoming us was quite abrupt (on 38, not ground floor), and for the duration of our lunch didn't spare a smile.", "Our waitress was lovely and smiling, but didn't follow through the lunch: ie after our food was brought (by other people), she reappeared when we were finished to ask if everything was ok. My husband explained that although the food was excellent, no as I had to go to the bar to ask for cutlery, salt&pepper, and sauce, that half of my club sandwich was cold, and the burgers were just warm. So she proceeded in telling us that if we wanted a dessert , that would be on the house However, we never saw the menu. ", "We had asked a second round of drinks to the young lady who served us the food, and not being a waitress, she went to the bar to ask someone to come to the table to take the order...it never happened! I had to go to the bar to check on the order to be told that they didn't have it, to go back to the table that someone would be there shortly.....We had the second round after finishing the food. Long...too long.", "However, when we asked for the bill, it comes very quickly with the card machine.", "What can I say, the view is breath taking and the concept is great, but most of the staff there should have a thorough reminder of what pro-activity and customer service are."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r485960826", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "brilliant views", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "20 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your comment! We're glad to hear you had a great time with us. We hope to see you again very soon !"], "reviewer_pseudo": "donnalou1409", "reviewer_origin": ["Daventry, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "45"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r485960826-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["we didn't eat as arrived to late but did partake in a few beverages ", "amazing views from both inside and out ", "bar was very busy", "great atmosphere and quite fascinating watching the cocktails and drinks being made - very much a show bar ", "we went outside a lot of tables were reserved with times on etc but these times had long passed so we sat and made the most of the views - plently of cosy areas and lots of blankets for the cool chil"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r486060988", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Touching the Sky", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "21 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Wow. Thank you for such an amazing review! It is always our most treasured reward to make our Guests happy. The B\u014cKAN Team is very proud to read your kind words. Please note that we have live band every Friday evening and Jazz on the roof every Sunday. We hope to see you again very soon too!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Pacifr", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "73"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r486060988-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Spectacular location for this brand-new restaurant and bar, on top of the Novotel Tower Canary Wharf (38th & 39th floors). Either if you go there for a few drinks at the bar, or for a proper meal at the restaurant, you will not be disappointed, as the venue displays a 360 view over the financial district and central London in general (Hello Shard!).", "Outside space can be a bit windy sometimes, although well covered to shelter guests from the infamous London rain.", "Live music every day is a nice touch.", "Drinks are excellent, and bartenders are able to prepare also cocktails off the menu.", "It is advisable to reserve a table in advance, as this place is the new sensation in London at the moment, so it can be very busy, and I am sure it will soon become a staple for happy hours, mostly during the forthcoming summer season."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r488545065", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Fantastic venue, views and food. Service is slow.", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "28 May 2017", "answer_text": ["We loved reading your review, thank you so much! ", "The view of London is indeed outstanding and we're glad you appreciated it, as well as the Jazz on the rooftop. Service is one of our priority and we are sorry to read that it was too slow. We'd love to have you back for another experience with us, see you soon?"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Rogsta", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "59"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r488545065-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Regardless of the slow service (30 minutes for starter to arrive having waited 10 to be asked for drinks after being seated, the overall experience was very good.", "The senior waiting staff offered complimentary glass of wine and dessert which made up for the service issue and it seemed they had many people arrive just before we did.", "The views are spectacular and I would recommend it over the restaurants at the Shard, being able to get fresh air and have live jazz on the terrace is in my mind a better experience here than what you'll get at the Shard eateries."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r485353200", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lunch on the 37th floor", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "18 May 2017", "answer_text": ["A massive thank you from the bottom of our hearts! The B\u014cKAN Team is concentrating their efforts towards a common goal, making every meal a unique and unforgettable experience. We're extremely happy to see you had a great time with us. Hope to see you soon"], "reviewer_pseudo": "h0lidaystay", "reviewer_origin": ["Forestville, Australia"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "64"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r485353200-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We were curious to have lunch out at this new venue in the Novotel and thoroughly enjoyed our meal there. My husband had a light crab entr\u00e9e which was attractively presented. I had the most beautifully cooked grilled fish and our son enjoyed his very satisfying lamb dish. Our artistically presented desserts completed a very enjoyable lunching experience. All beautifully served."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r486217689", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing food, gorgeous views, lovely staff", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "21 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Your review has us blushing! It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed your experience with us. Come back soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Joanna H", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r486217689-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The food is exquisite and beautifully presented, the staff are incredibly friendly and attentive. Bearing in mind the wonderful views and high standard of dining, it's very fairly priced. Loved it!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r486361429", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing views for dinner or deinks", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "22 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your kind words! Great to hear you liked our new place and its Fabulous team. Hope to see you soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MrGV79", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "77"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r486361429-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["This place is just amazing and if you go on a nice clear day, you'll be there for a treat.", "Make sure you book a table if you go on normal busy hours.", "All members of the staff were happy and friendly, the food was very good (I had seabass) and the prices not too bad. ", "Make sure you take your sunglasses if you go there when the sun is shining. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r486580838", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Awesome, Awesome, Awesome", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "22 May 2017", "answer_text": ["We're thrilled to hear you enjoyed every aspect of what we offer here at B\u014cKAN! Thank you for your feedback. It makes us proud to hear that you enjoyed your experience with us. We look forward to welcoming you back very soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "F7763XWchrisk", "reviewer_origin": ["Leigh-on Sea, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r486580838-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["So, on the recommendation of a friend, and seeing the published photos this looked a great place to have dinner and also see the London skyline. It certainly didn't disappoint. Our table was booked for 7.15pm and we were promptly walked to out table. A cloudy day, and what could have dampened the view , soon changed to sun streaming through the cloud to highlight The Shaard and Millenium Wheel, sites we were able to see from our seats at the window table. Although the table had a 2 hour rebooking slot, something made clear in the booking, we were not made to feel as though we had to rush off or that someone was waiting for the table. As for the food. Well this has to be some of the best I have tasted in a while. From the 'amuse-Boucher ' to the main course of fillet steak, all tasted amazing. Will definitely be going back. Will have to just make up a special occasion to justify the visit. The icing on the proverbial cake has to be the roof terrace. The views from here, once evening had taken hold, were amazing. Being a little chilly that evening meant we couldn't spend as much time out there as we would have hoped but in the summer, provided it's not too British, this will be the only place you will want to be."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r487485669", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great Views & Food, but expensive", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "24 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Many thanks for sharing your feedback. We're delighted to hear you loved the food. The service is our priority and we want our Guests to have a great and memorable experience with us. We'd love to have you back too !"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Joanna R", "reviewer_origin": ["Bromley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r487485669-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a romantic dinner here, views are great. Its a dark, modern vibe, food was fantastic.", "Service was friendly but a bit hectic, our waiter was lovely, however, other staff kept also coming to the table. Was a bit too much, then one of the Managers took my unfinished glass of wine away when I was not paying attention!!! I told my waiter and he was very apologetic, replaced the glass full, and when our bill arrived ALL our drinks were taken off the bill, which was a more than kind gesture. I think the feel of the staff came across like they were not sure what was going on, however I think the place had only just opened. I would return to this restaurant again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r488264897", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great view. Slow service", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "27 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for sharing your feedback. We're glad to hear that you still enjoyed the view but extremely sorry and disappointed that your experience with us was not perfect. Service is one of our priority and we are sorry to read that it was too slow. Please be reassured that your valuable feedback has been shared with the Team. We'd love to see you again to give us another chance to shine."], "reviewer_pseudo": "minky82London", "reviewer_origin": ["london"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r488264897-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Live close by so decided to go for a few cocktails. Booked online a week ago. We arrived tonight and were seated quickly. Rooftop view of London is amazing in all directions. There were lots of security guards, some friendly, others less so. We were given a cocktail menu within 5 minutes of sitting down. No sign of waiting staff 15 minutes later so went to the bar to order. They take your card number to open a tab. Only stayed for one drink as a bit chilly and the seating wasn't great. Paid the bill not noticing that a 12.5% service charge was added. Very cheeky especially as I got my own drinks."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r488352019", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sunset and dinner @ B\u014dkan", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "28 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Wow...A Big thank you Caroline for your awesome review! ", "It is always our most treasured reward to make our Guests happy. The B\u014cKAN Team will be extremely proud to read your review. ", "Can\u2019t wait to welcome you back too! "], "reviewer_pseudo": "carolinebr3", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r488352019-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Throughly enjoyed the experience @ 38 B\u014cKAN. BooKed table on the roof top for late afternoon cocktails, second round on the 37th floor and dinner on the 36th. Great afternoon and most delicious dinner. Top notch cuisine, friendly staff and most professional. Very impressed. Chicken with foie gras and curry Osso Bucco cooked to perfection. Can't wait to return"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r481586663", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "second chance", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "4 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for taking the time to share your opinion on TripAdvisor about your recent experience at BOKAN.", "We are very disappointed to hear that you did not have a good time with us. We are very surprised to read the poor customer service you are describing here. Service is our priority and we All strive for our Guests to have a great and memorable experience with us. We are very concerned by guests' feedback and I would be more than happy to discuss directly with you about this experience. Please, do not hesitate to contact me directly either by email at justine.freytet@accor.com or by phone at 020 3530 0515 should you like to share more details.", "I hope you will give us another chance to show you the true hospitality and service that we are able to deliver."], "reviewer_pseudo": "david j", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "66"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r481586663-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["After my last dismissal attempt to make a booking i decided to visit unannounced to this well reviewed restaurant. It has a number of good reviews but i cannot see why at all. On arrival at the Novotel reception we were greeted by 5 members of staff all carrying IPads wow you may say? they directed us to the bar, but i could not see the reason for their presence as they didn't speak to us we spoke to them, very odd.", "On exiting the lift to the restaurant area we were met again by a very pretty young female maitre d, thats were that ends, she was confused and couldn't understand why we were there?", "We left the foyer and approached the bar were by we noticed behind the bar, 2 males picking leaves for garnish, 1 female waitress drinking a glass of wine and another constantly walking around making no eye contact or serving customers, strange we thought in a bar? how do they make money you may well ask.", "After waiting almost 10 minutes and not being acknowledged, we left and returned to the foyer area. I approached one of the same five greeters as we entered, and informed her of the extraordinary poor service we received, she apologized turned and carried on talking to the remaining 4 staff, i would love to meet the fool who employed this bunch!!. ", "As an employer myself, i was horrified to witness such poor customer skills and attitude to customers needs such as food and beverage, thats sarcasm!!, its obvious its not their money at stake, whilst the restaurant has good reviews this is our second time to this cheap rate hotel, this has certainly been reflected in our 2 visits, would i venture there again, no! i live here in Canary Wharf but would not recommend this restaurant or bar. Whilst tourists may stray unwittingly in, locals beware, its not good, for those who think its good value try Roka, Carluccio's, The Parlour, Plateau or The Manhattan Grill to name just 5 for those of you wishing something big and brash try Big Easy those of you who crave a view, try Nelsons column"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r482558191", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "amazing restaurant", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "8 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Wow, it seems you've been BOKAN-ized! Thank you so much for your praise. The Team will be extremely happy to read your review. Come back soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Gastrobcn", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r482558191-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I went for dinner last week, and is a beautiful new restaurant, with incredible views, great service and amazing food. i really enjoy the food, was really tasty full of textures and wonderfully cook and presented"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r481727804", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing!!!", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "4 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Wow, we love your reveiew! \"The best food & drink & customer service in London!!!\" That's some statement! Thank you thank you thank you! Come back soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "ForValerie", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r481727804-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Please give our thanks to all Bokan team! What a great place! The best food & drink & customer service in London!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r485108538", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing \"Shard\" type views", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "17 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thanks for the 5 star review. We're thrilled to hear that you liked B\u014cKAN - come back soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "CliveB83", "reviewer_origin": ["Winchester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "111"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "53"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r485108538-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["So a great sky bar with panoramic views across London. This is another great addition to Londons choices of high level bars with far reaching views and a cool interior. ", "The usual choice of cocktails abound and the atmosphere is buzzing."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r484180987", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sunday afternoon chill", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "14 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi Anne,", "Thank you very much for your amazing review! Raul will be jumping for joy to read your kind words. ", "Looking forward to welcome you back!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "AnneL2305", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r484180987-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to Bokan for drinks on the rooftop (39th floor) on a Sunday afternoon. It is an excellent experience to recommend for its decoration (East London style), atmosphere (amazing live music group) and service. Special thanks to Raul from the bar who nicely looked after us. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r482754780", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Poor first visit ", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "8 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your review, we appreciate you share your feedback. We are terribly sorry to hear about your disappointing experience. We really want our Guests to keep a good souvenir of their experience and we would like to express our sincerest apologies it was not the case.", "I would love to hear more detail from you about your visit so that we can better address this situation. Feel free to email me at justine.freytet@accor.com ot to call me at 020 3530 0515 and we'll continue the conversation. Thank you once again and we hope to hear from you soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "muscatand", "reviewer_origin": ["Muscat, Oman"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r482754780-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I arrived at the restaurant to be told it was closed which was understandable given the 10pm time but was informed that bar snacks were still available. I asked for a drink and a club sandwich at the bar and was told to take a seat and someone would take my order.", "After thirty minutes a waitress noticed I'd been waiting and asked if I would like a glass of water (with a club sandwich please!!) she apologized for not noticing I was there (6 feet 1 and 16 stone) I took the glass of water and she disappeared again.", "Thirty five minutes without a drink or food order - unfortunate as it seemed to be a great place with a nice atmosphere."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r482752187", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great evening", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "8 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Your praises on our attentiveness are surely one of the best compliments you could ever make to us! Thank you very much Phil for your nice review. We hope to see you soon on a sunny day for another business or social event!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "philcV2258FO", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r482752187-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Had my first experience of Bokan last week and wow what a great location for an evening out.", "The staff were extremely attentive in both the bar and restaurant and made the visit extra special.", "The menu had a great selection and offered a great non complex choice which when presented looked and tasted like a top star restaurant.", "It's a pity the weather wasn't a little warmer as the terrace on the 39th floor would have been ideal to hangout and hear the live music that is often on offer.", "I was there for a business meeting but would Highly recommend a social visit also.", "Thanks Bokan- keep up the good work "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r484260722", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous food and service", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "15 May 2017", "answer_text": ["\"Top 5 worldwide\" best restaurants, that's some statement! We're absolutely thrilled to hear how much you had a good time with us! Big thank you for your praises - when are you back??"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sunandsailcat", "reviewer_origin": ["East Grinstead, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r484260722-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I went for dinner with my family yesterday evening. We are lucky enough to eat out a lot in top quality restaurants for business and pleasure and I can honestly say that this rates in my top 10 - probably even top 5 worldwide.", "The taste and presentation of all the dishes was absolutely top notch. Good quality produce beautifully prepared by the talented chef. Although this can be classed as \"fine dining\" , unlike a lot of other restaurants who claim fine dining, the atmosphere wasn't at all stuffy which is great.", "The Roof top terrace and the bar below have great views of the City skyline, the 02 and beyond. Live music plays on a Sunday which just adds to the atmosphere. ", "The service was good without being over the top, the waiting staff and sommelier are rightly proud of the restaurant and I would heartily recommend Bokan. ", "I will return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r484246483", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Amazing views / poor welcome", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "15 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for your review and feedback. ", "We are terribly sorry to hear that the only disappointment was with our dress code policy and that it affected your experience. We understand your frustration and be reassured that we will share your remarks with the Team. ", "We hope you will visit us again for a seamless experience so you can fully enjoy the views and the drinks!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "AnnMo83", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "72"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r484246483-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went there for a drink on a Saturday evening. The place got amazing views and is very nice with a large choice of drinks. ", "The only disappointment was the security at the door. My friend was told by the security lady that she was being done a favour being allowed in with trainers (nice trainers not gym trainers!). The people behind us had exactly the same remark. And when we got to the bar we noticed that 40% of the customers were actually wearing trainers. This was therefore not the best welcome you can expect from a place like that. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r484725202", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Very nice roof bar", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "16 May 2017", "answer_text": ["We are over the moon to hear you had a great time with us! Thank you very much for sharing your feedback. We have 6 different craft beers by the bottle but not draught beers.", "We don't see the view from the lift so we can be blown away when you arrive at BOKAN!", "We can't wait to have you back!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Olambu l", "reviewer_origin": ["Essex, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r484725202-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Very good welcoming start from the entrance ", "Very good service and view ", "Drink price is quite reasonable but restaurant is bit pricey but worth it ", "They can think about to add another premium draught beer ", "I wonder why they did not think to have view / window from lift ?"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r478320473", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing night", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "23 April 2017", "answer_text": ["Well, your review is breathtaking too! Thank you so much for your kind words! Great to hear you loved our new place. Come back to visit soon!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jane M", "reviewer_origin": ["Manchester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r478320473-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Breathtaking views, relaxed and yet upmarket. ", "Wonderful ambience and , as expected, top notch service. ", "Lovely outdoor top floor bar, gorgeous atmosphere, chilled music and cosy throws for when it got chilly. Loved it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r481234340", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "There is a special place in my heart for Bokan", "diner_date": " May 2017", "rating_date": "3 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Viktorija, we would like to thank you from the bottom of our hearts for this heartwarming review! We are ready to welcome you again and again and again for lunches, cocktails, dinners, coffees... We don't have marketing positions at the moment but keep looking at us - your enthusiasm and passion is exactly our style!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "viktorija16", "reviewer_origin": ["Southampton, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "79"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "55"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r481234340-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I have visited this place about 15 times now and not because I live just 2 minutes walk away, but because it's so amazing, that I fell in love with it.", "For the restaurant: you do need to make a reservation in advance, and if you want a window table, do mention it while booking. The menu selection is amazing, I did try almost all of it. In my opinion the best from the starters are Sea Bass Carpaccio and the Squid, for the main is definitely an Angus Steak and the best dessert you must try is a Tropical Floating Island! The service so attentive, that we were recognized from the second visit. ", "For the bar: they have one of the best selections of cocktails. And a very good Lithuanian mixologist, that I would highly recommend getting cocktails from (don't remember what was his name). All cocktails come with a nice unusual decorations and the prices are very pleasant as well. I would definitely recommend to try a Hendricks Tea Pot! The terrace is very cozy, has loads of cushions and blankets and you can even order cigars. ", "Overall, it's the best sky bar I have visited in my life and there is a special place in my heart for it. Still looking up their career page, waiting for a marketing position to come up, as I would love to show the world how beautiful this place is! I would definitely recommend it to everyone and come back many more times! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r479459815", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "A much needed addition to the Wharf\u2019s bar and restaurant scene", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "27 April 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for the kind words Sam! We are thrilled you had a good time with us. Sorry for the delay in the Service, that's not great and we will improve that. We look forward to welcoming you back very soon "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Sam K", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r479459815-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["A very good looking venue with excellent views, including a unique rooftop terrace. The drinks are excellent and the food is above average. Many reviews have mentioned the service, and I agree that this probably the single most important issue this new venue needs to sort out. Waiting 30 minutes for a drink is not great. However, speed of bar service aside, all the staff were friendly and professional."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r479768966", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great service", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "28 April 2017", "answer_text": ["WOW, Juan is a super star indeed! He is going to jump for joy to read your kind words, thank you so much! We're absolutely thrilled you had a great time, we look forward to seeing you soon again."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Raz_D29", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r479768966-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Juan, excellent service and very professional you Rock!!! whether if was a pot of tea or just a conversation you rock!!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r480252443", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Ok food, great views but pricey and slow service", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "30 April 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your feedback. We're terribly sorry your experience with us was not perfect. We can assure you that this is not a true reflection of the service we want to offer here at Bokan. Could you please send us an email with your full name, email address, phone number date and time that you visited us, so we can investigate further? Many thanks"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Steven H", "reviewer_origin": ["Chesham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "59"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r480252443-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went for a friend's birthday lunch on a Bank Holiday. Very impressive views out over Canary Wharf, the interior has been well designed and the view from the men's loos is something else (we all made a point of going for a look). However we waited an hour for our starters to arrive and thought they were nice it wasn't worth an hour's wait. The chef clearly was struggling and sent an amouse bouche to keep us occupied but we had to ask for bread which should have come as standard. The mains were nice but I was certainly not going to leave feeling stuffed. Slight style over substance and for the price I would expect more of a complete plate of food. We were there not long after opening so it may have been a glitch, it was only half full so they would not have coped with a full service."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r479356665", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "27 April 2017", "answer_text": ["We're fan of your review! Thank you so much for your praises. We use indeed a mixture of local British ingredients to craft a menu inspired by rich European cultural cuisines. Thank you for your recommendation about the bread, we will look into this. Looking forward to welcoming you back."], "reviewer_pseudo": "SarahHongKong_40", "reviewer_origin": ["Hong Kong, China"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "41"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r479356665-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I loved this restaurant. I stopped at the hotel so experienced the high quality breakfast and ate dinner here twice. ", "The service is outstanding and helpful. The views over London are glorious. ", "On my first visit for dinner I tried the lamb which was probably some of the best lamb I've ever tasted. The dish itself is quite rich but we ordered a side of veg which balanced it out and the veg was done well. ", "I also tried the fillet steak. Beautifully presented with mash and roasted onions. ", "There is a good wine list with plenty of wines by the glass. ", "My only complaint was the sharing bread seemed wasteful if you're eating alone or even for 2 people.", "The breakfast has high quality produce carefully selected such as beautiful fruit and free range sausages. All produce appears to be British. Excellent!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r480452407", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing!", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "1 May 2017", "answer_text": ["YAY, Big thank you for your fantastic review! The Team will be very proud to read your kind words. Come back anytime, you will always be more than welcome in your second home!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "mudchute", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r480452407-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I'm so lucky to have this as a local bar/restaurant and have been three times since it opened. Came for a birthday lunch on Friday and it was one of the best meals I've ever had. The seared sea bass was as beautiful to look at as it was to eat and I can say the same for the chocolate and blackcurrant mousse. ", "The views are just amazing and the restaurant tables arranged in such a way as to make the most of them. When you think of how much you pay to go up the Shard (which I also love by the way!), you can come up here instead and enjoy a drink or a lovely meal for a similar price. Plus you get to see the river encircle the Isle of Dogs and get views of Greenwich and the city as well as 'up close' Canary Wharf. The ambience is stylish but relaxed and doesn't feel stuffy and the staff are lovely and helpful.", "Love it!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r480694635", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Brilliant roof top bar", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "1 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your review! We're pleased to hear your kind words and that you plan to visit us at the hotel too! Hope to see you soon."], "reviewer_pseudo": "341miteshc", "reviewer_origin": ["Manchester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "19"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r480694635-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["this review is only based on the bar.", "good selections of wines and spirits. great cocktail menu and good, friendly bar staff. It's a roof top bar and amazing views of London. I will go again and next make an effort to stay there."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r481210125", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "a little pricey but really great views and service and food!", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "3 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Great to hear you enjoyed the buzz at BOKAN! Looking forward to seeing you again."], "reviewer_pseudo": "lisaejt", "reviewer_origin": ["Houston, Texas"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r481210125-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Gets v crowded after 8. Nice buzz at bar,(bar menu great, some great new wines) restaurant delicious. No complaints "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r481060098", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Far from perfect ", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "2 May 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you very much for sharing your feedback Federico. We're glad to hear that you still enjoyed the view and the cocktails but disappointed that it was not as good as the first time with your friend. We are very concerned about your comments and we would like to understand better where they were lapses. I would appreciate an email from you at my email address justine.freytet@accor.com. Many thanks"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Federico S", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r481060098-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Been there twice, first time everything was almost perfect (but we were served by a friend), second time the only good things were the cocktails and the view. I'm sorry to say, but given that I work in this industry too, I would expect the whole staff to be much more professional and welcoming. One of the bartenders kept arguing with the waitresses (one of them even started to cry, everything in front of the guests), and he tried to apologise by offering us the second round of drinks. They aim to be one of the best bars in town, but they are still very far from this achievement. Still far from a remarkable experience."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r474026684", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Good view, poor service, ordinary food", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "10 April 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review. We're so sorry to hear we did not fulfill your expectations. Our service charge is only discretionary as a reward for our Team to show your appreciation regarding the service. ", "Every feedback is a gem and we would love to have more details about your experience.", "If you could send me your full name, email address, phone number date and time that you visited us, so we can look into this further? My contact details are justine.freytet@accor.com or 020 3530 0515. Many thanks"], "reviewer_pseudo": "davidhE6187DP", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "34"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r474026684-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The venue is great, and worth a trip for the view alone, but do not stay to eat or even drink. It took us half an hour to be seated, with staff ignoring us, and palming us off to other disinterested staff members. We eventually ordered a bottle of prosecco, which took 45 mins to arrive and 2 trips to ask why it was taking so long. We ordered a cheese platter to start, and waited almost an hour and half for this to arrive. We were however given a plate of calamari by way of apology, but we noticed that the only reason for this, was because they had ordered it by mistake, and didn't know what to do with it. The cheese board eventually arrived and was very uninspiring - not worth \u00a320!", "We decided to go and eat elsewhere as the whole experience was a bit of a joke. We noticed we weren't the only table complaining, as wrong orders were being delivered and people were waiting ages for drinks. The mandatory 12.5% service charge really topped it off"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r476106869", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Horrid service, lovely place", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "16 April 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for your feedback and your praises.", "The service is our priority and we strive to make sure every Guest has a great time with us at B\u014cKAN. We're terribly sorry it was not the case last time you came. We'd like to look into this further, do you think you could contact me to discuss about it? Or send me more information? My contact details are justine.freytet@accor.com // 020 3530 0515.", "Thank you again for your nice review and honest feedback, we hope you will visit us again."], "reviewer_pseudo": "RobTheRusski", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "38"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r476106869-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Bokan is by far one of the coolest, most beautiful bars/restaurants in Canary Wharf. The drinks are great and the food (although the menu looks a bit boring) is surprisingly good. The service however is so horrid that if it weren't for the terrific views, most people would never come here again. Even when empty, it can take up to 30 min for a drink. It took us nearly 10 minutes to get a menu at dinner. With proper training of the staff, this place could be spectacular. Come if you're a slow drinker or if you have serious patience."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r474921960", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great rooftop bar", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "12 April 2017", "answer_text": ["Wow, thank you so much for your review and praises! We don't use incense but some of our cocktails are smokey - it might explains your sneeze. ", "When are you back?"], "reviewer_pseudo": "we4loveusa", "reviewer_origin": ["Bedfordshire, UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r474921960-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["If you love a rooftop view and cool setting this is the place for you. Really great atmosphere and city views at night. Drinks a bit pricey but probably ok for this area. Table service good and very attentive. There is an overriding smell of incense which made me sneeze but it was worth it for the views. There's a restaurant too."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r475115598", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Great view but slow motion service ", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "12 April 2017", "answer_text": ["We'd like to thank you for sharing your feedback about your recent visit at B\u014cKAN. We like your 'steam punk' definition!", "The view of London is indeed outstanding and we're glad you enjoyed it, as well as the drinks. Service is one of our priority and we are sorry to read that it was too slow. We'd love to have you back for another experience with us - why not trying our restaurant next time?"], "reviewer_pseudo": "haibane", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r475115598-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I just had drinks, which were ok. The view is great and the venue has a modern \"steam punk\" vibe. The service is so slow in almost unbelievable... even when it is not crowded. Good place if you are not in a rush and you don't want to drink much."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r475191504", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "First class food, great service and views are unbeatable", "diner_date": " April 2017", "rating_date": "13 April 2017", "answer_text": ["A massive thank you from the bottom of our hearts! The B\u014cKAN Team is concentrating their efforts towards a common goal, making every meal a unique and unforgettable experience. We're extremely happy to see you had a great time with us. Hope to see you soon,"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MBA1888", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "163"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "75"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r475191504-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["There are 360o views of London from the top - amazing views. But the restaurant is first class. The food is delicious and beautifully presented. Service is also first class. I've also eaten in the bar and the food is different as you would expect. "]}
