{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r463029026", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Food didn't meet with expectations ", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "26 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Hi, thank you for letting us know what you thought about your dinner. We're really sorry to hear BOKAN wasn't for you. "], "reviewer_pseudo": "Renata N", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r463029026-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["I have mixed feelings about the place. The set up, the location and the view from the 37th floor are all wonderful. ", "The drinks are good, however we didn't get the wine we originally ordered. They didn't have it in stock, we got apologiesed and we got over it.", "The problems were mainly with the food. Starters came quick and alright. The butternut squash soup was amazing, the beef tartar was okay. ", "As about mains, the burger is a burger. Nothing much to say. The chicken was however badly undercooked and quite plain. ", "The desserts were not even close to expectations. Yuzu tart was small and boring, barely tasted anything. The chockolate souffl\u00e9 was too much, contained too many eggs and looked raw. They explained to us it was the special crunchy chocolate balls in it. It was not crunchy for sure and resembled to egg yolk badly. ", "The service was okay, bit more practice and it will be perfect. ", "I would have a better opinion if I see more effort to fix the mistakes. Sometimes it helps if you ask what you can do to make it better than simply say sorry or tell the customer they are wrong. ", "They contacted me days later on Facebook and offered a free drink for my next visit. I appreciate the offer, however it came late and I don't feel comfortable receiving private messages from a place I had dinner 2 weeks ago.", "I will not go back there, however I couldn't advice the same for anyone. Go and see, maybe it was just a bad day for me"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r462901371", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Soft Opening - Lessons to be learned", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "26 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you for your review, we love your stye! We appreciate your feedback and recommendations. You have been some of our very first guests to join us on the Bokan journey and as you said there are kinks to iron out here and there. Thank you for your encouragements and congratulations ; we look forward to welcoming you again soon to provide you a seamless premium Bokan dining and drinking experience!"], "reviewer_pseudo": "fly4fun2", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "117"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "127"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r462901371-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["The view from up here is what brings you here, the food is what you will go back for. And maybe the bar too! (hic!) ", "This visit was made during the soft opening period so we were prepared for anything to happen. ", "We had some issues with the meal. My starter was ice cold but the plate had been warmed up. For a pea and mint fritter, that gave the game away that they weren't freshly prepared to order. No biggie, but surprised someone would plate up something straight from the fridge and hope that the customer wouldn't notice. ", "We also had some issues with a member of our party who asked what she could have that was gluten and dairy free and offered alternatives or alterations, one of which arrived with dairy fairly obviously (a chocolate souffle that had a big Bokan signature chocolate (dairy) disc on it as one example). There seemed to be some disconnect with what the front of house staff were telling the kitchen crew and what was coming out. ", "With the other dishes, a fish dish was verging on being undercooked. A rotisserie chicken a tad dry on the breast meat section (wonderful flavour otherwise) and pork belly dishes that were well received. Despite these items, we really enjoyed the food. ", "We passed our comments on to staff to inform not criticise as we knew this was the soft opening but we were very keen to go and see this place. The staff were very gracious in their understanding and more than generous in removing items from the bill without us asking for this. ", "I imagine by the time of the official opening all these things will be ironed out and the place will be jumping. The atmosphere was great, matching the view and decor of the venue. The staff are very enthusiastic and provide a fresh venue for locals and wharfers to go to escape the other, sometimes dull, choices available on the main CW estate. Several of my group are considering hiring out part of the venue for parties, so despite the small setbacks on the night we went, we know that this place will be pretty good when it gets into full swing. ", "Welcome to the Wharf, Bokan!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r462878121", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Teething problems ", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "26 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Thank you so much for sharing your feedback. So sorry about the delay in the Service. Please come again and meet our new bench of awesome people who have just joined the BOKAN Team, we'd love to see you again."], "reviewer_pseudo": "zomof", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r462878121-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["Great views and drinks - but overpriced with haphazard service. Bar food took an hour to arrive... And they were understaffed. I'm sure it will improve - it's a brand new bar/restaurant so there are bound to be teething problems."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d12156905", "id_comment": "g186338-d12156905-r462872187", "resto": "Bokan_37_Restaurant", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d12156905-Reviews-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great addition to the area", "diner_date": " February 2017", "rating_date": "26 February 2017", "answer_text": ["Awwh thank you so much for this fantastic review! We are really flattered to hear your amazing feedback. Hope to see you again soon"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Fabien-E14", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "31"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d12156905-r462872187-Bokan_37_Restaurant-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to Bokan on their opening day to check the venue out and we've been back nearly everyday since! ", "The chef food is of great quality (ex L'Atelier Robuchon) , the service friendly and efficient.", "But the bar and the views are what makes us go back days after days.... the cocktails are amazing and the team on the 39th floor is one of the best you'll ever encounter. ", "Finally a great place in Canary Wharf "]}
